user_reviews: [{"Name":"Eric Burnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVScr8t8WnLqF_KZEDLPRkd-_0tYQYClftfL1AlvPRZvmgWrBpf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maaaaaannn, I love this spot! It’s not just a barbershop, it’s an experience. This is a barbershop you look forward to coming too when you wanna get fresh for the week. Shout out to Chevy Blendz who is an amazing barber. I guarantee you will  look better than you did when you walked in. The crew there is really cool and professional. Definitely will be back in a week or two!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPlvJfyXn2yZcYyYD0D1bEZkGOGaEAiY_3Xyy4Z\u0026fid=0x0:0xff60ccb3ebea235b"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Austin Patraw (Governor4444)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPLQ9tQBgte7DuzROtdek2X1SKwIo9adjZsg4OLHUy_bvlqiEx0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Damarcus for a few months now for my haircuts and as long as he's cutting hair I will be going to him. He's a master at his craft. And he's very kind and welcoming. I am very grateful to have found him. The shop itself is very nice as well. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aleksey Rozanov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsE2xVvapD0vKWl5WW1y9GWh9IGF14dDQyJ90UhTMK_OMSZHZc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It was the worst experience with my haircut I've ever had so far. I had to wait for 20 min despite the appointment time, and the barber was making a haircut with my had turned away from the mirror because \"it's not ready yet\".\nWhen I got home, I realized that my temples were completely assymetric, so I had to fix them with my own scissors...","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Myers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb2X6aYT66G0aZqrVWaTtzmsJWmRtRfj08cIM4g4GYS-cOSdOS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Khi was incredibly thorough and took her time to make sure everything was absolutely perfect. I can’t say enough great things about this gem of a barbershop in the Marcy-Holmes area. The attention to detail, the welcoming atmosphere, and the skill here are unmatched. My best haircuts have come out of this shop, and after today, it’s officially my go-to spot. Huge shoutout to Hassan as well for making the first cut make me come back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zachary A Rogers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJaPBbK7DuPn_bsVP-4N5mWgdqRBYqigIMsclzO56IAA_Fr3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Ace of Fades. I followed James here from his previous shops. I’m from Houston and was nervous about the lack of diversity in Minneapolis to be able to cut mixed/black hair. I’ve now gotten my haircut by both James and Simon and have not been disappointed yet. Plus, northeast was missing a reliable place to get cut. I haven’t seen a bad haircut yet from any of the barbers.. and from what I’ve seen, the braider has skills as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paul B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjsUuWs9xql694E-NA596dKJ38oiT6A7ALcQ8-24E1pqTN4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is an awesome barber shop. James is fantastic. We’ve been going to him for a few years now - he does an amazing job and is so nice (my 6 yo son absolutely loves him too). Can’t recommend Ace of Fades highly enough!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPplZ-mgDgc_fNBCJqXuzuhTn_EqIH0N1YF1zeN\u0026fid=0x0:0xff60ccb3ebea235b"],"When":"2024-3-22"},{"Name":"Trinity Mary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhHCQ1g9SCoEMEoNSzv8eUQyZ_-wVVPuRJftlFlO-Pw2KhvixOuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had one of the best haircut experience with Celeen! She made me feel comfortable and understood when it comes to my preferences with haircuts. I think I found my new barber place!! Thank you sm Celeen!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Finlay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI_Ai1lzUhQP55ExxAT-2-dsqMJ2IzrqROTVgbQsAWBQeb0OMV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celeen is an excellent barber—skilled, detail-oriented, and always delivers a great cut. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Sunic Calero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpvbzushlAMlidOCjlWZ_U42Hit_rCnvCTNJIGamjqKP-K6UgR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Soho really knows his stuff! Super fast with the scissors and pays attention to every little detail. My forehead was looking too big, and he immediately suggested leaving the front a bit longer to balance it out-best advice ever! On top of that, he even showed me the best way to style my hair for everyday looks, so it stays fresh and natural.\nDude isn't just cutting hair, he's making sure you look your best all the time. Definitely will come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacob","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa3fRbYYo4ul3634C40jjwGGjQouELRzW82hfOtz4D9WfeLG3p=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got my hair cut by Soho and he did phenomenal. I warned him that my hair is kind of flatter on one side and he accommodated perfectly. Asked for a little touch up at the end and he knew exactly what was looking at. He also did tricks with the scissors which was pretty cool. 10/10 amazing barber, would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derek French","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx5jRbXIqZvQGtolSDoJHHzeznGZjMrx_Mv-bA4MJm5PCV3QYn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As I like to call it, “Roy’s Hair Lounge” Roy has been my personal barber since my brother recommended him to me.. His fades and skill are out of this world.. He can do hairstyles for me that no one else can. I am very very picky but he has mastered his craft to the point where I can bring in four kids, two of my three boys and my daughter and he can give us all perfect haircuts in an hour. My youngest can’t sit still long enough to get a haircut yet but when he can he will be going to Roy as well!! I encourage everyone to give it a try and tell me it’s not the best haircut you’ve ever had… I’ll wait…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsJjto4ocDkdIzM1QxYRrH5ihNppDJA3XdnwUa\u0026fid=0x0:0x4698416c39a5a2b0"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Paulo Frank","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1g2Zn2IVt1Z2QCZZbcg5q6skJKVeuQ5qNkn5b5MWnYljzSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best barbershop in the Twin Cities. Fair price and excellent service, would highly recommend to anyone in the area. Soho always does an amazing job taking care to get my hair exactly right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Louis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7gFH2c123f3t7NBxsc9XQ-NUiwHeiI8U5MTHqvSc5M6hwyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just move here from Bay Area. First cut in Minneapolis.Tremendous and fabulous! As an Asian, I got the perfect cut. SOHO did an amazing job! Patience super Patience. My bang keep perfect with just a little trim exactly as I mentioned. I have to say it is abs a surprise since many Barber just cut my bang without even understanding Asian style is abs different. 2. He knows I am a little bit bald and adjust the cut based on that.  Abs recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxh_PvgTuq_xdv57glRP8Yvnhmh_Pi-bXivAZzIwO6HIEBN7IDcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Soho is the best y’all! Dude is patient, listens to what you want and also gives suggestions when asked. He is so talented, I will definitely be asking for him again!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwEHBLRj1L8Sn0b8-X-GXwLTEViXbyBhSY59T3\u0026fid=0x0:0x4698416c39a5a2b0"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"BandwagonBlake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpj09eC9HhP7T5HAhA1yWtEWIvPchHRgG-FvX46qxWRw5ptHYqHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"By far the best haircut I've ever received I highly recommend Soho! Not only was it a great haircut but a great experience as well. Thank you Soho I will be returning in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tod H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1heIduDlORC2uAANTWnMWd1qipCEznaCTHzQHzyw_yCWfNA2D9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This might be the best haircut I've ever gotten. The blend from the shorter back and sides to the longer top was smooth. He razored the edges with precision. I've got thinning hair, so feathering the front hairline is critical. He did it just right to make the most of the hairline I've still got :). He trimmed my eyebrows without even asking. This is the kind of skill and - more importantly, care -- that you rarely see these days. Thoroughly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jim Boyne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0JvXL5GYldACkH3v7zmbBavDtTPHsLI8P9x-wIPtzwyBo8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best barber in town! Comfortable, relaxed atmosphere. Always ready to start at my appointment time. They listen to what I need and make sure I am happy with the cut. Good people.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blake Anders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEE7OPfhW9eFZ0dP5H_2yM35xkaVydDPAwxYDsKddAUjXljw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience at the Good Neighbor Barber Shop. From the moment I walked in, I was transported to a cool retro environment that added to the overall charm of the place.

Nick, the barber who cut my hair did an exceptional job. They took the time to listen to exactly what I wanted and then executed it perfectly. The attention to detail in their work is impressive, and it's clear that they take great pride in their craft.

The shop's retro atmosphere is a unique touch that sets it apart from other barber shops. It creates a comfortable and nostalgic vibe that adds to the overall experience.

Thanks again for the fantastic haircut and for providing such a cool and enjoyable environment!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Ayers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNJBK0XjCam3zjcHhvI1gj7WuD5XfKOUDlfx7-s6BnV_Pb5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chill and welcoming environment. Service is top notch. Nick and the team are the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWe7ptYVDWNN21ycZZibv7S8ug-o5vQYN4evzoa0OKTOHJyjYJl8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very impressed. Great cut! Best cut since I've relocated here! Mike was the barber.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shaun Riffe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSt2LgP28rY1zbWoClgiYLZ4K7il1S9MQrL2TQ5142yPwfLId1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick and Mike? They are truly exceptional individuals and masters of their craft! If you're searching for an unparalleled haircut and an authentic, yet contemporary barbershop experience, look no further. These gentlemen are the epitome of excellence. There's no imitation or fads here, my friend. You'll find a sign outside their establishment indicating when you can walk in or conveniently book an appointment through their Google reviews.

But wait, there's more! Nick and Mike's impact extends far beyond their skills as barbers. They are deeply ingrained in the local community. It's remarkable, really. They generously offer free haircuts to those experiencing homelessness. Can you imagine? Not only do they provide exceptional service, but they also make a tremendous difference in the lives of these incredible individuals who may not have the means to afford even the simplest of services that we often take for granted. Nick and Mike are truly the MVPS in their field, without a doubt!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVLy1spA_spX12Kjil1xv8EebG7DJyDpRHFiej&fid=0x0:0x55e4ae3eec7b7c22"],"When":"2024-2-1"},{"Name":"JetBoy Co","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4MVaarzJhZZBuKVnCDaJitCkdcb4gFUf37Qx5oeRToP9s5r6K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike and Nick are good people who give great hair cuts. Only barber shop I’ve been in where everyone there is talking with each other! Such a good place to be and even better place to get a cut!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andy Flamm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVakaWDmLBx76ilwAlmlrP_SUFuQ1xz6Vt9DLeS8wKhkeyiXtg8MA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great haircuts at reasonable prices from friendly barbers...what more could you want? Oh, yes, they also have handy online scheduling!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Willard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmHnKdCOlFCXdZaKzH-v2LPhKjlyObVAMglNi8yn20XSWlvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was in from out of town for the weekend. Scheduled a cut with Nick. He was very professional and personable. Had a great conversation and received a great haircut. Very reasonable price. Would be my go to spot if I lived in the area.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Truman C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB8Aa6j6bkuLvkkESC2pqCWTR9w6YoHDyeHyqQ_zqgFuit0J0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beyond happy I went here. This was my first time being to a barber. Ever since I was a kid I've had my mother and sister who are cosmetologist line me up. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Alex Morawiecki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOXxY8NEWEM2gWXM6iYB02fLL00z8ZEautMb2swD3OJ0I4LQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great people all around and masters of their craft. Hunter has been cutting my hair for a couple of years and I keep coming back because of the genuine interest he has in doing an excellent job every time. Highly recommend him and this shop to all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Benny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUPI2JQo3IyZdYscbbGfbzvtL1hDqZYkwTo0B7XCN6Gbs16McUzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying these guys out as I am growing out a beard and wanted good service. For years I went to Sport Clips and it was an in and out experience with decent results.\nBut I knew I needed some advice and guidance on proper beard etiquette and went on a search. Read the reviews and this place sounded good. From the vibe and decor upon entering, I knew I was home. Kyle C took care of my needs and gave expert direction on how to properly care for your beard. Took his time cutting my hair and forming up my beard and threw on the hot towel for the ending.  I can say confidently that this was by far the best experience I have had at a barbershop. Great atmosphere and you can tell the locals come there a lot by the way the staff greeted everyone pretty much by name.\nKyle C and the gang have earned my business from here on out. Thanks Kyle!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Holets","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhCLbq_288BY3Cbw5r7T-Eu2uHok6h6pYLu4sdspieICd_vOuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Harsh lighting, I can’t see a fade. 90’s music is lazy. Had no bad interaction with barber, it was an empty shop. Owner left negative feedback after my feedback because of sensitivity issues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Collin Carpenter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFTbMdQ4DuJvUHr8Z6xm53P8FrpL4JSOXvNPkRPE6WAtmkMFiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kyle did a fantastic job with my haircut. Well, I was in that boat for too long (about 3 months) after mine [stylist] moved away. I was recommended Elizabeth's and had my cut given to me by Alex. I have no been going every two weeks for the last handful of months, and I will NOT be going anywhere else; at least I hope to not have to. Ya'll better not leave! (lol)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8_wx302vs6tUhMaxY0CxxjmI3P-6krxAE2wRJ\u0026fid=0x0:0x48a399ba593471a2"],"When":"2022-12-28"},{"Name":"Tim Farver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoRRVaeFrTQlk1QlKeAJ3gY_XsSzPLFhI8mFrbFGK6as9Zxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The shopped looked amazing via pictures. I seen photos of the hair style I wanted being advertised, instead of the basic fade/blending pics of low cropped hair. With that being said, I was ecstatic \u0026 genuinely enthralled so I called. This is when I was met with a very unprofessional interaction. Someone ( will not name) answered and said \"Elizabeths\" I said \"hey how you doing?\" I was met with a brief silence than a follow up with \"how can I help you\" I said \"yeah absolutely who do I have the pleasure of speaking with?\" The tone of the response was that of a wtf (if wtf was a tone bare with me) and the words \"who is this?\" I said \"are they're any stylists there I can speak to?\" He said \"what did you say kind of hard to hear you\" So I spoke louder and said \"I asked how where you and if there's any hair stylists available.\" I also started to say while being interuppted something along the lines is this even Elizabeth's it seems unprofessional while I was trying to speak he started to apologize by sayin \"ah my bad man I could barely hear you\" Which isn't true because when I asked who do I have the pleasure of speaking with he said in a nasty tone \"who is this.\" So not taking accountability and the lack of proper telecommunication etiquette with clients I said \"I'm quite disappointed this was my experience.\" And hung up the phone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Huss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTFiwH4eTNXcEhW3lICTL6e3QfLmiwqtU8mb_YtvV5k9s07g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jeremy was super knowledgeable about his craft and really did an amazing job. [{"Name":"Nathan Yi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2syeCgsRikta4ne9i-5-8tPrwA91xEHq8v0SWiwhQIJ4LNirD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Drew is the man! [{"Name":"alex bednar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEaUjTa3t1gFfrTyxyuLSWysiUR7A1YHa_7-TNtxT0wg8jWcs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I used to go to Great clips or fantastic sam's and get basic haircuts but after getting a couple of bad cuts and bad experiences I was over it. Andy is a super easy to talk to laid back barber who can do everything from fades to eyebrows to beards whatever you need he's got you. Card is accepted cash is preferred","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Muneca Muerta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHjjJu1y3OrKN-JUqrpxCNqtxvn_aPKWbpdj_DO5JjFGrqR8w5Ug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic barber shop for young guys who know what they want. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Keith Hagen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwhJiA0AUiPfxQltE20smqTXKBgrwwaKg8JG6RtO3zqH6fDX9J=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an awesome first experience at this gem of a shop, conveniently located on the west side of St Paul for this "west metro/downtown Minneapolis" guy. I went in without a specific haircut/style in mind, but instead, went in with how I needed my new style to work with my life. Andy was my barber for my first time there and he clearly listened to everything I had to say and swiftly produced a plan that matched exactly what I wanted. He communicated his ideas expertly and fully demonstrated his skills with a scissors!

I was very impressed with the feel/vibe of the shop. You immediately got the sense that it was full of stylists that truly cared about their craft and their clientele... yet it felt as far from stuffy and pretentious as one could get. I just felt comfortable with my surroundings the minute I entered. I was graciously welcomed inside and the waiting area was plenty comfortable to hang out in until my appointment time. Andy was promptly on time and had me out of the chair exactly at the time he said he would.

There is a part of me that wants to give this place a bad review so that I have a better chance of getting back on the calendar. But anything bad I'd have to say would truly be a lie and I'll just have to be patient to get back on Andy's calendar.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Easton Maucieri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8fXoW_JYyeSFlt9acgy4oWcJ3_1Pjj_MIzEXy4tJS_ytOlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently got a haircut at The Dapper Wolf, and I couldn’t be happier with the experience. Andy is a true professional—he took the time to understand exactly what I wanted and executed it perfectly. The attention to detail was impressive, and the atmosphere was both welcoming and upscale. I’ve received a ton of compliments on my haircut, and it’s easily one of the best I’ve ever had. If you’re looking for a place that combines great service, skill, and a cool vibe, I highly recommend checking out The Dapper Wolf!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Sonnee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhzWkqqPOoDn6CF6XUPGAtdKqi5-C_W0IkenS4HReKai2NmRK3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Dapper Wolf is an absolute gem. The new place is warm– from decor to the cozy chairs, the owner Andy, has nailed the vibe. Andy is a wizard with scissors✂️ ; he’s cut my hair for 10+ years and has yet to disappoint. The ambiance is top-notch, making it a truly enjoyable experience. If you're looking for a spot that combines style and skill, this is it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfeOxiWkEiW5udY9ynMer6wiQLuM5LpeMk5vj2&fid=0x0:0x64ec5d40da51883b"],"When":"2023-12-14"},{"Name":"Collin Olson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_Gr7TpiP5ihTXDBH3jzKzmG66CDN8mMb46lOV9_oNUzhMUqAx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for the first time and saw Cassandra; it was the best haircut I’ve ever gotten. I have medium/long hair and I couldn’t be happier with the outcome. She’s very knowledgeable and super friendly!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Matos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMpVdzcBCsID78aR13JbGwlkU8krCLhQbd05sJHvJVgO0h02bgug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"TDW is *spectacular*.

After recently moving to the Twin Cities, I read their rave reviews and decided to come here. My 1st appointment was with Jack, who did a stellar, A+ job cutting my hair and dealing with an annoying cowlick. I highly recommend him.

My subsequent visit was in anticipation of my upcoming wedding. Since this is a once in a lifetime event, I figured I'd set the appointment with Andy for both a haircut & beard trim. Suffice it to say, I received one of the best haircuts I've had in *years*. I never trim my beard, but only plastic surgery could have made a bigger improvement than Andy's trim did. Absolutely phenomenal. He also clearly explained how to style my hair & beard myself come wedding day.

Finally, it's worth mentioning that both these gentlemen were extremely affable and great conversationalists. Frankly, if I ever win the lottery, I'm hiring one of these guys to be my permanent, live-in stylist.

Obviously, I'm never going anywhere else for a haircut again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Asher Krisch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcLwEyofE9q7ZOHVZdvk--VyKN5z-cdIG_mIhCgiUhCgnWMX4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I booked a last minute appointment with Dan. He was super professional in his work and really chill to talk to during the cut. I usually have an issue with finding a barber or stylist that can/will do my hair how I want, but he did absolutely amazing! As long as I live in the Twin Cities area I'll be coming here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RezDog","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc1cWJSOMt-yyxeang-yovjxz9QrNUtL9_QilCabLiwbUYEW6Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Drove an hour, not knowing what to expect. I was definitely nervous, considering i have maintained a longer hairstyle for so long. The transformation was amazing. I pretty much let Elaine do her thing and she sent me off to what was a great weekend thanks to her care. I'll definitely be coming back! Also, very nice atmosphere with all the plants 😍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jayce Mulligan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQnq2sbH0pUwzYcXp0WnL0zU40g6Tzhcmp8LEK1Lgvc9XNM4xKFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the only barber shop I have been to since moving to the cities. I love the vibe here, it's got a casually masculine energy that doesn't feel overwhelming or oppressive. I always feel refreshed and confident after my haircuts because Holland knocks it out of the park every time. It's been nice to have someone cut my hair who is willing to go on a journey with me and experiment a little bit. Worth every single penny.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPp2gBAy2bQg2ncBQjESojRTWiAkYW5iDHsMpY7&fid=0x0:0x64ec5d40da51883b"],"When":"2024-8-31"}]

[{"Name":"Josh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrqoyvocIR7ZIguxkINfpUf_JDJhQhmmUTJebLNW79IWin789X=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is such an amazing place. Everyone who works here is so friendly and professional.

Brett is highly skilled and a great listener. After only seeing him once, he nailed my haircut. Prior to that, I struggled for years to find someone who gets it. I even tried excessively overpriced salons. Brett changed all of that. I couldn’t be happier!

Rich also helped me one day when Brett was out of town and I desperately needed a quick cut. He also nailed it! This team has it going on!

On top of all of this, they charge reasonable prices and are also conveniently located in the skyway.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Welter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI3R0AJtO2kfQU1Q6nJUx-CAZ3k4EBym5KRxSypuMkWtrG4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Brett for the first time today. Great guy, did a great job, and reasonably priced. Will definitely go back to him","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Chochrek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKN0Zq6FknR6xiMMYSvg2nMFhFKsKxVx20Alv7sEKHyiOYjiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I genuinely look forward to getting my haircut here. Not only is Brett a great barber, but he is just as good (if not better) of a person. I have never left the building feeling unsatisfied with my hair cut or service. Overall, I would recommend Brett and 225 Barbers to anyone who asks.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"charles toomajian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvVyeg21kRwGvs815i3kdW2zKDyxAkPeHLUDV29kvMeNa_B27_AA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'd been searching for a good barber in Minneapolis for a while before finding Brett at 225 Barbers about a year ago, and now I don't plan on getting my hair cut anywhere else. Brett takes care to talk with you first to understand what look you're going for, and then he nails the execution. I've tried a couple different styles and he's been spot-on every time, whether it's a short taper or going a bit longer. Great attention to detail and unbeatable value.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicholas L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVz1jY9C420SJFZCDAne-LWZqjbcz10I18oZWJLfa7kM4hCtWboZg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 out of 5 stars!

I had a fantastic experience at 225 Barbers in Minneapolis! From the moment I walked in, I was impressed by the [quiet and relaxing atmosphere. My barber, Brett , was [very nice and careful. They really listened to what I wanted and gave me a haircut that I absolutely love. how my haircut was a different style and i loved it. Overall, I was very impressed with 225 Barbers and would highly recommend them to anyone looking for a great haircut in Minneapolis.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Illstone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKElSlg6hls8t3DXMYZ0zhVWH1eTv9Zqdzcid-YBwC29i1e0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had my hair cut by Brett. Nice guy, but if you care about having a precise cut or you have a particular style, then this isn’t the place for you.
There is no real strategy to the way Brett cuts and feels a bit rushed the way he somewhat carelessly uses the clipper over comb without any clear direction, you will not get a good fade.
I think Brett is best suited to an older person who just wants their hair cut, if you are below 40 and care about your hair, go elsewhere.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin Kind","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIoZG43kjt-W_f8mqvnCaC_sI-4M3O1sMeEVclpAnb4PSExmoM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going to Brett for the past couple months over my summer home from college and it has been fantastic. Super personable and did a great job with my fade every time. Would 100% recommend to anyone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Noah Rutgers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7Vo-GP63aOhSTGLmsBdndTJcn8NKYdPOYyLvA7-BhDq-VjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been visiting for a few months now. Greatly skilled and helpful staff. Have given me some excellent direction on a new style. Affordable and timely. If you work downtown, this is the perfect spot for a midday, professional cut.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Would highly recommend to anyone looking for a great haircut from a wonderful human being.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Malzahn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_v_QXiyM7Ei33QcnF8LPdybgv8sD9OoNJ6supWJOxkKO8jQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabe has been cutting my hair for almost 4 years now and he does a great job every time! He also does a great job on my beard, so I go to him before every vacation I take. I would recommend you schedule an appointment online a few days before you would like to visit, he's a solo shop so walk-in availability is very rare!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"alejo gambed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhOKO_oNvBH5YaBIAiNq-1kYW-LdUoQA359onRNTMJKtQcOys=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every service I get from Gabe at Barbers on Bryant has always been top notch! Before interviews or special events I make sure I come to get a touch up and feel full of confidence, he takes extra time to make sure it’s perfect and that I’m happy with how I look!
Thank you Gabe and Barbers on Bryant for being there for me for the last 8 years now!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christian Hoover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvPVfpTbEZYHik8aok_-l3akofLoWAS_quFKXbInuH4G4nFYY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"David did a great job on my hair. He was absolutely meticulous in everything he did. Before we started he cleaned the entire chair, every single one of his instruments and sanitized them. Way more than any barber I’ve had before. He also spent a lot of time on all the edges and blending.

The shop has cool art to look at while getting your haircut too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhW4rWaCmWkTbp3Gbk2RYY0GN4Dsi3ciqUmkP-np5HSsE_Mw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a disappointing experience at Barber's on Bryant with Gabriel. Despite reading many positive reviews, I found him to be hostile when I arrived for my first appointment. Although I was not aware of my mistake, I was confused by his attitude towards me. As I waited for my turn, I noticed that he was also snippy with the previous customer.

When it was my turn, Gabriel was dismissive of my longer hair and didn't seem to care about my online appointment notes. He even said, 'I'm a barber, not a hairstylist,' which made me feel unwelcome and frustrated.

As a result, I decided to leave without getting a haircut. Unfortunately, I cannot recommend this business or Gabriel based on my experience.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I searched my old Google Reviews and found this 6 year negative review on Gabriel when he was working at another shop.

Today was my first time at Lyn-Lake Barber Shop and I was very disappointed.  Their website says walk-ins are welcome and this is why I chose the shop.  During the cut my stylist Gabriel was hostile towards me when I explained my preference to walk-in verse making an appointment.  He suggested I go to Great Clips in the future.  At one point I told Gabriel to stop ‘lecturing me’ as I am not five years old and I understand he wants customers to make appointments. The cut was good and the price fair but the experience overall terrible.  I did not feel welcome at all, which is unfortunate for me as I live a few blocks away and the shop would be convenient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Castillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeTRi_yw6oGTxmNrp3U4rlreaxxhm3l2AszAym5hXzyeQWSLr-_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recommend this place 1000%! Gabe cut my hair and he is one the kindest, most personable, most skilled barbers I have met. He gave me one of the best haircuts I have ever had. EXCELLENT at fades. He will work with you to find the style you want, and he is just such an incredible human! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Riley Cashman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT5KlEZQtAEPqDcIJ9xBU25cxzhjjjCK2RE_cWSVVIY-2KVVbp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gabe was a wonderful barber, very professional and friendly. He made me feel welcome in his workspace and provided a the best barber experience I've had this year. He gave me a high quality haircut and impromptu beard trim (we had time) for a fair price. I love my haircut and it was done better than I had hoped! I will definitely be back for another visit.","Images":null,"When":""}]

He takes card, normally I pay $35. $30 for the cut and $5 tip. Just now I got my haircut and had an appointment at 11:40. The haircut itself was ok but Abdullah was yelling in my ear on the phone and I had to sit in the chair for about 5 mins before he came over to start. I would still come back but it wasn’t a tip worthy haircut today. I give him my card to run and normally I say $35. I didn’t today and he is a bit taken aback and goes “any extra”. I said “not today”. And he goes “ok I am going to charge you $33 for the fees” which is clearly a lie. Credit card processing fees are 2-3% max. Not 10%. I just went along with it and called him out after he had ran my card. I won’t be returning unfortunately. I enjoyed the haircut and convenience of the appointments but the incident today just rubbed me the wrong way.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arif Mirza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfnlmt8PshwvBDUVO_OCUcSadJVmzD1O21tBSS80hi8qfjV1k9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Heard back from Abdullah it was very nice of him to reply back after my message of disappointment. [{"Name":"Andrew Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsCtxnrBL_73y6W3lLFyABlnXim6O_erh4iHULanov1hCrkzIq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The absolute best place to get a highly professional haircut in the twin cities metro area. Been going here and getting my haircut by Anthony for about the last 5-6 years and i trust no one else to cut my hair the way I like it other than him. Great shop atmosphere!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emmanuel Onyeji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFrK-8VMg-lO3_yxN3Egn-bnk4EFvCM9yjMn-JdSbEwL8rlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been knowing Anthony Chapman for about 10 years ever since l sold him a vehicle and found out about his passionate profession of a dedication barber and the best at his craft!. Haven’t looked back ever since. Ask about him, google him, the works speaks for itself, you won’t ever regret it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garret Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5xSnVR1i7sVe0GRiBGKcnj7AtLtjC9EJnD8tZ1uu_LtVxSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Literally my first ever good haircut. I’ve got some really straight hair and I like it long. Every barber I’ve gone to I’ve had a horrible experience except for my last two. One guy for a haircut awhile back cut my hair while on his phone, as well as simultaneously watching the tv. He made my hair choppy and uneven. Another lady at great clips dug into my neck and made me bleed. Dee however paid attention, gave me advice and most importantly cut my hair right. I will be going back again, definitely book my man Dee at your haircut appointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harris Lengsavath","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQWrmhG39DqHQRrwcGin7GYvTJtQ29GO3UfIcKlCzhs_3wZLI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of visiting Details Barbershop, and I must say, my experience was exceptional. From the moment I walked in, I was greeted with a warm and friendly atmosphere. The staff was professional and attentive, making me feel comfortable right away.

I had my hair braided by an incredibly talented hair braider, Amber, who did an amazing job. She expertly crafted four rows with a zig-zag part, and the result was stunning. The braids were neat, precise, and had a crisp finish, showcasing the skill and attention to detail of the braider. I was truly impressed with the quality of her work.

After my braiding appointment, I decided to get a line-up from Anthony Chapman. Let me tell you, this barber worked magic. He took the time to understand my desired style and executed it flawlessly. The line-up was sharp, precise, and made me feel like a million bucks. Anthony’s attention to detail and skillful technique left me completely satisfied with the outcome.

Overall, my experience at Details Barbershop was fantastic. The combination of skilled hair braiders and talented barbers ensured that I left the shop feeling confident and satisfied with my new look. If you're looking for a barbershop that delivers exceptional service and top-notch results, I highly recommend Details Barbershop.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Hernandez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXww_-_DCRrEBl_dMUB9DLfAZ0TCCyR-On_5qImzlSnic8Q9e5JiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very clean professional atmosphere! All the Barbers can cut hair like no other. They are the best of the best!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM704BKU32hWQKVpbItP4925VFCEZRV5JOo4zoZ&fid=0x0:0xb66832331e671016"],"When":"2021-11-13"},{"Name":"Giovanni Torres","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvZdR3dZYOctoiShwFQsshjH6UOPlMr_ip22Qej8v6oZ-4JA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rio is an excellent barber! His haircuts are always clean and precise, and he takes great care to make sure that his clients leave feeling satisfied. I would highly recommend Rio to anyone looking for a top-notch haircut.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kati Herrgott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxmZo3x91nDVzXbveqdEEc6VuA2hA9j4tWyVKyeN1aNCgeZOKe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I brought my son here and was very happy I did. The barbers in the shop were quick to determine we had an appointment as it was a pretty busy Saturday and there would have been a significant wait for a walk in. The barber we were scheduled with was apologetic and let us know right away that he was behind.  My son has loose curly hair and a number of stylist have failed to properly account for the curls. Riio did a fantastic job with my son and his hair. Fantastic Barber.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Liam Titan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHMr-FfsaKBuBIqmOZlUDND1Juu9Ockw2hKb9tptbz2164xVe6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere. The guys here are old-school. It's definitely a stress free spot for the boys. Been coming to Josh and he has been great and has always taken care of me. I recommend the baber shop to anyone who wants to get a pro cut. They do haircuts and beards and very reasonably priced! Support local businesses!!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Make an appointment today and you'll be very happy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdzJn_ykG61qT9GzJ-_eC_yhkOarhRGGCfK78JDRp2p3m1iAed=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Paul is a phenomenal guy with years of experience. I leave with a great haircut everytime.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOD7P8yOtZzqOM5UZI10mRA9iYfpMBJnYYdXYZI&fid=0x0:0xe4240065e42e8c0c"],"When":"2022-4-21"},{"Name":"Scott Simpson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZwV3Zlv_R7fiZAe2AvmXlivDLrAAdRH8MfHGYBBH0QD15hBQC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly neighborhood barbershop. Paul has been welcoming to me since day one and three years later I’m still enjoying great cuts and conversations. A barbershop that leaves you looking forward to the next visit.
Make an appointment and enjoy a friendship.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cameron Ganley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKAIo6YhatJnltlUq9TNRQ3DBwbrm07chZGTdakvHvaJzlUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got a cut from Paul, the owner, and it was excellent service! I move around the states for work, and I'm someone who really values a real barber, not the standard "supercut" cookie cutter haircut.

You can tell that Paul values his craft and takes the time to know your head and understand what you want. We got to talking about a great range of subjects too!

All for 20 bucks, in an efficient and comfortable setting. If you need an actual cut done well, go to Kenwood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacob Nuxoll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUf3Hlfph6-iJBFgleHM5m_q7hNyi0k0vo5g-PJD1eLczy6toej=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I stopped by here a couple of years ago during a visit to the Cities, and they couldn’t see me because I didn’t have an appointment. It’s a small shop—2 chairs—so that makes sense. He gave me his card, and I kept it for my next visit. I knew was coming back for another visit and called a month out. Turns out he wasn’t accepting new customers. I said I understood but had kept his card for years. He was touched and squeezed me in. I told him that wasn’t necessary, but he insisted. I came in, and he did an excellent job. He made me feel comfortable without talking my ear off, which is exactly the kind of experience I like. It was a no frills haircut, but that’s also what I wanted. He’s a barber, not a salon, you know? Strongly recommend if you can get on his list! Thanks for seeing me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkf0e4Tc-vWCEliMZoxo5fuIEzZYEz8tLslid79lv-8Ic1YvjJ4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best haircut ever. I have bounced around between barbers and salons for years trying to find someone who could cut my hair the way I wanted it and no one could do it. I found Kenwood Barbers about a year ago and Paul is amazing. He was able to cut my hair exactly how I described the way I wanted it. I recently moved further away from the shop but I make the drive with no hesitation because of the quality haircut that I receive.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsCeA3ZYn0u3YWcgk6S61ZfPG48P3Hof_xdQNfH4Wkc39HTA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The day before my wedding I realized that I needed a quick clean-up to be ready for pictures, and I tried this place on short notice because of the great reviews. Paul didn't disappoint - best service I could have hoped for, and at an amazing price! Got a better beard trim and shape-up than I've had anywhere else. I'll be a customer here from now on!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anthony Cherek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsb5gnCmqAGBFMy3AD1rOsCT3MOwtQGpKOOhfmciVDgNLAJ1e4iA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I struggled for years to find a place where I was happy getting my hair cut. When I moved to Uptown, I decided to give Kenwood Barbers a go, based off of the great reviews - they did not disappoint. It's very affordable and Paul is a great guy! I love knowing that I'll leave satisfied every time. Heads up, it's cash only.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Go get a fresh cut!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Stark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqMsXj2syzyY4C3cKUjriRAVmwrpak-NbxWNw44P1NWNpCcfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mr. B is a pro! RJ did an amazing job with my son. He asked what I wanted done and did exactly as I described. RJ was fast and accurate with his clippers and unphased by my son's movements. It was a really wonderful experience. The atmosphere in the shop was very calm and inviting. I would 100% recommend and plan on returning for my son in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jet Thammavongsa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3xa10K-9gmQpHD9GRfyfF1W9APvQOWAyrqaTEn8L9AM7xzEH6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Faded barbershop has been a staple to the uptown neighborhood ever since they opened and continues to thrive on great service and professionalism. You are going to get the barbershop talks, the music (not loud no worries), the latest news, or sports on the TVs. Ed’s crew always makes customers feel welcomed which is a warm experience. Ed, one of the best barbers around. His cuts are crisp and he pays attention to your requests and details. They don't waste your time and get you in and get you out.
I have TWO suggestions for you Mr(s) Customer:
1) Book online
2) Give clear communication of what you want, they'll take care of you

Also, they do great charities for the community from time to time and that's something to get behind.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIdHLI0RSQhOdiyP9Rmi-v_KhBUicQPtlDESZK&fid=0x0:0xbc040d69563873d0"],"When":"2023-9-13"},{"Name":"Alicia Northenscold","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJ2m4OJSAopS6QcLOMstkjzyp9951vJdSGoCy0tHNxTnk3FwTH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is it! We have been looking for a consistent spot for my family and we finally found it. Talented barbers, an owner who teaches and guides the crew, clean building space, cool vibe, acceptable prices with an emphasis on getting the kids through the door. (They even did an amazing job with lines for my daughters). Professional, relevant, and clean - just what Uptown has needed! Welcome to the block Faded.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdNX9Jle3jtLdAG7I98ylpXSDEHQaVU3djN3EF&fid=0x0:0xbc040d69563873d0"],"When":"2021-6-18"},{"Name":"B B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZnEe6a3d7j3ZKJnPFN3J0jSaKeerES_zTJQH-R3eVGo9DalXq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great shop. I went in for my first time today. RJ cut my hair and  the haircut came out very nicely.  They have cool hip hop photography all over the walls with basketball games playing on the screen and good music. I’ll be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jack Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrWbjLZoj6EP8v8htgKP-HVSgTx9TCEqsqJl9_BSZ1umO8Vt2Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As the other reviews said, barber was on his phone a lot. Was facetiming with someone during my cut. He also cut my forehead trying to line it up. Will find a new place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdtk2El2S-_nIR3YQiy130cpVG87VGPhcUelX0&fid=0x0:0xbc040d69563873d0"],"When":"2023-9-6"},{"Name":"Omar Mohamud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIRyB3zNPZuCpxulL3Z7dRDD7l2ocapVPAasD3g9v_ZY_WvrOZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent barbershop! Clean shop, friendly barbers, and great environment. I get my cuts from Eddie who is nothing but professional and considerate with your cuts. All the barbers are very good at their craft and they all seem to enjoy being there which adds to the vibe or the ambiance in the shop. Couldn’t recommend a better shop!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Kilgore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfDnEa01S3S9tKUgSpC-sNfHh8zsDgkCAJLcvfh84rp34-eF2t_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming here for two years. Started with Malachi, then Polo, then Gregg and now with Webb. Each barber is better than the next. Great lighting, great atmosphere and EVERYONE looks to take care of you. If you truly want an immersive experience,  Faded Barbershop is where you need to be. They truly represent the culture and it's why I go back and continue to go back and will keep going back!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Ask for Alex!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"chad scharnberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJtAtJKOi8HphcE1pGV3Lte4dGLC6QKGsElATMQN9rHUmHfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have a longer beard and I wanted it trimmed, sculpted and shaped. I won’t be back and will make sure that I pass the word.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cole Oehlers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVd71Vo9IOIrOpzNp4Od-cVLaY-ueRjodOhcfBBi8z1YfYqDP5C=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just moved to the area and was confident that this would be a safe place to try due to the location of the shop. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Steven Debrincat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGA2ljj-AEdIc8uoIWZoRLYnwRK10qPhumKKvSNr7QeeGpNcKN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been getting my hair cut by Aaron since I moved to the Twin Cities 3 years ago and he has always given me a fantastic cut. He and Jess are awesome people. They have a fantastic new salon which is a very comfortable and inviting space. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Sutera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_y6Lv4N5j-Vb_MDqhG0CTEorOndie-qRAFnDcSNlLuN4DdXt-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10! Aaron is both my and my husband's barber whom we started seeing at his old salon. His and Jess's new space is excellent and feels more intimate. Both of them are absolutely genuine, caliber humans who clearly love what they do and the people they serve. Haircuts are always top notch and Aaron goes out of his way to work with you to get you what you want while offering suggestions along the way. Come for a cut and stay for the conversation and friendship (and maybe a beverage!). New location was actually a few minutes further away from us in St. Paul, but we are happy to drive the extra distance to Northeast. Special Note for LGBTQ+ folks: Aaron and Jess are vocal and passionate allies who love to serve all folks, but particularly our community. Theirs is a wonderful, safe, affirming space, which is sometimes, unfortunately hard to find.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jake Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEdN-oTyQEpqhKgTuEogaO974XLg0Qd3m-f35k-ZJerlAEW_86=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My partner and I have been getting our hair done by Jess for some time now and are always so extremely happy with the work she does!! Her and Aaron have created such a warm and inviting atmosphere at their new place, Sturgeon, and they are always so enjoyable to connect with during haircuts. Friendly, inclusive, professional, and welcoming!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jack Wibben","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIao9GMS4Gb6m4RZJg9IDMgP9YTZfOeTpzxId2Iv0MrLcQ9xQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Aaron is the best barber I’ve ever had. Takes his time to get to know you, your hair type and your preferred style. I always feel confident knowing my hair will look good afterwards. Super fairly priced, the new location is very aesthetically calming. 1000% would recommend to anyone looking to get a great cut!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garrett Kubischta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVe61cOkOe9zLHDmdHUdZzF9jBr9Sr7b7_mt0mFh2VvkE9jirFlBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful, warm, and inviting atmosphere! Aaron and Jess are so friendly and do such a great job with the haircuts. And so laid-back!  I've never felt so comfortable during a haircut!\n\nEDIT: Sturgeon keeps getting better. Get great haircut, pick up a nice candle and some gummies for the road.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJcT6-Q2Tp78UpoHLjka1rfIAxb1UEVlpbSxJQWNI6XlX4Jmc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jess cuts my hair on a regular basis and does an unbelievable job every time. Great service, fun conversation, and a super cool shop! I always look forward to going in 🙂","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Ketchmark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkUho_77MBPvKxu8Oq3Q6iXr1SQsOzxJfh2DsBaWlP99tEKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great vibe that focuses on men’s cuts.  Awesome service.  Beautiful, cool space. Aaron is extremely talented.  He listens to your wants and then kicks it up even better than you thought you could look.  Best experience and worth every penny.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mitchell Ewald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIKTs1HYQd9uTQA3LIiHmv5HBml7jwkoUKxHmn52UpQwENZrLbgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible cuts. They run off the business model of \"good cuts, good vibes\", and boy, do they nail it! They've got good music that was curated by one of the owners, they've got a complimentary beer fridge to sip on something while you wait your turn in the queue, and they will spend the necessary time to get you the cut and style you want- the first time! They may be a bit more expensive than great clips, but screw that place, they're hack-artists that will send you home crying 98% of the time. Sturgeon however, they are the real deal. Husband and wife combo who both give just incredible haircuts and I will be going back until I move out of state (which hopefully won't happen because I don't think other locations could match their skill)","Images":null,"When":""}]

Good haircut good vibes and good pricing to","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Gamez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0L-O4n55iYsgcD6l4SCjFETLyV3q0tjQN21wtmJ8tIg8bJioZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best places to get a fade cut in the entire Twin Cities metro.
I've been here a handful of times and I have always been treated with kindness and respect, and I've always walked away with a supreme haircut, and I'll always get compliments from random people about my cut after I get my haircut here.
The barber takes his time to ensure professional quality, and is also fast and very skilled.
This is a true American barbershop that serves and supports the community, and the values and integrity of ownership reflects this.
King Milan's is where it's at! :-)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx5gqoTqZ1L6WP3CV341J4EubMqxvezedZRdTD47KXhiq3UKZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My younger brother gets his hair cut here frequently. I have just chopped my hair(natural woman)  and was looking for a go to stylist or barber to help me maintain my look. I ended up at King Milan’s Barbershop and I am very pleased with the service that was provided to me. From the moment I walked into King Milan’s Barbershop I was greeted respectfully and  I was able to get my hair cut right away! I am overall pleased with the services provided. I will definitely be returning here for my upcoming cuts! Thanks guys for the amazing service.  Not to mention the walk in service as well as the whole seven days a week for service! Best,
Cece☺️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hatim Mohammed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU67eHBw1fxuWk2HzH6xrd0oSIhUGtAqfT689WdadtrY64ecem7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This was one of my worst cuts I’ve ever had in my entire life. I come in asking for a mid taper fade with a slight trim. I wanted to make sure my hair was equal all around. He pick out my hair but not enough to trim it around. This caused for some areas of my hair to be longer then others. The barber then used scissors to trim the front but in doing so made it so my front was half the length compared to the middle. This was the worst part about the cut because u can’t simply ask him to fix it since he already cut it. But there’s also more. On the taper I asked for a mid he did one of them right but the other is too low. He didn’t give me the fade at all. Plus the crazy things is he didn’t even lineup the middle he should’ve pushed my hair back then lined it up for a more straight lineup. Idk how it took me a night to realize how awful this cut is.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tryca Gillespie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBL_4Txr4_uWjzkEJ9dk4u869NXRA08BiT_lwRkXtuBQXnzVtG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been bringing my boys here since 2017 and the barbers take their time and make sure the cut looks good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ric Basurto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7nsOVQBMSjv8oBLRAQhscR7ix6F6-6dmXVDQNfBa8qbUS-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Milan was able to get me in early last minute on a Saturday morning. He gave me a pretty good cut in a timely manner. Smaller shop, but laid back atmosphere. Will definitely return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffany Hicks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVti-cOALbsvqc89hbgLB-FNdVoi8hP2cPig79PlYPTaBpA8VXvxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Best Barbershop in St Paul
I have been taking my 3 sons for almost 3 years now...Not only are the prices great, The Barbershop is open 7 days a week. ALL of the barbers are skilled and experienced, offering that personal touch to each customer who walks through the doors.

The owner does great community outreach and customer appreciation events.The Annual Back to School event where he and the barbers give free back to school haircuts along with backpacks filled with supplies and they provide food and beverage all day long is second to none.

He does monthly customer appreciation events where he provides Free food to customers. The owner also employees the local youth allowing them to come in and help out at the barbershop in order to ear extra money, He is a real champion to and for the community.  You must RESPECT and APPRECIATE his support for the community.

I highly recommend King Milan's...Good vibes, Great cuts, Cool People,  only at King Milans!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

She does an amazing job but has also been so knowledgeable about products and styling for my hair type. She asks questions to get my opinion on things I would have never thought to mention, but this ensures that I know what she is thinking and get exactly what I was expecting and more!\n\nShe is also so knowledgable and helpful when it comes to styling and products. For years I have tried different kinds of products to get my hair to stay including texture sprays, pommade, blow drying, wax, and hairspray and it would always end up flattening pretty quickly throughout the day. In about 30 seconds Jackie was able to explain the issue based on my specific hair type, reccomend products and then explain how to use them. Since then I have actually been able to style my hair and have it last.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alex Rank","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhetAYpuDuq2fXGOhtjxeyxSiGgtKDgPEkUko1trrRY1fFBtSB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I get my haircut every two weeks and I’ve been going to Ken at Capital Barbers for over a year now. It’s the best. He’s always extremely friendly, the shop is clean, and he gives me the best haircut I’ve ever had. I love the atmosphere of the shop too. Very old school but pretentious. The other staff members are great too. If you’re looking for an old fashioned gentlemen’s barber, this is the place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Nelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVevgZTOYZMnTT5x3MgqC5kZMP3jd3bBWRw2n-XWosPGril4EOR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First timer at Capitol barbershop. Couldn’t be more happy with Ken and the haircut. What a great shop. Best haircut I’ve had in the longest time. Thanks!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke Morgan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4Xha8aet_ddSVhwfbVflJTGY177FRDLQxVX21ABUjWc17WjOK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ken is an immensely experienced, efficient, and friendly barber. He's a good communicator and quickly understands what you need in a haircut. He's run shops in St. Paul for nearly 50 years and will take great care of you. I have not used other barbers yet, but everyone I met seemed friendly, competent, and professional.

One thing to know before you go is that the shop is hard to find. Park off of John Ireland (paid parking) for easier access - Google directions will take you to a lot that is only for legislators to park in. Plan on an extra 10-15 minutes to get to the shop, and ask for directions in the State Office Building.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Preston Albrent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvloMfLEdXInSgCX4K9_9I9vOaaCwnvIsPwAQX8_GVCIQcICWh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently moved to St. Paul and discovered Capitol Barbers. I was immediately greeted by Ken and given rockstar treatment. Very friendly and excellent customer service. Will definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kels Cao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiEbiqJPizRO8GROlpRDGdev1sWOTpNcvW5eWMQfxP2VLSoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I read a lot of good reviews on this barber shop, so I bought my husband here to get his haircut for the first time, since he likes to cut his own hair most of the time. Now I know why... The workers and atmosphere was nice and all, she did a pretty good job on his hair. BUT, after we left the shop, my husband told me that she gave him cuts on his skin and ear, which shocked me. (HE HAD 3 CUTS on the same side, and 1 cut on top of the ear.) I took pictures as well. He didn’t want to make a problem and was being nice, he knew if he told me there, I would’ve talked to them stating this was not ok at all. I trusted her with his hair since she said she had a long experience on cutting hair. I was very upset, still am! I would not go to this place ever again, sorry..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLh9-j7FanWCXX3uiNG9jxHUe6yjLmZIg4QhKPjyFNcMUHVxFEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice owners!! I can tell they are used to regulars and maybe mid-age to older clients. The place is a little hidden. The best way to get there is maybe park in the Sears parking lot and then crossing the street over the federal buildings.

If you are not a regular, Brings pictures and let them know what you want before they start snipping. It’s definitely worth an experience if you want to try them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mack Grimes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVX8ZPF4xGKslY7zvOCm68iaw8EI6v3hZ1or2xK3HUcO0CwsvGc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ken is the best. I was in & out in less than 30 minutes (as a morning walk-in) and couldn't be happier with the haircut and trim I got! He really takes care of his customers and the vintage barber atmosphere is cool.

He's had his shop in the basement of the State Office for 40+ years and has served on the board of the National Association of Barbers so he's been around awhile. He's genuine and friendly and seems to be on a first-name basis with half the Capitol! Sadly he's selling this shop to his son but for now he's still working Tues-Thurs so there's a chance you'll catch him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Brossart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoD2i-M1TwX-H4kL-RU6gX_FIEKQ7KyI-G1l9ObxInBkxm9NMhJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this barber shop exclusively for 6+ years.  The former owner, Ken, has conducted a smooth handoff to his son, Josh.  Both are models of the traditional barber.  They are engaging, friendly, professional and above all, give a great haircut at a great price.  Online scheduling is very easy.  Their ability to balance modern technology with traditional barbering makes Capitol Barbers worth a visit.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"John Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJX6M91AhiPOzG5Ce_u0rsXNXLW5GaSv4n8uFEj0-JkrVUVAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"He does a fantastic job and it looks just as good after my hair grows out. He is nice and fun to talk to as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie McLennan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyGXRrwWxL6vM72y5UQPGZhH_6X91FPI3M3S07lwkDWLKg2tUuBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've gone to Dan for years and am excited for him to have a space of his own! Great barber who has been doing this a long time. He always listens to what I'm asking for, and will ask clarifying questions or give suggestions to help me get what I want and ensure I leave feeling good. As a woman with short hair it can be a challenge finding a barber who collaborates and Dan has always been fantastic! Kind and welcoming, LGBTQ+ friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ian Dees","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkOEI2-uwVikG3VEtrFrDzapKIM5qQepmpYGq15xPe7QlbARDsdA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan has been cutting my hair for years. He's a great barber, and I look forward to chatting with him every time I visit. He's detail oriented: I've had the same cut every time, and he says \"are we doing the usual today?\" but he still confirms what it is every time. I appreciate that! It's great that he was able to move to his own space and I look forward to having Dan cut my hair for years to come!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connor Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfbq8hFemnJTV3DUQ8xQb4M3ps_sdxbzPPfWr6UxPDr5Rg3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I moved to Minnesota, I had to find a new barber. After 5 or so different people I found Dan at his old location in Como. I have been going to Dan regularly for 5+ years since then. He is an excellent barber that will cut your hair per your request. I have never had a bad cut from him.\n\nWhile a cut from Griff’s may be slightly more money than a generic Supercuts, it’s worth the extra money for the extra quality you get. You won’t regret getting a haircut here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chase Hoffius","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJftNMgbasxGLrwKPER1lIAs3MFLaY7RLmYCFmbs2JtTZ7-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan does a great job! His new space is nice too","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Dolan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvR3ufwIxG3fh5nsmyvbvKKOS5akN18HVSwS6jy12XxYLW4v-2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan is a solid, efficient barber that I’ve been coming to since I moved to the Twin Cities.  Also has a great soundtrack for his shop.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Peroutka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWa3crbzgddG4E_yG26qmxNU6xYWh0FC7-T9JkM3EcjrVPh4No=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan's an exceptional barber - perfect mid fades every time, 6 years and running. Great, down to earth dude. Can't recommend him highly enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen Rossetti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIme59IXU2Tuoa4q6H-47awGx2mUBGMTIJWXunGAER_4t2QM_i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great guy, great convo and great haircut! He didn't rush the haircut at all and spent time on the finishing touches. He even cleans up the neck area and eyebrows too. Fair price too!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Janay Downes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLV0nFdByJBIzz26E7fuKT1sHn182tOM0YRd8GNITwaY_LZLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited A1 Cuts Barbershop and I have to say, it’s an exceptional place! The atmosphere is welcoming and stylish, making every visit a pleasure. The barbers are highly skilled and take great care in their craft. They listen carefully to your preferences and deliver exactly what you ask for, all while offering helpful tips for maintenance. I walked out feeling refreshed and confident with a top-notch haircut. The attention to detail, friendly service, and overall professionalism make this barbershop a true gem in the community. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelunda Moore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpYVIMVdsYFk8gAYOO4UB2sinBU2oNWuUWJC8Us8GojhKqXjRc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A1 Cuts Barbershop exemplifies what it means to provide supreme service in a professional setting. From the moment you step inside, you are greeted by an ambiance that seamlessly blends comfort and sophistication, creating a quality environment that immediately puts you at ease. The barbers are not only skilled but are dedicated to their craft; their professionalism is evident in every interaction. They are attentive listeners, ensuring that they understand exactly what each customer desires before the scissors even touch the hair.

One of the standout features of A1 Cuts is their commitment to punctuality. Appointments are honored to the minute, eliminating frustrating wait times that are all too common in many barbershops. This efficiency allows customers to be in and out swiftly, which is particularly advantageous for those with busy schedules. The barbers' precision and expertise ensure that the results speak for themselves—everyone leaves looking sharp and well-groomed.

Overall, A1 Cuts Barbershop offers an exceptional experience that combines quality service with professional skill. Whether you’re a regular or a first-time visitor, you can trust that your time and investment will yield a phenomenal haircut in a welcoming environment. Highly recommended for anyone in search of a top-notch grooming experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rayshawn Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_nUvg_DO7UC7NsQS81w-1kqi_8B7Vd2dgWrBma1qB2PQ5qDnvgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to this barbershop for I believe over 8 years now and received an excellent hair cut every time. What’s lovely is that it’s not just the haircut it’s also the conversation, the cleanliness of the shop, the team that’s here. Love the consistency of effort and determination.I stared coming here when I would get a fade, by the same barber. And now that I have locs I still come see the same barber! She’s amazing at what she does! And the environment and neighborhood of the shop is amazing because it’s my born city!
I won't get a haircut/lineup anywhere else now except here. (Unless I am traveling lol) Thank you for making a wonderful hair cut experience well worth the price. Thanks Love!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shacara Hunt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsQhOM7DLwY9zqtmInYy_Od-ukeBl8pvftT24jrtvnSgl0dA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visit A1Cuts for your haircut, eyebrows, waxing and facials needs‼️ Wonderful atmosphere, clean shop, wonderful customer service, good vibes and good people‼️ The owner is a wonderful lady and does fabulous work! Please disregard the one star reviews.. they are all false because the owner next door wants to purposely sabotage this business because they are a solid establishment. If you want quality haircuts, waxing and grooming packages.. A1Cuts is the place to be! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bre W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQLWrLOAjvrdbRUB9IIsblOxgFbhcxM2r-LCwMwBxW77VqyCM2cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming here since 2018 and I don’t plan on going to any other barbershop. I was specifically looking for a woman barber & I found A1 Cuts on Facebook. After booking my appointment I met Madie & she’s the only person that I’ll let cut my hair. She did my undercuts back when I wore braids & now she cuts my hair completely bald as I have alopecia. She’s always honest & transparent with her clients about haircuts, styles & designs. She also uses the “TheCut” app which makes it easier to book/reschedule/cancel appointments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashly M (Ashalee Da Brat)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB2bKNrP_Tkz4_EJJpSdWMdTq5G-xO6YT-BnYk7GuD_VkE02B7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son and my brother see Imade and lemme tell you, She can make ANYBODY look amazing!! They're booking process is flawless through the app, they're walk-ins are always welcome, they do discounted days for children's cuts and so on. I've even put my brother's next door neighbor onto her to get their 3year olds hair cut And they were so impressed with the affordability and the final look.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Austin Marlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnBNEq4LQ_Hv72osEjkKz5CAyzSZEr8x1C79l1uy5Ir6eNGIl0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing service always a great conversation. Any questions I might have about my hair I can always ask haircuts are always done in a timely fashion great with kids if your even thinking about going just go you will not be disappointed much better then the barber shop down the street that lady can't cut to save her life","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DJ Slumpa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSeyIXRqgFJ5NJ5Ty0ocJDoIanN16lw6dJxRdXLB0KML4MgAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great shop. Madie has been cutting my hair for 15+ years and I wouldn’t have it any other way. Super professional and always punctual.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Angela Hohmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJrrT2xyzx8sdZYNJBeWLVIm2o3KRcWzdDzed1SEPygL8_zKv7Tg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Pete at Southside!! He’s been cutting my son’s hair for a couple years and he always leaves happy with his haircuts. Pete is so friendly and the whole shop has a great vibe. Can’t recommend enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dane Neidich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHdt6GSR1oCkh-VDqx7ZDW4xzPHSo8KRmhi5cazm0akkUs8RYb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently came in for the first time after following Lida from another shop. She is new to this location, so make sure to get an appointment before her schedule fills up!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grant Glad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKcqvO66WMB1qn44SO6ZZ9HPGvfRegp_h6LgKdMppHgoQtAjM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best barber shop in town hands down. I don’t live in Minneapolis anymore, as I’ve moved to Duluth, but I made it a point to make the trip back here to get my haircut before my wedding.
