user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jacob Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmpagKYm7JT99gGuA8ieEDKPC1gNkomAEPzPhMhg8jWq86wN4_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"💈Grandview💈 was what I have been searching 🔎 for and more!

Sadly, I've been to too many barbershops that play music 🎼 with lots of swearing/cursing, as well as, talk about unprofessional topics (that can't even be mentioned in a Google review) in front of their clients! 🤢 How unprofessional! 🙅

I am thankful that Grandview is not one of those places! 🙏🙌🎉

There was some smooth and classy jazz music 🎹 playing and I even received some great suggestions for parks 🌲 to take my family to. This is the kind of business I want to support with my time and 💰: Classy, professional, and family focused!

As to the hair cut and beard trim service 🧔. My wife said, (and I quote) "This is the best hair cut and beard trim you have ever gotten!" 😯What an amazingly high compliment!

As someone who moved to the area recently, I am thankful to find a barbershop 💈 that far exceeds 5 Star 🌟 service! This was truly a 10+ star experience all the way from start to finish!
🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theo Guerra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3MqbAK3Rr8l56DmD0LiDDmtFa4oWmRlfd9W2BAajzsh_glcCr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I usually jump around barbershops since I tend to book last minute, but I left my appointment yesterday knowing I found my regular barber. Jacob cleaned me up with the freshest fade I've had in awhile. I'll be rebooking with him for sure. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connor S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPhjTNh9BOZ2sVZQYWv_VXMTikuHxL7nqXkr8vwaHVvAaEdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jacob was extremely professional and easy to talk to. He was the first barber I’ve ever had to work with me to figure out the exact cut that I wanted, and I’ve never been happier with my haircut.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anthony Hietala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJL8VRuTiToL6Xhk9LjjeIUbIKfBhu7NQCVCdc9q9qiEcHxxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every time I get my haircut here I end up feeling and looking much better. Jacob cuts my hair so good that I tell my Family and friends that he should cut hair for the Present as well as Kings and Queens. We both always have a great time talking about music, food and tons more. The price is right and I've never had a better haircut. Stop by and get your haircut here I promise you won't be sorry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin D'Heilly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtCz-pd9lThvzv_ni6KrcF0Zl8UYWouQam5ydL0PAkPBvNGLXn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at the barber shop with Jacob. He greeted me and made me feel at ease while crafting an impressive haircut. His conversation made the visit enjoyable. I left looking great and feeling rejuvenated—highly recommend Jacob!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrmAGHY0A3uMVX5tXsexcCR780uiBuFOH5M3QFI0iLPt55Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one great Barbershop! I first started going here in 2011, when I lived in that area. You will not get a better haircut anywhere in the state of Minnesota like they do at Grandview!  I have now come back, even though I don't live in this area anymore! I am very happy with their services & you will be too!

There are two gentlemen that work here & I think they own the shop as well,but I am not sure.  The person who cuts my hair is Jacob & the other goes by the name of Gib. They both know how to cut hair extremely well. Gib is a former bodybuilder & for an older gentleman he looks much younger. Jacob is the one that cuts my hair & he gets a PhD from me in the knowledge of his craft.

Let me tell you how  my haircut went. Jacob takes his time in assessing your hair & how he is going to cut & finish your hair so you can look great! There is no place  like this shop to be found.  Jacob follows the growth, style & structure of your hair & then proceeds. Even my hair that grows on my ears he cuts away because he knows it's a nuisance. He shaved off my two  weeks worth of stubble and it was done so well. His knowledge of his craft is one of a kind. Once you become a customer you will want to come back & become a regular. Gib is excellent as well!

So give them a call and make an appointment. I think they take walk-ins as well but give them a call to find out. It is a very small Barbershop. It is extremely clean with off-street parking near Fairview & Grand in the Mac-Grove area of St Paul. I didn't take any photos because the photos they have on their site are sufficient.  If you want to look good for your significant other or your employer then this is your place. I have had my haircut done in many cities, but Grandview Barber Shop is a complete winner🏆!!! ( I don't know what other services they offer. What I get done at this shop is a haircut and beard trim.It is always a good idea to give them a call to see what other services are available.) This shop  is what Minnesota nice is all about! Great People & service.  Grandview has very reasonable prices!!!👍👌Highly recommend!!⭐⭐⭐","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wu Yansong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEULHfUnBqoWKDc-TCPKdl-HkcxU6jqgV9WPoFbG1mXN7TF_k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jacob was really chill and friendly, the vibes were peaceful and the haircut was nothing short of masterful. My hair turned out exactly like my reference pic. You would be in good hands coming here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Audrey Kludtke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdaHfjtjoTrNb0MY0HdVc_Mbhv9x5-w3Bvz1mzq-2WfV9MxoZE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don’t forget to make an appointment before enter the door. I thought I want to support some local business. This place it is!  The place have two chairs with only two barbers. They are very loyal with the hair and did the details really good.  I live near by and thought why not check it out. 19 dollars for normal cut which it’s good deal for experienced barber. Go and check it out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3Fnz-Aa-3TnpSbXAcOQYxM1R6gxM70iFKAGFc&fid=0x0:0xcf2fed5a9442573f"],"When":"2019-8-5"}]

I’m normally afraid of getting my hair cut because I’ve had past stylist cut my hair way to short.

Karina was my stylist. She was very thorough with my haircut and dying process. With having 5+ years of experience, It made me more confident in trusting her with my hair. What I really like about Karina was that she was passionate, patient and dedicated to making you hair look and feel flawless.

I’m screaming because I’ve never been SO excited so show off my hair before. Oh.... and during the process I took a few pictures for y’all to see my 5 hours hair transformation. I am extremely satisfied & happy with how it turned out. Definitely coming here next time! Thank you Karina!!!

☀️DIFFERENT LIGHTING ☀️
All of these photos were being taken with different lighting. There are some indoor photos, outdoor and direct sunlight photos. None of these photos were photoshopped for the soul purpose of true results.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjp-7iW6muD36lf-08_4ZQZikWkTkrBN2TEQ8-&fid=0x0:0x6193ff8a8511cc3a"],"When":"2021-8-4"},{"Name":"Janie X","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLsnvMhNHiveNuGIIiDAyU-KIo8ki9y32cfxVI5iUa5L4f5dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going here on and off for 3 years because sometimes Karina does not have availability for my impulsiveness and I have regretted it every time I see someone else. This shop is always clean, he is punctual about his appointments which is nice. Make sure you book online ahead of time and get you a spot because if not you’ll miss out and that’s on you.

Good talks and he doesn’t put up with crap from rude people which is what I like the most. This is the real place and if you anywhere in St. Paul metro this is the spot.

I’ll keep coming here until this place isn’t here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dustin groth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxPZMsUgJwTNt31-Kp-Zcc62sKpS6G0ySDZDR1I8HUAw81GA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there today on my lunch to get a beard trim. I just wanted them to blend it more. I think the guy had a personal vendetta against me I mean it doesn’t even look like he tried. He shaved off my entire back of my head baby bottom smoooth! I just asked for a fade :( I’m not sure why I got targeted but I’m white they are all African American maybe that’s it idk but it’s my hair man that’s not kewl. Never will again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laye CM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCgIVY8DEtUt1jSFYeKDe37f69gsRRoS1-rbF-J2EB6cphDEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First of all, this place is not recommended unless you are of lighter skin color. I went there yesterday 08/28/2024 around 5 with my nephew to just get a fade up. When we entered the shot 2 Latinos were waiting to get cut and there were only 2 Barber available and they were cutting hair at the time. Once they were done with those 2, they called the 2 Latinos * they normally do appointments or just sign your name and wait to be called* after cutting those 2 Latinos it was me and my nephew left, but I noticed the other barber left unnoticed, and the other guy was black skinny about 6 feet tall, instead of alerting us that they either wanna close and go or do not wanna server us they made us sit and wait for more than 40 minutes just to find out the guy can't cut hair or have no clue what tool to use to shape up the kid hair, waste my time, was my money and messed up the kid hair line, and after all he have the guts to tell me he can't do 2 hairstyles because the camera is watching him🤔🫨 I noticed something about Minneapolis, people here are either awkward or not use too socialize. I wish I could post the kid photo to justify my point but since the Internet is a sick place and privacy is dignity I can disrespect his dignity to just prove that ignorant can't cut hair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kairav Kukkala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_6VR6Ig8uHPI2SabWSoE3tsSeJx6-Rok7NSf7vFa9S_E2Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just got a haircut from Jay and he did an amazing job. He did the hair how I asked but also gave me more insight of how it would look and made sure I was on board with how he was cutting it. He gave great suggestions on what would look good and the actual haircut itself was very smooth. Very friendly and I was very happy with the haircut, will be coming back again soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maxwell Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCOVfrliE_5xTQq-sOUoyPWZbeAIILz_RcRlzKOnTdAPtbnuZN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going here for 5 years. I started getting haircuts from Ammar 6 months ago, and make sure to choose him every time now. He (like everyone else) is always punctual. He also is willing to give detailed recommendations - I changed how I get my sides cut on his advice and am liking it a lot more.

There is a recent negative review on here about him that I feel is incorrect. It is about a day where the power went out on the barbershop’s block and appointments had to be canceled. I had an appointment that same day, that also had to be postponed due to the power outage.

Ammar called me over an hour before my appointment to let me know the situation, and even offered to return to the shop late that evening once the city had fixed it. His communication around this unavoidable cancellation was quick, clear, and well-done. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charamea Pollock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw-6HnSIPdrKwbPY7g-ZbtvquVAAgbxbgoGd_VIJaESKKJpG5KeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yo! I just read KD’s bio & knew he could cut! It was my first time going to him and I’m in love 🫶🏼

Every time my haircut is consistent. The style is consistent. The timing is consistent. It's very nice looking. Dubai does a phenomenal job each and every time. I couldn't ask for a better Barber. Dubai is the best barber i've ever had. I would recommend This barbershop to anybody worldwide. Great Job!!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jesse Olson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtg6KNAFDu2Rma1pXaPeRrMleus9Ehd-NLAnGbFDiHe2TXvKaM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Peter is the owner who cut my hair.  Great experience!

He told me, this is his 2nd career.  He made a change 6 years ago because he had a childhood sense he would love barbering.

Peter made a great decision!  His passion and love for his work blessed me today😁😎😁

Plus the shop is old school meets today.  I left thinking… Its great to be a guy🤓😃😃😃🤩","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8IOhSDPoHn8GXVHHJn1Dy85IqStG2vsfSLfPm&fid=0x0:0xf5d5953ea3f6d80f"],"When":"2023-2-28"},{"Name":"William Hoeschler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPNOYa0uhheKyar82F1RS9WmrEfYCGP9jjelO2an264K8ppknB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place rocks! JP was excellent: kind, easy to talk to, detailed, and communicated with me throughout the entire cut. Barbershop is clean and classy. Nice waiting area, cool art on the walls, complimentary coffee and chocolates. Definitely will be coming back. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tyler B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIGtEOY762PRd_UUnJojAmbhSYlh5sANOmoO-gjAUJzKSuGekq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was visiting the Twin Cities on a trip back home with my partner and we both needed haircuts, so I did a quick search and found Pete and his crew at Tsar Barber. It was a quick and easy reservation process, and it’s a wonderful location to arrive early to or explore after your visit.

This barber shop is incredibly clean, comfortably decorated (with a variety of very cool barber collectible items on display), and the staff made us feel very welcome. Pete was very efficient with my haircut and we had a very pleasant conversation throughout. I walked away with an excellent haircut, a comfortable experience, and a new MSP barber. Please, give them a try and see for yourself.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Salim Kherbaoui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKyOQkIIONH5hufKhAk2v-5N23lOgxyCL1a3L6vpHZgeiYCqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience here! It was my first time but definitely not my last. Pete is very passionate of his craft and took time to explain his method and vision for my haircut. Great haircut and conversation about his career and life. The environment was very relaxing with lots of little touches that show the rich history of the barber industry","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luc G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpAq6xDqfZK4iP8JgYe62C0edHe34EDnNiBgWx-o8KvwYy7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here a few times now and will continue coming back! I have been bouncing around several local boutique men’s barbershops/salons spending $10+ more for cuts that were usually pretty good but inconsistent.

I have gotten a very good cut and a quality fade (a good fade is hard to find) each time I’ve been here. The owner is a great guy and always makes you feel welcome and appreciated. Online scheduling system is simple.

You may struggle to find this spot based on your GPs directions. It’s at the back and center of the strip mall. It’s easier to park in the back parking lot and enter right there rather than park in the lot facing the front of the mall along highland parkway.

Tell your friends!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Widder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJF2QAGHyQTfhylctJIS20-S4YbEPp0hjqaEN87JARy_brYVcM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pete is exceptional! Fast, clean, interesting guy. He teaches at the barber school so you're getting an expert cut at fair price. Go to barber!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samh a","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjEqRgkwtjBoZ6jiao2lMkefo--cTc97g-9F3CfAcwYkbnMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly professional both in service and in result. Would recommend to anyone looking for their style of haircuts!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Owen Dotson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3mWHOiXmrGx-N1G7bv7JO_d9TztkqMa7wyQT9pQwioc2F-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I could leave 6 stars, I would. After my first ever haircut with Peter, he got me hooked. He is very professional and gave me the best fade I've ever had as well as a traditional straight razor shave (which I highly recommend). I also thoroughly enjoyed our conversation about the roots and inspiration for the Tsar Barber. Pete knows what he is doing and is damn good at it. I can guarantee you will NOT find a better barber at this price. I will definitely be back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Aaron was awesome—so attentive, and I really felt like I was being pampered! I spoke a little bit of Spanish and I was able to make some conversation and jokes with the people there. Lovely service and man, just really stellar work. Thanks, Aaron. 👊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7DUe_WhbSP25CMyOkyJTdo0S4pfE2VCrimj83KiAJD1DykPk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Booked online with Cortez and could not have been more pleased with the service. The stylist used methods I have never seen. The price leaves a lot of room in your budget to tip your stylist…and believe me they deserve it. I don’t think I can ever accept anything less than what these guys offer. I found Bill to be hard working man with a dedication to his work and his faith. The shops atmosphere was most enjoyable with good and wholesome conversations. David, Tanya, and Deyonte","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tisha Sherdan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMwmijaed4ZDiy9gOJe_9ZMcjBkJTmmsVTlGU5MOBsjftQxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bill, the owner of the barber shop, was very professional and did and excellent job on my eight year old son’s hair. Overall, I had a wonderful experience and would highly recommend this salon to anyone looking for a high-quality hair cut.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wordsmiths - Collective","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5ShqOR7xz37-2JH1np0d3w6gl9lrdqAkJJrD1dvH9cwQUGXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Called for a walk-in whoever was on the phone said they could take me, I asked how much the haircut would be they said $40. When I get there noone says hey, they're all joking and laughing and I was waiting for about 20 minutes before asking them "Hey are you guys The barbers?"

One of them responds so I ask him when I can get my hair cut, he asks if I'm reserved or walk in , I say walk in and he proceeds to tell me that they can't take me as a client... none of em, not even the one who called me...... keep in mind they're all joking and one dude is sweeping.....

Unprofessional. If you want to walk-in to a barber, please go to the MOA not here...","Images":null,"When":""}]

I have been through so many stylists over the years and eventually started going very long periods of time without getting a trim or cut simply because I usually left feeling worse than when I walked in. Would absolutely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mickey marigold","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbhipc__kLv4_-VoQaHWzGX_JYjcQ3kvmoZ-v6ZV5ZBrx-fW9R=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst haircut I’ve literally ever had. Super choppy, extremely sloppy, my sideburns are insanely uneven, extremely weak/lazy incompetent hair washing.
The place is filthy, didn’t hardly clean up after the person before me, very unsanitary.
Bathroom was like out of a punk rock party house— nightmare.
Seems more geared towards white middle class men, not a place that knows how to do Black hair.
The forced small talk was awful, please read the room, some people can’t do small talk (because it’s awful torturous waste of time/energy). Some people’s lives are not small talk-able, and trying to push it really sucks.

Really bad experience, still tipped well, but im really really regretting going there.
Im sorry for seeming so harsh but it’s the truth, it seemed like you didn’t actually try, or were trying to make my haircut and experience as poop as possible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Bowen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtD9EkqGHOvUGQ0n0epaCF-vcVo62q0x-IIzpK53ktLz3N4Npf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the place to go! user_reviews: [{"Name":"Hunter Dvorsak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdf9iEmhDw0VRUlo5CKXH1nwnb49qH1CvqdsqiB5PCbR8xqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Nice fella but good lord he cut mine short asf and didn’t ask questions abt what he should do, also the cut was 40, told me 45 when he only did hair so that’s lowkey wild asl, unsure if anyone there cuts white hair could be really good if u don’t have straight hair","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Isaac Arli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmcxMXq1PG0_hpY_f6dSq3DIXbUQKRyRm7sv0LCTe9NV_vQHB8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The photo with the long hair is what I asked for, the one with the short hair is what I got. He did pretty good on the sides, and spent good time on it but oh my goodness the top. I don't understand how the barber thought to cut like 90% of my hair after seeing that photo with the long hair. And I couldn't even see how short he was cutting cause I'm facing away from the mirror. I probably should've been more specific but I'm pretty sure seeing that picture is pretty straightforward enough. I only get to see a small mirror at the end and I didn't feel like complaining cause the damage had already been done. He didn't even check how much I wanted the top to be cut or made sure. I spent like 4 months growing out my hair just for it to be gone in 20minutes without me even knowing. And also, $30 is such a rip-off.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOI8H8dPZdniInZdGU1TD0Igp9lIhLlKIaFFPao\u0026fid=0x0:0xe3b90f86d8f3e5d8"],"When":"2021-9-1"},{"Name":"Ebasa Girma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURcCdCMtfN9CCPTmup1hjm-_gMe9D8vSqhnpXlW5Enm7Hp8U1P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is the worst barbershop! I called for an appointment and they told me they'll do walk in. I sat for an hour and I was literally seeing the barber calling 3 people ahead of me. The way the Barber treat and acts are not welcoming and it looks to me that they're doing me a favor for their service. My experience with them was awful and I won't recommend anyone to use their service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyle Solom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE8QfNsoRU6MfM4-CSCo17toAjiliwwfyuinG9hvku8vIHqvnO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great cut - Calvin does a great job. Best cut in MN I’ve had. He takes his time and blends well. I will be returning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOosznpFK8CUwe_01tU0ESF9ZDJTIdLPG5Awqzo\u0026fid=0x0:0xe3b90f86d8f3e5d8"],"When":"2020-12-18"},{"Name":"Paul Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBFRLsYmhg7xWxL07_IN95YyCnHbP3se4_AFyKJpsTbcKig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to this barber for a while and I have always had a great experience. They're super chill and always have a good vibe. I always bring my friends here if they ever need a haircut!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wyatt Fairbanks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-ov8deMc6Y8xgJXMuhg6I-SpGcFSrprQ7mNXIpIEtEdAvrSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Walked in not sure what to expect. I’ve cut my own hair for the past four years, with mixed results. Honestly, I wasn’t really sure what I wanted. Calvin was immediately able to help me out and in no time at all, everything was cut clean, and I walked out feeling and looking good. Fantastic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hawk Bjork","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpfdej6VKrpz74zfY6D0zu4B1wZgCwdnA17qrhtAN6nf5u7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Calvin is good at what he does. He did everything I told him to do and made it look well, even though my cut wasn't what I thought it would turn out to be. I didn't get my \"best\" cut, but Calvin made me feel better afterward. Since Calvin told me what I should do for a \"better\" cut next time, I'll be back for an updated cut.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garrett Brower","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSWvHpIwmr-M-vgM_Sdsv6wEol6Bi2Z4-Dxd7nQEjZE7S2BA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible haircut, and expensive. Came for a walk in at 12:30, wasn't out of there till after 1:30, albeit with an awful haircut for $45. Asked for a 3 on top, and a 1 on the side, came out with a buzz cut the same length everywhere. Probably would have been able to have a better haircut if cutting it myself. Not to mention the unprofessionalism of the barber; talking about drug use, chatting with buddy instead of focusing on haircut, etc. Do not go to K Signature in Dinkytown if looking for even a decent haircut at a fair price.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I was nervous going into the appointment, but Calvin was so comforting and he really made me feel confident. I always have a hard time articulating what I want, but Calvin worked with me, read my vibe, and gave me the exact haircut I had been dreaming of. Book your appointment now!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kirsten Dalrymple","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWMbhSGm1sFmg3bDKcXJ4cBa4A9K9sWUWtaLu4vd8Ms0lPkxqN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great experience! Even without the keratin treatment it is the best cut I have had in a long time. I went from looking like a tired, busy mom to a classy trend setter in the blink of an eye! Salon is nice, chic, and professional. I tried this salon because of a Groupon I found (so glad I found it)
I felt very welcomed and comfortable at this salon. It’s not the fanciest salon but I like that because it feels intimate/comfy. Also huge plus for the big parking lot in-front 👍
The staff were very kind, my stylist was professional and talented, and I honestly don’t have any complaints. I would definitely come here again and will tell my mom to try Accolades!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPi878xg8rWXTDv4P9sPOXuXr3mV4kTm7ftpkVU&fid=0x0:0x1c99d923818a2222"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Christine Meyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIs4qtY6MzyDHtgSijN21F_EjPclC6pdw_AvOncqPdhnsdV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So I brought my teen daughter in to Laura Nova for highlights. She was so happy and lived it.  I asked her to write a review this is her review:

"My hair review:

I have to give a ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️, Nova did an amazing job, she was very friendly, very careful (and mindful of the hair dye color) she did her best to make sure she didn't get the dye on me/my clothes. She was careful with not messing up my eye makeup,or accidentally grabbing my earrings (i was wearing hoops at the time). And for the hair, she did amazing! She did exactly what I was hoping for, and I was very pleased with the results. I would like to  go back to get it done again for a lighter color, but so far, I love how she did!"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Urban Refurbisher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNNySNC1WyUdz5axN2gPoZ3Fqo2cjhmnqPq0-yiEtns8t-fg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nova did a beautiful job on my hair color. I’ve had the full spectrum of reds in my hair over the years, but the one she did may have been the most perfect one ever for my skin tone. A beautiful chestnut. Even the highlights were well located and toned perfectly.  Loved it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lilly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8NuOZDqSdA90NFlQ4oKOwhEg8b5iF5wKMc-t_P1n97CRJlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Laura Nova for a little over a year now and she does a fantastic job with my blonde hair every time! Whether it’s making it brighter for the summer or toning it for the fall/winter, I always leave feeling my best! 11/10 would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nancy ellis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGg7MRkC-74mxFwenpkF0AyKwhPpAgqZPhNGkk9rVZ3JiZAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It took me 5 years to find a hair stylist and my search is finally over! Sam is amazing, patient, took the time to talk to me and looked at photos of my prior hair cuts. Bonus: mini facial with my shampoo.
Love everything about this salon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Franklin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ-DGxzGqG87m5u4UAghq4OsmGmnwNv4KUPZKZAaTpvc8D53t-0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience at Accolades with Nova, the best I have felt at a salon in a very long time! I booked my appointment a little incorrectly and she was happy to accommodate me and take all the time my appointment needed. She explained things really well throughout the process and made me feel comfortable. The hair cut was perfection and she made sure of it! I am so glad I got scheduled with Nova and I am so happy to have found someone who can cut my hair exactly how I love it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ELLI KLAUDA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyz0N1lR9KVDXAcicQo7sK71UBAW3N4wg9ZrvYhW_yL_shJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ani is the absolute best! They were so helpful and creative during my consultation and we decided to do a root shadow and gloss along with some baby lights, which perfectly blended my color for a natural, dimensional look. Ani is not only talented and hilarious, but also attentive and made sure I was comfortable throughout the whole process. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Kirsten Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJieYaRG-h9b3cjRT-4lfZu11vtv1ebtSEu4jNJIh9216Hitg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've gotten my hair cuts here for years and have had reliably good cuts, friendly kind and helpful stylists and excellent customer service from the host every time. They offer tea and a nice sitting area. Their prices cover a spectrum and you can ask when making the appointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuMPpcMZdI61bzXIjktQpF-GL6KqTsv1oZHT08bALg7JfyZOE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I get my hair cut here regularly by Mandy. They always provide a great experience, have great prices, and have amazing customer service!

After having my hair cut at so many places that messed it up/didn’t do what I wanted, I found Moxie and Mandy and have been going here ever since!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mar Boh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICTjDQzVJdVMitoP13CtnVfe8StkEZ7ihGkweDMD4ZIZtl2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went to Moxie Hair in St. Paul after calling several times —for what I hoped would be a professional curly haircut, but instead, I left with one of the worst salon experiences of my life. Despite repeatedly asking for a stylist experienced with textured hair, I was assured that Jenna had the skills needed that she has been with Moxie for 12 years. That couldn’t have been further from the truth.

From the start, basic steps for curly hair—like properly detangling before cutting—were ignored. Instead, Jenna cut my hair while it was still tangled, resulting in uneven layers, a ruined curl pattern, and a much shorter length than I requested. To make matters worse, my hair was used as a teaching tool for an intern without my consent. I had to detangle and comb my own hair during the appointment— while an unbelievable frustrating experience at a supposedly professional salon.

The worst part? This wasn’t just about Jenna’s lack of training, but the blatant dishonesty from the booking team and management. I was told to contact Betsy manager who was worst manager! Never responded then when I emailed the owners she sent a dismissive response telling me basically that it was my fault because my hair supposedly is not what they do! Clearly discriminatory so only go if you have Caucasian hair they clearly don’t train or serve people of color! Their promises of diversity and expertise are nothing but a façade.

If you have textured hair, stay far away from Moxie Hair. They are not equipped, trained, or honest about their capabilities. Don’t make the same mistake I did which took me months and over $300 to correct what they messed up!  This salon needs serious training and transparency if it ever hopes to cater to diverse clients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elena M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUA_zX1GfqWycwp__TCKC0vicvlZme-hfls5gu0PECSK07N0q9y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After my old stylist of 15 years moved away, I was hesitant to try a new salon and stylist. I can safely say I found my new spot and artist. Tianna has cut my hair twice now and every time I leave feeling amazing about my hair and myself. She makes me feel so comfortable and I’m so happy to found this salon. 10/10 would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Partridge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZhbH7Ficg3qpuAmnb27_MBOjrNZNf1t8WppVfo63eeWhWa2XEKA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got caught in a hair emergency where a product had singed off a good chunk of my hair I was growing out. Called around town and was lucky to serendipitously end up thankfully with an appointment at Moxie. Also, lucky to get paired with Tianna who was beyond comforting, down to earth, professional, kind, and reassured me that my issue could be remedied to allow for regrowth and gave me some tips as well moving forward. The salon itself is beautiful and the front desk gal was very friendly and awesome too. Honestly, would highly recommend and Tianna especially. Thank you so much 🩵","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rae Rodrigues","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpiymgYua0ep85qCGwuZd8Adj_uj6INXVt5Sgf6zXIBlOMdsB9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brendt did my hair and I’m so damn happy I could cry. He knows all about hair and was familiar with my Brazilian hair texture. After endless searching, I have found my stylist. Thank you so much","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN8CTIMeLfMhpVAG6HNdAU_xaYQ6ouraulZ8MO&fid=0x0:0x1df750a5f51e2df0"],"When":"2025-2-18"},{"Name":"Sara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwNLbPn9HeINr7_EEJNoblDAHebNk-cuKtSU5bJWwFO50Aq2re=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to Moxie to get my hair washed and styled after a mastectomy. Kelsey treated me with kindness and made me look like $1 million. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachael Meuwissen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUial8GV0vtngTxe0joonzbTL_nyWi8-2TWBTqO_7Re21AOxr53ZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great salon, awesome stylists! Torrey does a Fab job on my hair, while Jenna  does a wonderful job on my partners hair. Jenna also does some pretty sweet hair designs. Always a positive and wonderful experience at Moxie!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeaSOUG_g-YQls-dVBFFzaOwiVFhWIrRNr9AP5&fid=0x0:0x1df750a5f51e2df0"],"When":"2022-6-2"}]

[{"Name":"Laura Serier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5M8rTXQKAeWNggXmol_Kvo_Y4fypvQGzyu1jkwBf_DgPTAyop=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved working with Estetica for hair and makeup for my wedding. There was a private space for myself and my bridal party to keep our things while we got everything done, and the entire space was covered in rose petals when we arrived – it was beautiful! Everyone who got their hair and makeup done looked beautiful, and I had my hair done by Amelia and makeup done by Jo. Both of them were amazing to work with, and knew how to help guide me during my hair and makeup trials when I was feeling unsure. They helped me start my wedding day out the right way by helping me feel confident and beautiful on my big day!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6dowwuhCqUj4VxRn-9tpoENy7uTzela89TEBH&fid=0x0:0x6bf43eabcf0b9588"],"When":"2025-1-9"},{"Name":"kristi kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRcoZZulyOtARqKzlVQPpBWZ1tG8_nhJ9SZfZFtsSHviAyMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I Absolutely LOVE Estetica! Super cute vibe inside the salon and the Staff are amazing! I've been getting my hair done by Gina for years and literally wont go to anyone else in the cities. I like my blonde to be more of an icy white color, so she suggested a silver toner instead of the usual purple which i never would have thought to ask for, but OMG it looks fantastic and actually keeps my hair white between appointments! I get so many compliments on my hair now! Solid 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX90YKfwXKcLqOodeqR62_gumfH7_3actR5nXN&fid=0x0:0x6bf43eabcf0b9588"],"When":"2025-2-20"},{"Name":"Elizabeth Hoover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1rc8V5FkamfyQkqAW233bDn2ju680C2EtQPwyu1VNgg3nz9iPRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just received a 90 minute deep tissue massage with a foot reflexology add on from Shelby and all I can say is, wow!

Shelby is an incredibly skilled massage therapist. It was a thorough deep tissue massage for the full 90 minutes. She took good care to check in on pressure preferences here there and to make sure I was comfortable, but otherwise allowed me to drift off so blissfully. She honed in one all of my problem areas in my upper and low back, but also have plenty of attention to my arms, hands, legs, and feet. This massage was easily a 10/10. Will definitely be booking this service with her monthly!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sami Detourniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMisiW9wChBT_-bgGQ2gjlIVPGaJY2sqLhZNluigbuR_xXHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They do balayages so well and wonderfully and take care of you!!Francesca did my hair :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN9yFjgq2GNrC7I-12G40MKL8OgCPtxFIYSBRVE&fid=0x0:0x6bf43eabcf0b9588"],"When":"2025-1-3"},{"Name":"Kristina Oak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWh_zRCCeY5IHBsyRyDlDojxWxaEyGbxWmL4XFGOWHkO_Z3jS36Mg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every time Kajsa does my hair, I have a new favorite hair cut & color! They are so thoughtful, they remembered I have a sensitive spot on my scalp & took care to make sure I didn't have pain during the whole bleach/tone/styling appointment. I'd recommend them to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vanessa Hausman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRahPcRvENJTwih9OnEev4qHNTW5yS6CARawkV4HXgkqrrrD6jcA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't say enough about how wonderful Estetica was in a time of crisis. After receiving the worst hair cut of my life with fantastic sams, I knew a real salon was the only remedy. I was in shock (in the best way) after the stylists were able to save my hair! It was a group effort and during my time there they treated me like a queen. Recognizing how distressed I was, the stylist included a free scalp massage and was so incredibly sweet. I've found a new studio and will never again underestimate the value of salon professionals!!

See before and after pictures for proof 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvXZIzRwfFK1j6PhookuYWtJYVd7MR119_SSAD&fid=0x0:0x6bf43eabcf0b9588"],"When":"2022-12-27"},{"Name":"Laura Cap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOdS9C3MmGc5_ifxPgsniU8elpmJf83l1be_yTl24zWL0bJMEP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jasmine is the best! Always listens and gives expert feedback on colors, cuts and styles! She’s been my stylist for almost a year now, and I can always expect a superior service from her! Way to go!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffany F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbnOJiPJHcDIZv939uqTuSyTEbNqmK-elDBN8aGNzvW0i7hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Estetica for years, and haven’t ever thought about going anywhere else. I highly recommend anyone who is considering Estetica to try them out.

I’ve tried many of their skin services as well and those have all been great. Our entire wedding party went to Estetica, and they did a fantastic job.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Phyllis Beaudette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJyIKexF_TOs1XPEqTgoD4bP1LAtfddCGKbDZKJfZ5WBooUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very pleased with Lori.  She does a great job styling my hair and always has nice suggestions on something I might like. .. and she's never wrong.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Chavez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUL5bZV12y4lccOtk9voIttqE92i94fKpaW8uS4iuwuST5dxXlq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Angela is the best.\nI love the St. Paul location, even though I live in Minneapolis.  They do Not have the long vertical mirrors, showing your entire body!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mitch Runge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFHyCdzmHXoFYq4weU6WspDN5nwshgDr_PjX6Zw--B3paMXqkq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit to Petite Salon was exceptional, the staff up front were very helpful and I enjoyed a cup of coffee while I waited for my stylist. Noelle was super talented and did an awesome job cutting my below-shoulder-length hair in to a nice faux mullet/hawk, a much needed transformation! I had a partial foil done as well and the blonde turned out exactly as I'd imagined, all the while looking very natural and 'sunkissed'. I absolutely LOVE the Davines and Olaplex lines so I enjoyed shopping for product afterwards as well :) Overall very pleased and I'm looking forward to making this my regular salon going forward!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robin Edgerton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXevqXaVDglMNSKOt1GbAGkge5wTq3g9vVcbqvXv0wmWHR6q5lX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been getting my hair cut here for years. Have had several stylists over the years. All very good. Tony is my current stylist and is excellent. Competitive prices. Willing to work with my different short styles including adding  multiple colors. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Colette Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLazKfzJWceKDrNZ-cBil2sG6oNKAzY7SQQnip-UeyehPYCCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Petite Salon is exceptional in every way. I have had nothing but the best care for my hair at Petite. I have trusted them for over 15 years. Brandy and her team are always doing continued learning to better their art. They are the best in the industry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jane Stevenson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDXDiaUzE832-prV5mdxuD2LJLO3G2Ns86LkCzRXtstiA_jwO5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tony Wrich is so good I followed him to Petite Salon from his previous location in Woodbury, but the commute to see him is worth it to me. He's especially good with short, precise cuts, but also excellent with color.  He takes hair very seriously.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJhH1VaEnkwp22CKjBGVe2T3YknlmrTqnUHfgy\u0026fid=0x0:0x31ca29b71b1c9cf7"],"When":"2017-5-8"},{"Name":"Katherine Bock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlTp0q5yznVSYsJKp1cxnTKUHhJy2acAYxc3Fy8pwpTWWEuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Shocking treatment!  Hair stylist Tony cut my hair way too short knowing that was not what I wanted.  When I expressed my unhappiness, they told me to go somewhere else.   Very, very poor treatment and customer service.  He certainly was happy to take the nice cash tip.    Beware!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristen Aeikens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkdt01YF6tslqIQ0BTsMXvhpK0GFl_6sY83Pm3dsSp9Ec5u5ZdEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Petite Salon is an absolute gem. Talented, friendly, accommodating staff who are truly invested in the customer experience. High quality cuts, styles, and products - they're simply the best, and I can't recommend them enough!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Zola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWA00O67zDfStZT6GjzBZEOB5cRy3WCT8Pad83SrC6MfX9PoAs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My stylist Chelsea is fantastic at cutting/styling my hair and her  artistic talent shines when she colors my hair in blues and purple! I feel like a walking work of art when she's done and I get enthusiastic compliments on my creative hair color all day long. I spend a long time in the chair and the atmosphere is upbeat, laid back and very courteous. I really look forward to getting my hair done now!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPirVFphJaZq8AN8IOk1HheS9LopJObiz71-7wr\u0026fid=0x0:0x5098abb0364728c1"],"When":"2024-9-15"},{"Name":"HD M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtwU52c_wnoBdMq7cCx6cdmtw2Jv9cAhhpYRJKQ1EgrYNwTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Tease Salon and the expertise the stylists bring to transform winter dull hair to spicy, moisturized, voluminous hair!  I adore my new look that Mary created.  She heard my kooky description and I'm very pleased with the result!  Will definitely return!  You can't go wrong with the stylists at Tease.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"er gk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaa2rjWaMIBgtim4OFGoDMYpGPibY_icoa7lSXBwNibpOkPPwV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so glad I started coming here! I have been seeing Mary for the last year and a half and have always been happy with her work. She recently colored my hair just in time for my wedding and it looked amazing! She is also a warm and lovely person. I recently sent my mom her way and she told me she loved her experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Lautaret","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhLViurcgqD7VCuJx9etwGOqB4gYk3u5psn7wFWtMxEA5hCFA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent atmosphere, with a warm, relaxed vibe. The staff is amazing, especially for those who have disabilities. I am blind, and the staff is caring, respectful and does a very good job especially in regards to blindness etiquette. They also are very respectful of my service dog, and I love going to them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hurricane Mala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-T8pHGrEBeeDDoRSY8gmpY4WY2KEKzOwWgowEBj1x4H81xoY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lots of very happy loyal customers. I've been going here for years and talking to other customers in the lobby... they are always returning happy customers. The stylists are talented and able to provide consistent quality service. Amber is amazing! I still remember sitting in her chair for the first time. She could read my hair and tell what I had been already doing. I recommend this salon to everyone. I proudly tell all my coworkers, family and friends where and who I see. Love it! Love it! Love it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO407TMwp-jOtnCsiN8Sfh5KPX_yVnV8jSUt5R8\u0026fid=0x0:0x5098abb0364728c1"],"When":"2021-9-11"},{"Name":"Ashley Sipple","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsA50MJoZKu0hg6Mak08eZk28yxir1jmrRudTln2uXXuPdD-i8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This salon is perfect. From the atmosphere, to the products, talent, and pricing. My hair has found its new MN salon home. Shout out to my stylist Chelsea for getting me back to my icy blonde hair goals and taking her time to perfect it. ✨","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tsheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvSQRm_TSYDt2mDbg1KoTK3lNv37bEuyEXgpcAsfTOsExTcZnkig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was nervous about getting my hair cut, but Tease salon was a great experience. When I booked my appointment, the lady on the phone was incredibly nice and helpful. I had Mary cut and give my hair a gloss. My hair turned out better than I wanted and it was so soft I couldn’t stop touching it. Mary was the attentive, sweet and made great conversation. I totally recommend Mary if you’re nervous about getting your hair done!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfUC56ZhyxdqS7knpItxIoGUwlg1Ni4gUU0G0m\u0026fid=0x0:0x5098abb0364728c1"],"When":"2024-1-2"},{"Name":"Sarah Northrup","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc7cQ4PDlfACboCZv1e6bN6QUFJm5EXD_TQknN2L5R3E15NlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Tease for the past year now with Auri as my stylist- I can't say enough good things about my experience! I had my first balayage hair coloring done today. I was nervous at first, but Auri did an incredible job and walked me through the whole process and was very transparent about the cost. I highly recommend Auri, she's personable, fun, and has a great deal of expertise. Definitely would recommend if you're looking for a new hair salon in St. Paul!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6GTcuPNbYOH-fIrkvrcKfrBRIWbivp21gChKW\u0026fid=0x0:0x5098abb0364728c1"],"When":"2023-12-31"}]

Sam was so kind and not only listened to my hair concerns (very dry scalp) but also provided education about possible causes and how to care for my hair in the future. You can tell they really wanted me to be happy with the results. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emily Nelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV84HZyAknKCUvxX-jRWctb3rVkX1RcjZX-JqT7MQ5o9lYB8WwI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sarah Jo is awesome. So glad I found her to help shape my fine, curly hair at whatever length I'm contemplating at the moment. You'll love the process of working with her.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monica Shaffer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJK1g3xtAYrlCeXt7vpgo2emnh8OXOmVTbEAS1sjdJ3k9l4qA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love getting my haircut here. I want to give a shout out to one stylist, Sarah Jo! She is so friendly and special. I am a plus-size person and it is wonderful to have a hairstylist who understands that part of my identity, which means that we encounter the world, our bodies, and our hair differently. Seriously, she is amazing, highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lexie Haglund","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBYCms13F-OPtZTcm24easuEJp5NVgLWAOzO0B-blSPnW1vw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Madison L has done my hair multiple times so this review is overdue - 5 stars for overall results including hairstyling, cut and color everytime I come back it keeps getting better! Wish I had photos to upload !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SneaverMan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAf22z1u6vN1LQ8SwmNm3RLPE9MHy9NoMP8Yl77PwQzbduEXMH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have gotten about 5 haircuts from this place over the past year and it has changed my life— and that’s no exaggeration.

I started coming here with a head of messy, wavy hair; yet full of potential. After getting taken care of at Juut by Delaney and being given proper care instructions for my curly hair, suffice it so say my curls are living to their fullest potential. I used to be described colloquially as the “fashionable guy who does x” or “Latin guy from ——,” now I’m described as the “guy with the great hair” or “guy with gorgeous curly hair.” Older women are particularly taken with it. As a waiter, this has been of great value.

The experience at the actual salon is lovely, too. The vibe is very welcoming and comforting. There’s more than plenty of coffee and tea at one’s disposal if one so desires. Maybe some lights snacks or little chocolates would really bring it to the next level for those of us who get peckish at the salon. The location of the salon on the lively and cute Grand Ave is pleasant, too.

All in all, a top notch experience that has revitalized my appearance, confidence, and given me the healthiest hair I’ve ever had.

Thank you Juut, thank you Delaney.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alicia Leckas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5R83CQslHhO3tsr4nA0b_x0HjPGCH84Iy_f9gHyTrH2liqa99=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Damianna is so good at her craft. Instantly starting with a scent journey and shoulder rub. I am growing my fine hair out and she shaped  my hair perfectly. I will be back!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Dabbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuzcvhCdMQo49fpox5HldRFmhS_jjlDtjS1rrMGvD17Ko5b9nd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had Sam cut my hair before and have always been impressed with his attention to detail and professionalism. This time was the big cut.  I donated 10” and went for a mid length cut.  We talked through what I was looking for and what would be possible for my hair.   He executed the cut and style perfectly.  I have zero regrets and love the end result.   To top it off Aveda offers some amazing products to help style it for a fun naturally all day look.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhQf4Ie8SFrJInj08g9HRK3AwL3GqgO2EUgQFf&fid=0x0:0x42487893db843537"],"When":"2024-10-6"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Daniela Buvat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXo5e2mUtLenQc5-_O2HSkAYgYUN-futZnqj8OdT2aQQUXqg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 I love going to Hannah at Honeycomb. Hannah always makes sure getting my haircut is a fun and approachable experience and I leave feeling fabulous. She takes the time to listen to each client's specific needs and always delivers and exceptional finished product. She's truly an artist and amazing at what she does! Plus, the salon is buzzing with great, inviting energy. I also love swinging by Marigold next door to stock up on fun drinks! Cannot reccomend this south minneapolis staple enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKtzwlSFFvkGh7q65s32sEZQwiItehlZMr3JKtn2-0t3UQqBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Each time I have had an appointment at this salon, I have never left disappointed. I have always received an outstanding cut and/or color. The staff are fantastic at their craft and if the owner is present during your appointment time, you will likely receive extra hospitality and an entertaining conversation. I would suggest to plan ahead for appointments, they book up quick for obvious reasons\n\nMy last appointment was with Aileen, she was an absolute delight through the approximately 137 microfoils she gave me back in September 2022","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophie Schroeder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWK-T4WN5rI9hVe9rNYXSmE6Q0OUzyzYGg_ss6NsHynov3Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hannah gets a 10/10 every time ❤️ She always takes time to listen and makes sure we have the same vision. I have a long hair history and sometimes forget some things that may affect how color comes out but she has a lot of experience and is quick to make changes and fixes. She is also sooo fun and every time i get my hair done we blah blah for hours. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maureen Olson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0hf_3kBnbbEn37WvsLLpI4KJvGcVl14alm_9yLiq1c_8Ch2m_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this salon!  Aileen spends time figuring out what I want and what is best for my hair.  She even brings her colleagues into the discussion, which makes me feel very welcome and important.  The vibe is super friendly and welcoming, and the Marigold shop next door is awesome, too.  I highly highly recommend this salon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lindsey Goss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRsIHlEqg-1i_jUaFRJCx7WS5uN34jhc8JtgSZUu5gHaGWKyWR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So glad I found this place. Hannah is amazing and fixed a not-so-great job I had done at another location. She really listed to what I was hoping to get to, was clear about a path forward (ie- it not being a one-and-done fix, though even the first step looked so much better and I was and am still so happy with it!), and was just lovely to chat with while I was in the chair. The shop environment is so warm and welcoming, and definitely don't skip on checking out the attached bottle shop! 5/5, definitely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaylee Burnham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUuGTXSBqEu-TbXYBNWM87NKKpAcXJGJZ9t8RU3QqhNgrumB58p=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So glad I found Honeycomb! I found Amanda when I looked up stylists for curly hair in the Twin Cities, and she is incredibly talented and just a lovely person to be around. There’s no one I trust more with my curls! And everyone at Honeycomb has always been really kind. 10/10 would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Felt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX42FiW8QNMD0O9bCN3EBX71fYGRB6rk1e95MEkgLChfp9gyIxL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this salon and I love my stylist Amanda! She is great with curly/wavy hair types and is so nice and easy to talk to. The salon offers high quality hair products and cute accessories. If you are looking for a good salon, I highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ellie Alexander","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5GiPp0krBHwWnnCYo6QaaxK_7sZRrqq2UB2QcUJff-B-sRZYFYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had one of the best cut/colors of my life with Jenna! And the salon is beautiful!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWJJp9OuxIGaOERxtebb1DW1x3K6ZFcfwywlFR\u0026fid=0x0:0x322fd39848c90690"],"When":"2019-3-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Brea Lindsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK22sND4zJaiYHUxU7uPDY4M_W2s83XmjeJwrbHY_l9GoAmZA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time with a new stylist for a while! I usually cut my hair myself (I can be picky about who cuts my hair) I booked with Sam Rose and when I showed up she was unfortunately sick that day. Luckily Luci was willing to do my haircut! I felt like she really listened to what I said I wanted and referenced photos I showed her at the beginning through out the haircut. She did an amazing job on my hair and I found someone I’m happy to return to!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNE1m5_Lr02giR6w5pBxo2DdTNcDX11TmjBBEUX&fid=0x0:0x6af68bb7da555ee4"],"When":"2024-1-12"},{"Name":"Alicia Eisenschenk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhcWuJO3O3bYqFl1_jzQaAF-IJ1XE1lSGI4y-_cByHZquyicQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had the pleasure of knowing “new” Jessica for a few years now.  She gave me the most gorgeous updo for my wedding in 2021, and has been a part of my hair journey since then, including perms, red/purple hair, shaggy wavy cuts….all the things!  Not to mention she is bursting with energy and enthusiasm – it always lifts my spirits!   I followed her to MN NAF and we recently did a mermaid colored look.  She continues to kill it in every way and I’m so happy to support this business that cares about their staff, the community, and their clients!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWCMkSnVnI5Oi1jvI3vaQ_531W8Tk2BLeKviDb&fid=0x0:0x6af68bb7da555ee4"],"When":"2024-6-6"},{"Name":"Avita Samuels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXdUUUCMBe-DHAxbsYI0b9odFSrJgOGeyAexjo7GiBJ48gXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This salon and Jessica are for lack of better words, sheer perfection!!! Where do I even begin? Ok, maybe let’s start with the services provided. I do the following at MN NAF. Cut, color and extensions. I found this place (and Jessica) by complete accident. I was desperate and losing what little I had of my fine, thin and VERY curly hair due to the stress that comes from losing both of your parents at once. I needed to feel some dignity restored but didn’t know how. On our first meeting, Jessica reassured me that she knew how to fix everything! I was pessimistic because I had failed with many other stylists in the years prior, but Jessica also had naturally curly hair and I’d always wanted extensions anyways. She ordered the extensions, custom permed the hair and dyed my hair to perfectly blend with the Bellami weft and installed within a week. I am not kidding when I say I walked into work the next day and my coworkers were questioning had my hair been that long the whole time?!?! I see my coworkers every SINGLE day! Until Jessica, I had been told that I really couldn’t do extensions unless I was fine with straightening my hair every day and I was not. My hair looks fabulous and I am living the hair dreams that I have had since high school!!!!

Onto the other factor. Every stylist at this salon is absolutely wonderful. I spend A LOT of time here, extensions require move ups and reinstalls so you better like your stylist, and I honestly could hang out with everybody here!!! It’s a warm, welcoming, fun, women supporting women, environment. Come here and support this local female-owned business. You will leave feeling good about it, trust!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Timothy Farver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlxPB7tHkg8rQV4YH9hBERTise1-v-LRLuquhxG99LHS7Yfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stepping into MN NAF is like entering a sanctuary of refinement and artistry. The owner herself embodies professionalism and warmth, creating an atmosphere that is as inviting as it is sophisticated. The aesthetic of the space is nothing short of mesmerizing—each detail thoughtfully curated to elevate your experience beyond the ordinary.

For men navigating the realms of executive presence or polished business-casual looks, this salon is an absolute gem. The precision, artistry, and tailored approach to styling are unparalleled. My experience left me with a cut that not only complements my features but also aligns perfectly with the image of confidence and leadership I aim to project.

What truly sets this salon apart, however, is the owner’s intuitive understanding of her clients. She welcomes you with open arms and listens attentively to ensure the final result exceeds expectations. Her ability to transform vision into reality is nothing short of extraordinary.

For gentlemen in pursuit of a sophisticated, professional edge or anyone seeking an exceptional hair experience, this is the place to be. Thank you for an unforgettable experience—I look forward to returning for many more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPcBKHXF0EKJeCK1rJlfzE9jUI_T9nqo64KqVI&fid=0x0:0x6af68bb7da555ee4"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Katerina Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUjU0OoA8NdbUHcbp7aa8odcjJgdL5rdrj8JP1pvfN1hJ0t9iV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent experience! Siobahn did an awesome job with my cut color and style. She made me feel comfortable and got my vision spot on!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Shirreffs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwgg5gioCEnxY687jFRXA9OgWGXxlq_x1fGtLbmplR843n-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am Always nervous about getting my  long hair cut. Levi was awesome and he was very patient and reassuring. I couldn’t even use words to describe what I was looking for and he helped me figure it out. 10/10 recommend. Thank you!
P.s. my hair looks great","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah Moreno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJo6sx-ZceK_0lyveYZAorHqdgVA2jeqwGaLuyG1w0FBQtiBIH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I finally found my salon! It’s very homey and bohemian- not at all pretentious like salons tend to be.

Leslie is a lovely human. I enjoyed getting to know her, and i love what she did with my hair. I was needing a change and she helped me decide on a cut that can be styled when I want to look fancy but also actually works with my very low maintenance hair routine!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNON7aXVjy9InDRBnVgS07zNjqSDE_GgZnTDU43&fid=0x0:0x6af68bb7da555ee4"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Jemma Larson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHxB2onWigyWJ8ZZ4mqoIam5OrOHoTgEArdGfKZDLQ5G6BfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic! I am so beyond happy with my refreshed blonde hair for summer (june 2023). Kait is amazing, I always the most fun to get my hair done with her and feel like an absolute superstar. No matter what I want to get done (even an amazing pink balayage in feb 2023) it always turns out way better than I expect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM20JlPgwbGvUG7NprrYkPpBUYK-WFL4iLZxa0h&fid=0x0:0x6af68bb7da555ee4"],"When":"2023-6-12"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Molly Duncan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdFJFKXOU0B6NOSeSuobrAFM1-yvWQdv4p4o4Rk5u3FsS6ptO5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called ahead to see if they carried the Kevin Murphy hair product line and they did so I went in just to purchase product. One of the owners Jim spent at least 15 minutes with me explaining all the different products and  Jim even offered to order in one product they didn’t have in stock specifically for me.  Jim went above and beyond and I didn’t even have any services done that day just went to buy product. They have a VIP product card once you get 10 punches you can use it on your next product purchase and get 20% off And they’re not only a hair salon, they are a med spa and they have every service you could possibly think of for hair, permanent makeup, makeup lessons with a shopping trip, various facial treatments, Botox, last extension and tinting and application and a plethora of  other specialized hair, face and lash Services. I think I found my new salon!  Overall, my product purchasing experience was amazing and the receptionist that checked me out was great.  Overall, CaJah Salon Spa was welcoming and radiated positive vibes!  I would highly suggest you check it out.  $$$","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdtezIKH9_66UeaJ56WNnAP16CaTSjeAZnzhNG&fid=0x0:0x4d2fc8d655db7635"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Eleni Achrazoglou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI2cpTfmzJOuyCWfyfN-5HCfsbNR2JkLs2iyHLnzfd4i_qShHtFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got the most amazing haircut from Elizabeth last week! She had great banter and gave me an awesome massage during the shampoo. I have never seen my natural waves look this good and  I love how she gave me a cut that kept my length but took a lot of the weight out of it. So happy to have found my stylist in the cities :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX63-Uz1ZzKqb7bAoz6X9ISpM86-Ybx0Tn7mXaovdtUdFO82pA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son got a haircut and liked it. It was really quick. They had a parking lot and it was a very nice salon to wait in while it was happening. Ru did very well and we will be coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Keelin Nave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdsAq2psTvqco-ONT_Zq-LozZyHvB92KUaRLA1cnU9RwnIJeRfKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful time getting my haircut with Elizabeth C. She took my indecisive thought process and gave me a great haircut/balayage that suits my fine hair. Will definitely be going back to her!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmwOQATnh-_1LeADyjQfDXQZG-gwRlULuwJpiB&fid=0x0:0x4d2fc8d655db7635"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Joy Summers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW6YpRwPuY5BoEu6hEq9x2fqBeVkFEVY-RYfm36f_dQ71v5aLk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"1 out of 3 appointments ended in an actual haircut. Our first experience was great - my teen loved his haircut. Second - the salon was still closed from the move - why our appointement wasn't cancelled, no one knew. I had confirmed the appointment the day before. Third attempt, we came ahead of the scheduled time and sat for 45 min after the appointment before giving up. Again, no communication or apology for wasting our time. I'm happy to agree to the policy that we will pay the salon for tardiness or no showing, but as a customer, we weren't granted the same courtesy or any consideration.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jada Elizondo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVC8R34oa-DVLGoh0j1uYopNhFNrCSgtEmMKijmu5wyePaYoeIU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot recommend Jennifer Cassidy highly enough! She is truly a master of her craft and has transformed my hair every time I’ve sat in her chair. From her exceptional technical skills to her artistic eye, Jennifer always delivers stunning results that exceed my expectations.

Whether I’m looking for a bold color change, a precision haircut, or just a refresh, she listens carefully to my vision and brings it to life with expertise and care. What sets Jennifer apart is her ability to personalize every experience—she takes the time to understand what works for my lifestyle and face shape, making me feel confident and beautiful every single time.

Her attention to detail is second to none, and she always uses the highest quality products, ensuring my hair not only looks amazing but feels healthy too. Beyond her talent, Jennifer has such a warm and welcoming personality that makes every appointment feel like catching up with a friend.

If you’re looking for a hairstylist who is passionate, talented, and genuinely cares about her clients, look no further than Jennifer Cassidy. She’s an absolute gem, and I’m so grateful to have found her!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ronnie Gentiles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2pmaP6gfuz4DpeQYs2fvJM9yCMXZEpETHi483LklnvYHjhEFu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My partner and I have been getting our haircuts at Cajah Salon since late last year, and Jules has been our go-to hairstylist from the start. He never disappoints! Jules is personable, easy to talk to, and genuinely interested in his clients. As someone new to the country, I appreciate that he takes the time to listen to my stories and experiences as a newcomer in Minnesota.

I value his honesty and transparency; he always asks for our opinions and goes the extra mile to suggest hairstyles that suit us best. Today, I had my first-ever highlights done by Jules, while my partner and I both got haircuts. Every visit, we feel welcomed and comfortable, never out of place. Jules Hendricks is truly a gem that Cajah Salon is lucky to have.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michele Fluhr Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEGM9K8imt0HYnxMDafghvmohzzHPWE4Jg4LozV7tYlqQNgkG9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great Salon Spa!  First haircut with Olivia and she is definitely my new stylist. They were moving the very next day to the new space on Snelling and still had a full calendar and GREAT customer service amid the busy excitement of such a huge undertaking. Can’t wait to go back and see the new location!","Images":null,"When":""}]

All the other employees are super friendly and helpful too. I have recommended Salon George to many other people who need a haircut. 100% recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dedekat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9srSrs0n7jo0B7xei0_ac5eIZdjGYTbvtXo_GuZCs_L-jbuMb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I thought my stylist was very nice. I truly believe she did the best she could with the crazy hair I had come in with. And had I gone back to fix it I'm sure she would have done a good job. The 2 stars comes from the fact that after I noticed the patches I was told I could contact her through Instagram to come back and get it fixed at a discounted rate. I did not want to spend money to fix their mistake. The color also lacked in saturation. My hair likely needed a fill before applying the permanent color as it was very light and porous at the ends. My wedding is in a few weeks and I do not have time to come back. I suggest asking for their more experienced stylists for anything that needs more than an all over color. Again my hair was crazy when I went in but I'm still bummed that I didn't walk out with what I had hoped.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIjPzj4r3AVIJRU7BeXnQLqGQuEcOwdFxxfG74\u0026fid=0x0:0xf6b53351a452973e"],"When":"2022-5-27"},{"Name":"Libby Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNiopwvgPzHjA6Sd1lE3iKZMRFNc6omEfcTIoBDYstAVA5KQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Where to begin! I brought my 8th grade son in to get his hair cut. He has a notoriously middle school aged relationship with his hair and hates it most of the time. He was met in the waiting room by Dustin who gave him the greatest greeting of all time, essentially telling him he loved his hair and made him feel immediately comfortable. I stayed out of the way and could hear them talking throughout. Dustin treated my kid with such awesome respect and kindness, talking to him like he would any adult in his chair. My son soaked it all in and left that salon, and Dustin, feeling better about his hair than he ever has. As for the cut...omg it's amazing. Thank you, thank you, thank you. There is nothing in the world like seeing your kid feel confident when he is navigating the hellscape that is middle school. ❤️❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Louise Bork","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLnQY5HhT5NVMaRK-gKPfeBM38EsMj8bu9WpVGT5Op4Jy-5CLc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got my hair styled for a wedding! Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pinko Possum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVO_w17mRx6Uzwv8rd7-yWFoROXbNK-mKI4R71NyP8xjmPAqWo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alanna is great. I’m now rocking a French bob that I’m super happy with!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carri Rin Tacheny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW74qQsCtYjpTONT35zj5_8ovOJAG35s4j31FomqinS2myZtpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"SG had character - Energy - and Style!!!
