[{"Name":"Sienna Casos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6871RL6IgyJbaTaIRqSF20t_jbZWbs_E4-kuV2hYd0taSlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the most amazing experience with Alexa today. I was so lucky to snag a last minute appointment, and I am so grateful she fit me in. Before we started, we had a quick but thorough consultation that got us on the same page. Every step from start to finish, she let me know what the plan was, gave me options, and checked in with me about how I felt about the progress and if I wanted to adjust anything. While she styled me, she took the time to walk me through product options and discuss a good curly hair routine. It was super informative and I can’t wait to see how her advice helps my hair. She was also a pleasure to talk to, and our time together flew by. I am beyond pleased with the finished product- my hair feels absolutely incredible. I would go back in a heartbeat- it was worth every penny.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmswPIbBBF_SL20kGhKNxCVhECXQHjYuzfAfjm&fid=0x0:0x7bb252faef80ec12"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Ellis Johnston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPnUzBCeXrfOPQKxvxpf8I6_Jg__l4vCronZkjjA7PQi7ySrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lily is fantastic and my experiences with her at hello hair have all been stellar. At some points in my life I’ve left a haircut experience feeling out-if-sorts or like it’s going to take a bit to get used to — not with Lily!! Every time I immediately feel like a star, like she’s able to create the exact hair vibe to match how I feel inside. She understands the vision and executes it perfectly in a way that’s realistic and fits m goals.

I also love that the products they use here all feel very natural, clean, and not overly scented. Their commitment to the environment, transparency, and taking care of their employees are huge wins and align with my values ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kylie Porter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsOx0Roy_86M3CHN7w3pO8NtPx7fUSMl1PNw4pWz5_LKcsKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had the most incredible hair transformation with Cat at Hello Hair Collective, and I'm still absolutely buzzing about it! I spent a full five hours in her chair, and honestly, it felt like time flew by. Cat's attention to detail is just phenomenal. She listened carefully to what I wanted, offered her expert advice, and then executed it flawlessly. My hair came out perfect – exactly what I envisioned, and even better.
Beyond the amazing results, Cat is just a joy to be around. She's warm, friendly, and truly cares about her clients. It was a really relaxing and enjoyable experience. The salon itself, Hello Hair Collective, is beautiful and spotlessly clean. Plus, the little touches like the snacks were a really nice bonus.
If you're looking for a hairdresser who is truly talented, passionate, and will take the time to give you the hair you've always dreamed of, I can't recommend Cat enough. She's a true artist, and I'm so grateful I found her. Thank you, Cat and Hello Hair Collective, for a fantastic experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corinne Deger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQ4IMiFiR7REFjVoxib3uq69q3lb909DZVFvWVbDQ-as1Y4IZL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got my wedding hair done at Hello Hair Collective and it was perfect! They were able to accommodate my entire bridal party. Loved the hairstylists and the space! Super reasonable prices too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpuYXA1J47B0GOZGRUXTb5avTSyy3s8vpZlU8T&fid=0x0:0x7bb252faef80ec12"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Maria Carlson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEMmAnsGZkN29z0WSxQBnjiaFRy-6-L5Ntg07l21ADtWG4QgPw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visitor, and really loved my time here. As someone who gets nervous going to salons and feeling out of place, this salon felt really safe and comfortable. The plants and windows really opened the space up and just felt welcoming. On the haircut side, Lily did my hair and was very knowledgeable and helped me learn more about my hair type. Pricing was great and didn’t have to tip afterwards since it was all included. Will definitely be coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sami Tahedl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCjYKU2IDVkseKzrlWH2Si_b49ZBZdan3Lm-ofagOFlXXcO5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Looked up best salons near me and this place popped up with 5 stars! Booked an appointment with Starr and I was NOT disappointed! She listened to everything I wanted and made it better than I was even expecting!! If you’re looking for a new place to go you should definitely consider coming here and seeing Starr! They just got a new regular customer!! Below is a before and after!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlK8AQ9jsxUO6A1iDa0JI3fXPKRKTVYVJqGlP3&fid=0x0:0x7bb252faef80ec12"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Lauren McCaughtry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTxcI2zXRaje7IZ7Xpw8b1lNU6YQekYGK_n7EveUbc1rMSn3Xe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the most relaxing and wonderful haircut experience here recently with Lily! I've got slightly wavy-curly hair that I like to style curly. She was attentive and asked thorough questions that gave me the opportunity to advocate for exactly what I envisioned and she DELIVERED! My hair is so much healthier looking and has the volume and bounce I had been missing in it for a while. Thank you Lily!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzPsWgic8QYlwGGjQg8stBrfiDcDp3hNCr7xO37EgkDamshw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a haircut with Cat, and I loved it! She was great at educating me on how to style my hair to achieve the best curls. I loved my cut, and have since used the same techniques at home and got great results! Thanks for a great cut Cat!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Wendy Vang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnt8sDkuLosbUMtBf402uySrEpKwXbabwOPPOgFft-41U1nMAB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've booked two appointments with Frankie last month and have been wow'd by how they were able to transform my hair with both the cut and how I wanted to color my hair. I had a lot of concerns about how I wanted to style my hair and whether or not I was doing my routine correctly, and Frankie took the time to listen to my concerns and point me towards the right direction of how to style my hair the way I envisioned it. Our interactions were very friendly and welcoming, which made the appointments go lightning fast.

I'm really glad I stumbled upon Steller Hair, as it's evident that they do care about their clients' experiences and want to make sure that whatever visions their clients hold about their hair, it comes to life. I'll definitely continue to come back here to get my hair styled in the future, and make recommendations for this location and especially Frankie to other people! Thank you so much!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmCJkp1tljI_2QEGXQrJ4QJYLy5Q74ZrNGh6Vu&fid=0x0:0x2ca6875eee0d7f33"],"When":"2025-3-13"},{"Name":"Lauren Matykowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLD9me79FiuOP0TeEHHuSqCTzHwsfy8Q4OR5h81Jr2rb_bmQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a wonderful place that is welcoming and and very accommodating. I've been with my stylist for ten years, Erika Nash, and she is FANTASTIC. Before I found this salon and Erika, I used to be so afraid to get my haircut because it never came out how I wanted it. I completely trust Erika and she has given me several great styles over the years. I always leave happy and feeling good. She's also taught me a lot about how to take care of my hair on my own. She's a real educator. Can't recommend her enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grace Neumann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKP4M14TUrUSHkSYlaAQb6yDsSM26DTB9pM2Th4pDgbMQadg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Frankie did an absolutely incredible job! I'm newish to the Twin Cities and it's always a little nerve wracking to get your hair done at a new place for the first time. Frankie gave me the most natural looking balayage I've ever gotten! Coming from a 24/7, 365 sunny state I'm used to having bright natural highlights in my hair year-round; my first Minnesota winter left my hair darker and duller, and I wanted some dimension and pop back. Frankie really followed my hair's natural highlights, and the result is my winter hair (artificially) looking like my summer hair, I finally feel like myself again! Also gave the best haircut I've gotten in awhile and I will 100% be booking with them again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandra Clemans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWncbCYARWv23vvzoe-IwRc7HOItPRAzN1DXz9rv6jL2Vu1LdY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently saw Bella for a haircut. I went in with one of the worst hack jobs (think mullet done by a child) and I've been growing it out as it seemed completely unfixable to me. I have not felt like myself for a long time and my self confidence was at an all time low. I went in explained what I was hoping to get done for my cut, and to say she met the mark would be setting the bar too low. She did the best haircut I have had in my entire life. I nearly cried out of pure happiness!! She was so kind and listened and was able to do exactly what I was describing to her that I wanted. I am so glad I made a last minute appointment and she was available because she is now going to be my stylist forever!! If you are feeling down and  need a pick me up---go see Bella! Also big shout out to the cute dog in the lobby who kept me company while I was waiting for her to set up, such a sweet soft pup! <3 Steller is a perfect name for this salon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwkefHMyhKuNcW71JQf6vo6arPjaRyIvsB4a9o&fid=0x0:0x2ca6875eee0d7f33"],"When":"2025-2-20"},{"Name":"Ariela Marshall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl7HD0eEdrSF7fWN8pWM63QM4EjYg7_PS2DgKQRJLMPtEkuCSz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a haircut and color (highlights) with Bella and she was fantastic! Not only did I love it personally, but I went out to dinner with two friends a couple nights later and they both said within two minutes of seeing me, "did you get your hair cut and colored? It looks amazing!" And they both arrived separately so they had the same comment without hearing what the other said! thanks Bella and I'll definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sam h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXog08i2bJQXL9UfC-Qci4IkbiHw4Ev4BVCZsBhDk9TF-pAwOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're looking for a great stylist for "alt" hairstyles I recommend Maeby. You'll need to wear a mask but her work is worth it.
Best stylist I've ever had hands down","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allison Steddom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz2-yHXb1rBn5WJG8iM-aKbqFOJ-9Wa1e3nYS3zEr6yap2kx-k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the simple experience of working with a stylist who listens and delivers. I've got a go-to stylist, but honestly I have confidence in the whole team - you will leave feeling and looking Steller!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEyg1qEpH_khF-CBnNo_2ljX0IddNP-hTSof9s9d0_utK_ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been getting my hair styled at Stellar, specifically with Bella R. on and off for a few years now.  Although I no longer live in Northeast MPLS, I still try to book whenever my schedule allows. She is always friendly, genuine, and most importantly great at her job of styling hair. Ive tried multiple other stylists from other high end salons in the area including JUUT and Haus. Bella cuts my hair the best. Maybe it’s because this salon is focused on women, but I really wish there was a slightly discounted men’s rate.  I feel cool being the only dude in the salon sometimes.","Images":null,"When":""}]

As a woman of color of South Asian heritage, I wanted someone who would understand my hair needs. I appreciated how she asked me questions about my preferences and also what had worked and hadn’t worked with my previous stylists. She took time to explain in detail what she recommended. She answered all my questions on the products she was using and shared styling tips. Even though it was my first appointment with her, I felt very comfortable with her. She was warm and friendly and seemed very knowledgeable on what she was doing.I  absolutely loved how she cut and styled my hair. I highly recommend Pa to anyone who is looking for a new stylist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jill Mae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqcetp8Q76Chw51uiMBQYd1xTqeNzBuvYcdUuaBsyZ-zzaLYAn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Meraki is absolutely stunning. She is not only the sweetest, most fun stylist I know, but she is very creative, and uses so much attention to detail when working. 11/10 recommend:)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcToGmpyNXaa9Kaxo_iG5RAnJxHeksOv7hJ793\u0026fid=0x0:0xd3535c60d0a7fe47"],"When":"2023-2-7"},{"Name":"Kelly Graber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAu_o587IfVcxB7K752UfJqEsCZZeUtxEMJLg1pt1a4XCtAPkQog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pa is amazing, she is attentive to client requests and is very helpful in getting the cut you want. [{"Name":"Mollie Chalberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGIcrwTbx3dgyAh2oIXIyYsXbkU6GXtcVQBf_ZXoBoPBWdpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alyssa has COMPLETELY changed my hair game! I know I can trust her to make my hair look AMAZING every single time! Words can truly not describe how incredible her work is!!
I came to her with damaged, awful hair, and she completely brought me and my
hair back to life! I’ve never looked better, honestly. I’m coming up on 2 years of coming to Alyssa, I can say it’s one of the best decisions I have made.
She also is such great company as I get pampered! Absolutely love her! I know I’m in good hands in her salon. If you want to look ABSOLUTELY GORGEOUS, go to her!! You will not regret it! ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMchGpapqQZWrgg6Jx0kA-dszsb53pu7WomYh4S&fid=0x0:0x44797b423a2a0af8"],"When":"2024-2-13"},{"Name":"Alice Piar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4QiXUGorIxfZiM-kMnCNeLZeDQm1GX7mZBxhWJ-0SYkoXzOcS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am thrilled to have found Alyssa to fix my hair. After a disappointing experience with a permanent box color, I contacted Alyssa and was provided a free consultation. She not only provided effective solutions for correcting the color without causing damage but also recommended a new color that truly revitalized my look. Thanks to her expertise and top-quality products, my hair feels healthier than ever. I wholeheartedly recommend her services without hesitation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9VuaCY4fizKeK9bbsJsO379fPaP5YUFbaOAn3&fid=0x0:0x44797b423a2a0af8"],"When":"2024-4-4"},{"Name":"Keely Rau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjYfY_5jntQUXi5Q8KJMWOYj6PHrNEYj_YFh6M7iwlFcWJIg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alyssa’s work is truly stunning! Not only does she deliver amazing results, but her recommendations for products and styling are also top-notch. Her salon space is incredibly inviting, clean, and a fun atmosphere. I would wholeheartedly recommend her services without hesitation, rating her a perfect 1000 out of 10!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4n9flvtCmP4IX_vj9C8VVT0Kp_A0JX84LLA0g&fid=0x0:0x44797b423a2a0af8"],"When":"2024-4-5"},{"Name":"Katherine Hamilton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8wBIzIF7I9p2qxjrO6xmLwmKIco_doLTQZMN3r9uQjPB5Qg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alyssa is the best! She transformed my hair into something I absolutely love after a bad hair job. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Angelina Peterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFlH2WWsm6cLXLiTge9Fpvnx8_NFQ0eA5kBLpXK1o9IldOWys=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the most incredible experience! As someone with type 3C curly hair, I've had my share of salon disappointments, but this was truly a game-changer.  The atmosphere was unique and modern. The stylists clearly understood curly hair.  Lori took the time to listen to my concerns and what I was hoping to achieve with my cut.  Not only did she give me the most amazing haircut my curls have ever had – bouncy, defined, and frizz-free – but she also educated me throughout the entire process.  Lori explained the techniques she were using, why they were choosing certain products, and gave me personalized tips on how to care for my curls at home and if I didn't get the same results at home she is willing to help teach me how. She has earned a client for life!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patty Amatuzio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVkJJbi4L59PzN0MRBYuVtKx7r-WyN2LqwA0IMY-e8Erh69h6lbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Twisted Hare Salon for CURLY hair styling and coloring session, and I couldn't be happier with the results! From the moment I walked in, I was greeted with a warm and friendly atmosphere. Lori  is incredibly professional and attentive, making sure to understand exactly what I wanted.

Lori did an amazing job with my hair. The color turned out vibrant and exactly as I envisioned, and the styling was perfect. I will be showing it off as my birthday is this month. The products Lori used are top-notch and cruelty-free, which is a big plus for me. I purchased some to bring home.

I will definitely be returning for my future hair needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yazzmine Zaccardi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5ry1WW52pVpn2fJ046UMImq7LWS98X6wKvcgZoPSdymNcZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lori ALWAYS does phenomenal work!! I always find Lori easy to chat with, professional, and personable. First impressions: Visually attractive environment, Friendly and welcoming staff, the stylist listened to my thoughts on the current state of my hair, and what I was hoping to achieve for a style now and in the future. The process of cutting, shampooing, hydrating and styling was relaxing. It felt like there was extra time and attention given to the styling process that acknowledges and accentuates the needs of curly hair. These stylists and staff know what they are doing. I'm looking forward to my next visit. Five stars!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa MacMartin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU32gcFS9lh6FBeBQ4nBYdyLHv4XPKN0B92kfINeTWZWMgi2mI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been searching for a stylist since mine moved out of the country two years ago. I've tried five different stylists at various salons since then  and have been unhappy about the results, especially my last haircut which was far too short. I had my first cut with Mars and I am feeling hopeful and happy. She listened, asked lots of questions, and let me put my glasses on periodically to check her progress. The dry cut worked so well--she trimmed a bit at a time, checking with me as she cut--I could see clearly the amount she was cutting. She made a few adjustments at the end, then showed me how to style it, a very different method from any of the other stylists. Mars recommended I wait 12 weeks before coming back, which makes sense to me as I try to grow my hair to a more flattering length. I'm a happy customer and will be back. Thank you Mars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Margaret Liddiard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB1tiDbpQYQlGwBvCSVLRWyLwIAS0N7ejmXLeLdjghVCTgsVNN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted shorter hair, but was unsure of the cut. Claudia kindly guided me through some choices and then got busy with her scissors. I am beyond thrilled with this result! If you've got curls, this is the place for you and your hair!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPs_Mx9Op3KaFt_kuVF1uXv2gB_JhnKvRffY-oX&fid=0x0:0x2af2383994a8ad90"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Jessica Wandrie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7YcZuriKCFwHijJc3icV7-I5AIhKAMqqtYqIYRka568R8ShH_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was recommended to try the Twisted Hare Salon from a friend of mine. I have been struggling with discovering my hair type. I booked a session with Lori and didn’t know what to expect. Upon arrival, she asked if I wanted to have some tea and while we waited for the hot water we had small talk then discussed my vision for my hair. My hair was long so I wanted to start with cutting a few inches off. Even with the 6 inches of hair cut off, Lori was able to find curls! I loved it. She taught me what products to use, that water is my friend when it comes to curls and how often I should wash my hair. I have never had anyone teach me how to do my hair. I scheduled another appointment 12 weeks later and asked Lori to cut even more hair off and I am in LOVE with my hair! I didn’t think my hair had this curl potential! Lori taught me how to dry/defuse my hair and gave me tips on how to pin it up at night. I am thankful that my friend recommended this salon and I am thankful for Lori being my hair guide/teacher!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPke3pMAecptDWu_2oeltN-1um0JJYD8rnivjMW&fid=0x0:0x2af2383994a8ad90"],"When":"2024-3-16"}]

The middle part of my hair has more hair than the bottom. I can’t style my hair like before and feel like I barely have any hair on my head. I noticed when she was cutting my layers shorter she wasn’t even measuring her cuts she was just chopping off  my layers even more. Not it looks like I have bangs at the back of my head. It’s a fun and eclectic feel once you’re inside, courteous staff and it felt pretty inclusive in terms of staff having knowledge of all hair types and textures. I wish they did more to fight the pink tax though. Would highly recommend. There are plenty of parking options, and the nursery next door is a must see.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christopher Pichner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzVJtsuyl505zLyudM-GDY6he0E-D6aRlUOYSsTD63h46elmUM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sarah is fantastic and Josie (the mascot) pup is usually there to greet you when you show up to get a rad haircut. She does a great job on my teenagers hair and my hair as well.  Also the offer you water or beer when you come in for a cut, what more can you possibly want?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIFSoietMANCIWstwDbNz9nu2Q29mDpIWSwmts&fid=0x0:0x1cae62a2466a3698"],"When":"2018-1-9"},{"Name":"Lina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIld8e6o_o_J_0KIklWFwHrXvS0qAbQOJUyZYSl4i8hOoIUhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Proceed with caution- The first time I went here the stylist did an absolutely great job. I went in wanting to cut nearly waist length hair into a lob. It looked fantastic and I couldn't have been happier. When I went back for a trim, I had the same stylist. During the cut she mentioned more than once being tired and the haircut seemed rushed. I was sent out the door with wet hair. When I got home I was pretty devastated to see that the haircut was pretty uneven. There is a large piece of hair on one side that is too short to pull back and its only on one side. The bottom is choppy even though I asked for a blunt trim. I'm pretty devastated. Its obvious enough that even my boyfriend noticed. I was offered a refund but ya know.. I'd rather have my hair. I will say they were pretty friendly when I called crying about my hair and everyone there seems nice. Overall proceed with caution. You might get a fantastic cut and you might not.

Update: I was asked by coworkers what had happened to my hair. It is that painfully obvious. I can honestly say I've never felt uglier after a haircut. I was given a refund that came up $5 short. I'm not going to bother asking for the rest back.
I would strongly recommend avoiding this place or at the very least, staying away from Madi.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGF5UTB5JQBFyvY-jtXIwB4Hd2rrAH9UssPGNS&fid=0x0:0x1cae62a2466a3698"],"When":"2019-3-28"},{"Name":"Julianna Kolb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyZSUBvg1uyU3mPEhuhMz-jdjYwEvVBFqsONUwgMgnnb9EhDy8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sometimes I like to try new adventurous hair colors and I always go here. Abbey is super knowledgeable and I love my new hair color","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erika Pieniniemi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG-hbHkTusZ09OPZoKuAJeWkNkeCarJfwJ-MeOCE7fjqb-ZIlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been looking for a new massage therapist and just had my first appointment with Rachel- it was such a good experience! She even had some helpful suggestions on how to manage some pain issues going forward and made me feel comfortable the entire time. I’ve also loved a recent haircut I got from Abbey and would recommend this place for any service based on my experiences! Great local spot in NE and I plan to keep coming back :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Véronique Lourdel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNqwLGqvq9lsjIL_PzuDlxM1-UuNKVh6QUpqdFZVZZD77yWSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently moved to Minneapolis and was looking for a hairdresser that was skilled enough not to butcher my pixie cut.
There I found Sydra who gave me perhaps my favorite haircut ever. She listened to me, worked with me, understood my concerns, and came up with a version of my cut that blew me out of the water.
If you are looking for a great team of hairdressers who are as nice and competent as can be, I recommend this salon.

Veronique aka Nikki","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Simione","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLrhdDefuDuj-qXwE7vJ2giHoylQpTGGiq7tbSXFZPSrA02A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I take my 86 year old mother here for her hair style needs.  She is always satisfied and happy to see everyone.  Skilled, friendly, and extremely respectful of all kinds of beautiful humans.  Don't judge this book with your biases.  These peeps are great artisans!  Great work Cryptic crew!","Images":null,"When":""}]

I had the best experience in her chair and will definitely be traveling the 4 hours back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCAh-e237ZqLEk8IzuBdadjn4S_aQW7PJ5w_K4&fid=0x0:0x9b135e3ea2e050f7"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Jessica Morales","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmaHMLWXk5PQPM1Q4kt4lm_XyuA4maH_H4GIHBM4G-6M9fbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been seeing Kailyn for a while now, her hands are magic when it comes to curl cut/color. She brings good vibes and energy, really engaging and makes you feel comfortable and takes her time.
The only down fall is the owner Kristy is not approachable, not friendly, brings really bad energy to what should be a fun environment and good experience.  Always seems to be in a hurry. I give Kailyn 5 stars and zero for Kristy which is bad being that she’s the owner…….","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"vidhu anand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvkdOkT4G0kXlyyhYrg7Fvqm0amdTLmBH6s3LnzHJ561jWV58=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Janessa did an amazing job with my curly hair cut. She is very thoughtful and spent a long time finding the right style for me. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rikki G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmCFlkWbymWyKsVRJCXmUPdUfcOQS26YKuN2jCRNOXTrvK7fkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The reviews about the atmosphere here are spot on. Pay attention to those. If you want a warm friendly atmosphere where your stylist engages with you, this is not the place to go.

My main sources of of disappointment are that Kristy (the owner and my stylist) was exceptionally rough with my hair, to the point where it was extremely painful. I was also up-charged halfway through the service, despite Kristy being the exact same person who did my consult AND booked my appointment. Apparently she booked it incorrectly as an express cut and foil instead of rainbow colors and I got shafted for her mistake with zero apology or remorse.

The cut was fine; nothing special. The fashion colors I had done were also fine but nothing special. For $300 and a 4-hour time commitment that was originally supposed to be 2.5 hours, and a head and scalp that took days to recover from being tugged and pulled and dropped onto a sink repeatedly, I won't be going back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Pumarlo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUJOD7rnLF3wdLAo0yOXlGGzbrK4j-qu8dimCu2Vh2FKpaOJk7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kailyn is exceptional! I was originally a client at the Maple Grove location and was disappointed when it closed. Kailyn's professionalism, enthusiasm, and ability to provide outstanding curly haircuts make the drive to St. Paul worthwhile.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Quinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSqQHgAl-RWDmvm0HfVB4ZWGpxwGEaQUGUava2H7uYD-hhyVTe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have seen Amanda 4 times in the last year. She is the first curl specialist I've seen and I have been so happy with her cuts and color that I continue to see her. She listens to what I want and always delivers exactly that!  My color looks very natural, the cuts always give my curls shape and new life. Highly recommend the salon as well, very comfortable and inviting.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Britnee Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnP7nrzTPw02GisXigpcs_vAFh3KY0VfMDWW3OFvwJVTFyBypV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Janessa was absolutely amazing! [{"Name":"Cathy Quarterman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4AyrYC6Rx341Iosa9flbtOpHzkPy3NRQKjGdeBhFvk1enCzpb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Michael is great he makes sure you are satisfied with his work I love the conversation we have and he always says if you are not satisfied you know where I am that is appropriated to know I can go back and he will listen and fix what ever it is thank you for your service and hard work Cathy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emily Wallner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0MHe-pMEcvqVi387Jbs0JO502kwGWmxIywh7UqSDydXgMF3mw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today (8/14/23)  was my first time at Pusch Salon. I was able to get a same-day with Michael, and went from shoulder length hair to an asymmetrical concave bob. He did a great job on my hair, was gentle throughout the process, listened to my feedback as we went, communicated well, and made me laugh. I enjoyed the appointment and do believe I have just found myself a new hair person! Price ($50 before tip) was very reasonable. Salon was very clean and organized. Free parking on both sides of the street (Marshall Ave) in a quiet neighborhood.

I also enjoyed his dog being there, Kuna. Kuna was friendly, just kinda hung out nearby and was very chill & relaxed. If you didn’t see her, you would not have known that a dog is there often— no hair anywhere, no odor, nothing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFFi3swfQOOz7DBjsXuL0zJ2WCRolFG5-a_kQt&fid=0x0:0xbb7bd1674e42abf6"],"When":"2023-8-14"},{"Name":"Drew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-eV3U2myDhU-WgLEnrhZ-uB_74W_p1tTCSpUkcUG3pt9UO2OOYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another great haircut from Michael. If you’ve left other haircuts disappointed, maybe it’s time to go to Pusch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nok T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVKpqH9CEG4xze9CmOtKg9CPUBhmnqHXo7g8Y7mgvx7NMoVcKbxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I just got our hair done from here. I will definitely go there again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vermin One","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrMiLqZffLUr4hC8jlpaGQJUVRSa4TFJMYlE9D4NG7a_OYcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After having tried countless salons since moving here 8 years ago, finally finding the perfect one is such a relief. Kasey is very knowledgeable about the science of hair itself, as well as being an excellent stylist. She is also very down to earth and friendly and makes sure you get exactly what you are looking for. The owner, Mike, is also super friendly and likes to chat so when you are there it kind of feels like you are just catching up with some friends. Except you leave looking fabulous!

Another thing...i have found their pricing to be very reasonable. Just had my color done and it was far less pricey than many other places I had checked in to. And it came out just perfect!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaXwKLq-fCttAwW5VOLLAGbvdZ8AJYKy0xF-QRhpSAsokwaVa0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Michael is amazing. I look like freaking g rapunzel and couldn't go five minutes without getting compliments on my highlights and blowout. Even though I was soooooo tired, he kept the conversation going and got me out with plenty of time to get to work. I will be booking a haircut soon","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kit ingersoll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUre6cnOpSdnkTCz_kd5xkT9Lsx5yEk74FhFXCuy5O5r2XcTSY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike is the MAN. High quality barber, extremely affordable. Got my hair cut from him once and I’m never going to anybody else. PUSCH Salon deserves 6/5 stars.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Will be returning :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Zay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVHpkfUCccR2cv_ut1yl0c8k6OLl7wZ99Fjp9g3WxrF3SSbsYy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kate is a terrific stylist but I’m sure everyone on their team is at a similar skill level. Repeat customer who will be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Neri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKIsF8JpvY-ZUY7XQBotD4d8gd2JAQeLuofhCzCxvE_VvMEw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the haircut I got (from Michelle!) and the whole experience was peaceful and considerate. I normally can’t stand getting my hair cut but here it was lovely!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"June T.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKEqFOGeNPuEkluCJZHZg_E-4eYNKZrx96GZe-YfMxfjZqb7Dj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time at The Chair and it was amazing! My stylist Paula was so sweet and accommodating. Loved my haircut so much I immediately booked an appointment for color! Everyone was very friendly. The salon is warm and inviting and the country music was a big plus for me! I highly recommend The Chair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"vicki rush rush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQA13hIIxKGw5iHvcZ1El7FXZyDkK-wjUkdY82jABF1FzVxoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kate gave me a super cute short cut.  I’m undecided in these moments.   Kate spent time understanding my hopes and dreams.  Kate delivered.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allison Nordman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBhT-P8XgIEylRfx18UuqZRuVnMpX0Ei-7Rd1ne60zxOdAzbry=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is my new go-to salon. Kate is amazing! She did a complete overhaul of my hairstyle (from long to short with bangs), and I absolutely love it! She took time to discuss my vision, walked me through each step of the cut/styling process, recommended products and gave upkeep tips (since I’ve never had bangs before!) - and she definitely delivered on the style!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWTShhwmD3Suu6lMu6_bkn8cOzUDDHf0kgboAU\u0026fid=0x0:0xe4fad12c485efe68"],"When":"2023-1-8"},{"Name":"Allison Gast","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfJU8hS7lRu6ZpdArUfqrjwJ7NK_-PvWPBa3ZFH1XQdF86_wW9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was brand new to The Chair. The salon is very cute, clean and rustic. This was my first time going to a different stylist so I was a little nervous but Brigitte worked well with my crazy thick hair and gave me exactly what I asked for. She was very relaxed and personable and I would recommend her to friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dorine Doyle King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5H_A1Ta4ZOGH9h8WTjslLMFQaCEDQ1rh4KWRa0Sp0MxcXVzFT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I live in a very small town in northern Minnesota and it's very difficult to get a haircut that feels and looks good to me.  I used to live in South Minneapolis and was here on a vacation, so decided to schedule a haircut at The Chair.  I may have to come back every 12 weeks!  Kate was awesome!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mara Maus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjB7byoL3k4NT1lZOElcg-u-ePmCdn4E3IvgOdiwWaOrYI-Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Curly hair folks, go see Zena! I have been going to her a while for haircuts and am always so happy with the results. Today was no different; she gave me a stellar wolf cut! Zena sees your vision, and executes it while prioritizing hair health. I also love the products she recommends.

All of the staff here are so welcoming, as well as the salon aesthetic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Morken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXK1xQnl0CIlXw_gXJ3CXSv1Infyrwhmb-wHtKuP8A3ZJe0Y5I6ow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stylist was Mayu. Called spontaneously for a walk in and she was able to fit me in immediately. Mayu did an excellent job on my hair. She was quick and efficient and friendly. If I'm in town next time I need a cut, I'm definitely coming back here. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Natasha Jenson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtR8M8P9j9a6Tva9LHdjY7kfIOv_uAuVTtwWep8ZoQ5fClMltEtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today was my first visit.  I was early and chatted with the owner, who was just lovely, and her long-time customer. Long-time customers are a great sign!
Laura cut my hair. She was a lot of fun to work with.  I haven't had short hair in a while,  but put my faith in her and am happy I did. She really listened to what I was looking for.  Every time I see my reflection,  I am just loving it more and more. I will be going back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryn Gagen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd-mAyDlkyhlu7Sj_rUooSWhEi2RsfubxmhQuNA637qmJeLa11jw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've gone here for haircuts from Laura several times now, and she is amazing and one of the only hairstylists I've genuinely enjoyed talking to. She does a great job at remembering your previous styles and helping you make choices if you're unsure, and she is great at cutting short hairstyles like pixie cuts or undercuts. I used to frequent cheaper chain salons but I am now happy paying a higher (but totally reasonable) price for the level of expertise and care provided here.

I recently went with the new COVID-19 restrictions in place and I felt so safe and comforted by the standards Rouge Urban Salon has set in place for customer safety!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Overby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_cLLHgVUj1VU-CHgXJ4daw-p_Jh-pQUvgwfK0AYgE3Pka7yg7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love my new haircut! Stopped by Rogue earlier this afternoon during my commute home from work. Loved the atmosphere. Smells amazing the second you walk in, very peaceful. Laura did a great job on my cut! Asked me all the correct questions before taking her scissors to my hair. Making sure 100% what I was comfortable with. Thank you to Laura and the Rogue Hair Salon Team for making this a great experience","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Bolduan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNKWDfaK_WiLC3yEA9ChJk46SdjqcUBaSVyCvJspO7zrXa_Lpa5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I use Laura Buske as my stylist for male haircuts and I have to say that her work is top notch and the prices fair. Even in the pandemic she's done a wonderful job of making a cut that lasts between times coming in. I've also seen her work on cuts and more importantly coloring on women and I don't know if I've seen better. If you're looking for a new stylist, I cannot recommend her enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vanessa Adame","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9E5NRgp5UxYqW5eUK21oi9tGVO1OEwbaYcjoRbHL93BK6Iyk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mayu was my stylist and was VERY pleased with her work. I know my hair is thick and I had it down to my waist. I asked for a short cut, wispy ends and lighter hair. She did not disappoint. Pleasant to talk to and constantly referred back to me to see if I like how its coming out. Will definitely be coming back to her","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catie Bearmon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlZ0WehChmTzj3gdJixWFC5j-kemklZIf92b3AVrBSUWT4FSCX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My stylist was Laura. She was great! Professional, kind, with great results. I love my hair! Rouge Salon has great COVID practices right now too. I felt safe having my hair done here!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sara Ochs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJR4TR6pxm2tR6sRlGZPP2DtCWimXWH8XhAoUWDgnumbJp_j50=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Salon Ori is lovely! The space is open and welcoming. Parking is easy, with lots of street parking available. I love Krishell!! She’s been my stylist for several years. She gives amazing curly cuts and is so friendly and kind. I always look forward to seeing her.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Drees","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ75haHBTmpkDrwJ2nB_OD_1PTxWFS1Y7HuIAgm8tf8zhAEuI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I originally found Salon Ori after I moved from Northeast Minneapolis to St. Paul and just wanted a haircut closer to home. I'm always one to do my research, I always look at reviews, the gram and tik tok.

I found Anne after deciding to try Salon Ori and *admittedly* stalked her Instagram to see if I vibed with her style. And now I'll never be the same. Anne is so in tune with my hair, she can read my mind and truly LISTENS. I love how she checks in often to make sure we're on the same page. She's also an incredibly kind human. You couldn't be in any better hands!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lydia Wilkie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkDNKVlMSOw_BKbod1OicpEp4Fa86rmxV04-U0_bTQYyYhiec=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this salon! I’ve been looking for a welcoming, queer space to get my haircut in the twin cities for a while. My stylist Cody listens to what I want to help me feel confident in my identity and gender expression. I have short hair and haven’t always felt comfortable going to barbers for a cut, often because I don’t feel listened to about the length and texture I want. Cody gives great razor cuts and has helped me understand a lot more about my hair and how to care for it. I’ll definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Ebertowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu0J3KRVQk5yMnysbbmxG7eeivJZrXeTVTTqc0jWqOsuHTrNzb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so happy that I found Cody Johnson! After my previous stylist retired I went through many before I found Cody. Not only does he give a high quality cut he is also always on time and will get you in and out as scheduled. I also appreciate his attention to detail and will always make sure you leave happy with the cut. Cody also fosters a friendly and relaxing experience during your visit. I won't go to anyone but Cody!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tammy Nienaber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOL0KZPyUiB1nPbasmw2ml58yW9ujnTHkA_AAbsScArBgh8la99w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jen did a fabulous job fixing my nightmare Covid hair! I've been growing out a super short pixie cut.

She even recommended an amazing all-in-one product I can use to keep my low maintenance style. It's a shampoo and texturizer combined. I'm all about spending less time on my hair each day.

Everyone at the salon was clearly diligent about following Covid-19 guidelines, which is highly appreciated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWSSwBYoHEF0W7V5qg81-VcWaE-hyhnLVO9A0P&fid=0x0:0xc92c6fe1d6292424"],"When":"2020-9-19"},{"Name":"Jon Michael Stiff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaKy6tVzkgYShEBaOmXan4UPUPzJSGKmOgLgFjBmaEkJqPoSbI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been seeing Cody as my stylist for almost 5 years now, but it only took the first cut to keep me coming back!  He has the knowledge and skill to listen to what you want,  make suggestions,  and find something that will work for your hair! Always friendly and easy to talk to,  you won’t regret booking with him!  I always leave so happy with my hair!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"melissa taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFG3eoq4K0WrIEVRt_CGfYPRZrBhF0-jJLjd0XtG28aCU8Tw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the best experience with this salon. First time getting my hair cut in years. I wanted a shaved cut which I have never done before and had a photo as a reference. Ashley did an amazing job and even asked if cutting more off was ok before she did it. Thank you again and I'm obsessed with the haircut.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pat Lealos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2xSpiCh48o7j1OOFx-JJ20eckpmzAZ0Ao1oo0tD5Szo-rdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great salon on Selby.  Cody is the best, he gives the best men’s haircut in town!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsqxzwvXaVKhkQwMHy0n5FmLieKCVmhIbIiemA&fid=0x0:0xc92c6fe1d6292424"],"When":"2022-1-18"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Gina Knutson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6ToXWIPEbIfGylYHicYzC_ueEW4oXTcCf3GNoHTAzOhw4nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alicia is fabulous! She does a great job of listening to what you're looking for and delivering that. I have naturally curly/wavy hair and she's great about cutting your hair for multiple ways of styling it (straight, curly, etc.).  She does our kids' hair as well and is always up to date on the newest trends.  I highly recommend checking her out.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maggy Schneider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN7m2uSnnnPPuSO4QxPto8oQVRufqse4dcQSC8pQbBgw88Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love my haircut! Alicia takes the time to notice my growth patterns and how to effectively frame my face plus she instructs me on how to maintain my hair - how to style, what products to use. I'll be returning again and again.  Thank you for making this part of my life a breeze!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnJ6eg6VTCcXHDRKyH8kNYcW0ZH6h4nWyybauhLtpSeNHiMTAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Salon Level. Jessie is simply amazing at cutting, coloring and styling hair. I am not very picky about most things, but I am definitely picky about my hair. Until Jessie I rarely left a salon feeling happy or satisfied. With Jessie, I completely trust her recommendations and I always leave happy with my hair and the whole experience! I have been going to Jessie for 6 years now and several of my friends and family members now see her too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corrie Lapinsky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdm56St2NKUF5RA9jL-lCv2No1K3iGvMt0EvjgTU9Aox5IHLXe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was so great to be back at Salon Level and get my hair cut by Alicia! She is a wonderful stylist, and I really appreciate the safety measures they're taking - masks, distancing and sanitizing. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlene Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6jHAub1vlQ-SZq6JLuAJgrLEKeEM9jn6XNTYyCjLul2TD-qw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have a love/hate relationship with my short hair. It came about after a bad bad bad bleaching incident. I have spent months going to different stylists trying to find a cut I would love! I finally found my answer with Alicia. She is meticulous, warm, and genuinely takes the time to understand your hair. I have unruly and inconsistent curly hair and she made it pop. I'm loving the style and know where I'll be going for the foreseeable future. plus it's reasonably priced!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Curran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpglss_1vI1yjtJ2J-5Bm85Iq0MwUDZ4-m5kK9K04ypUeJF0zv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far the best salon in St. Paul! Alicia (co-owner) always knows exactly how I want my hair to look (cut and color). The salon is spotless too. I am 100% happy every time I leave.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"eva lynn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpFil1OqAOVj5jOrsenLGDc4AZ8YeRAJLrSSXzqXESlNAxYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My dental hygienist recommended Alicia to me years ago, and I haven't seen anyone since Alicia is the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Bell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLXsHwwWuNX0Faq2jjMFlsONbnxDtZo6UutS-lLpphFcH_WhKLUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great location with a cute, clean, and comfortable salon. I've beenn seeing Alicia for 10+years, and she always done a fantastic job, and knows what I want (even when I don't!).","Images":null,"When":""}]

The place is very clean and inviting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVsgCUZd1i7wZk-ViX8JGN-vUUae2DQd-PrCdd\u0026fid=0x0:0x2e2fcf8d19ba0459"],"When":"2022-9-2"},{"Name":"Sherry Chaquette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhGYeTULS_vjowDadVvllx1_eCX6Oihzs3hMw3cyzhDAn75w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Torih is a true detangler whisperer. My daughter had taken her braids out , and her hair became very tangled to the point of matted. My husband googled top African amazing shops in the Minnesota area. Sense of Style popped up. I shared this shop with my daughter and we reached out. The salon was very peaceful, clean, and calm. Torih was very professional and knew exactly how to address my daughter’s hair. My husband and I were visiting from Missouri. We were all blessed by the service provided for our daughter who was in distress.\n\nI highly recommend any person in the Minnesota St Paul area to experience a place of calmness ,professionalism, and very knowledgeable in healthy hair care. I  high recommend this salon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paketta Norris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhATl3XMhtRm5soRy01vwTUMJFLFMSG84Tpxok4QDTqBdZOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I don’t usually write reviews. But my experience here was so terrible that I would give this place -5 stars if that was possible. I was bringing my five year old daughter in for a silk press and a trim. It was her first time in a salon as soon as I walked in the door. Torih gave a very cold hello and asked who would be receiving service that day. I told her it was for my daughter. She looked at my daughter and said she doesn’t look like she wants her hair done. Then proceeded to let me and my child know that she gives kids with attitudes attitude right back. My daughter had a 330 appointment. She was finishing up one client. There was another client waiting with dye in her hair. Another without an appointment that was waiting. Torih was the only person working in the shop. When it came my daughters turn Torih Comes over to grab her by the hand proceeds to show her the sink and where she would sit to get her hair done. She stopped and asked my daughter do you want your hair done? My daughter said no. My daughter wasn’t crying,  being uncooperative, throwing any type of fits or anything of that sort. She said no because she was nervous…again she has never been in a salon before. Torih Then, let me know that she will not be doing my daughters hair. I Proceeded to ask her follow-up questions as to why and it was simply because she just decided that my daughter was not ready. I let her know that that was very unprofessional. She was rude throughout the entire communication we had since we walked in the door. I told her how I felt respectfully. Questioned why she would not even make any type of attempt to do my daughter hair. She had no valid reason other than she feels like she’s not not ready. She then proceeds to take a lady who is waiting without an appointment to do her hair after letting me know she couldn’t start her hair until she declined my service because she didn’t have an appointment. I thought that was really weird and also extremely rude. Maybe the service the other lady was receiving was more profitable. I was in extreme disbelief. I’ve never been treated this way. In what supposed to be a professional salon. At the very least don’t let this lady deal with your children. She is flat out mean to children. Upon letting her know that I was upset, she told me in a very snotty tone. Well, then write a review. So here’s your review Torih. This is a seriously unprofessional establishment. I’m not sure if anyone else works there with her. But if you have other options, you should use them. Also, I have yet to receive back my $50 deposit that I had to pay just to book the Appointment. She let me know that it would be returned and it has not.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M. Morena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv3CslE1_e8ZGRiv4iJDcI1YynAhnrwM2ZYtQ3-PWXNRYTr5Kd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Initially, my visits to this place were fantastic, but my recent experience was disappointing. I was in the salon for FOUR HOURS as Torih, overcome with greed, overbooked and rotated between myself and three other women. The way that she was speaking to people was rather unbecoming as well. And when one particular client she talked to recklessly complimented my hair, Torih was quite the contrarian, quick to tell me that my hair “wasn’t that great.” I let it roll off my shoulders, but now I suspect this was a symptom of her jealousy because after washing my hair, I discovered severe breakage and a loss of curl definition in certain places, clearly a sign of heat damage. In retrospect, she did not put any heat protectant on my hair prior to drying it. I was fatigued from being there for so long, I did not catch it in the moment. The customers that come in and out of that salon are enough to make you want to come back, but this experience has honestly left me traumatized. I should be able to leave a salon with my hair in a BETTER condition than when I arrived. I pretty much paid this woman to damage my hair. I know how to take care of my hair so it’s a minor setback, but I no longer trust Torih so I will no longer return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULa8ZqFtMYBPfKNABriWvGHgpirKA0cgDlpdcirn4_w7Zy75_xxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful products! Very beautiful wigs, jewelry, and even gifts bags and art. The owner is a very beautiful, kind-hearted woman. Needs more attention than it's gotten! A friend brought me there, and I had no idea it was even there. It was a wonderful surprise! I had so much fun looking at everything. I can't wait to go back!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Crystal Champagne Irene","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWa94dqxerEK9EW2AUPobVZwWT3TRFWETlnYBVnkyYUpVXpWZQHCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My son came in with beautiful locks past his shoulders, length that he had been growing out for 3 years. came in And the stylist completely destroyed his hair. My son was dreading high school this morning/ the following day- he had bragged to everyone in getting a haircut. So all his friends were waiting to see the results. I have to buy a bunch of hats now so that he can wear hats every day to school...And you know what? I asked him what we could do. Can I take you in to get it fixed? And he said he doesn't want anymore Cut off!!!  his hair is up to his eyebrows!! it is pathetic how terrible a job she did and the fact that I was still obligated to pay for this haircut, My SON SHOULD'VE BEEN PAID FOR HIS LOSS.. Not just that, but they told my son that he needed products in order for the hairstyle To work.. How sad to destroy my son's hair and then tell him . A necessity for product THEN Charge the mother even more.. I bought the product Hoping RELUCTANTLY cause she convinced my son.!. They knew this was unacceptable. Another girl had to step in and fix what the other girl had done. Took her over 30 minutes trying to fix what was done... By that time it was already too late, how do you fix a bad cut- cut off more right?! Ugh . My son's hair was destroyed and his.  Confidence is my ONLY concern .. What do I do to help him now? It took him 3 years to grow out his hair! I took a picture before she cut it all off.. My poor kid... High school's rough as it is, I don't understand why this had to happen. I choose to schedule at a salon, so that something like this wouldn't happen!!   !His dad offered to take him to great clips . Would've been the same if not better to have went to great clips","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPk3mOCbmN1v1uJHnup57iX3SqCIIYrjjOWAKm&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Andy Landy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjD9e9azKb-FvPjsttW1GY9vUzIzwRCg_IDGQLM1vOee1qlveaEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've visited several times and always had a good experience. I gifted my partner a haircut here when they were looking for a more gender affirming experience ♥️ highly recommended. I'm excited to see the new location!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUohaQqs8bAvhgWwemhwst8WW3JOS3opbvbO47JNqR2cyGlQH-8qw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Hey guys. This was my first time getting my hair professionally colored by Karli. I was initially happy with it but the next day, a lot of the coloring was already fading and I realized the stylist missed spots in my hair. *I DID NOT WASH MY HAIR/TAMPER WITH MY HAIR* . I've contacted to try to get some of my money back, as they charged 300+ for this job. They offered to touch it up. But after looking through the one-star reviews, I do not trust this salon with my hair. They DO NOT GIVE REFUNDS they only offer *touch ups*. They won't even give me a partial refund. Believe the 1-star reviews.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZbXSAQpp4076NKnhzaK5zF2evBoZPrEacXr2W&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Corey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWH-B8eYYuGOrp05-lODKa8XLiUOueIdfGxPcnNOznAawUGKE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The value of the cut for the price was not there for me. A quick dry cut when my hair is not laying flat results in an uneven cut. The only time I’ve had someone do a dry cut it was followed by a wash, then dried and then cut some more to finish it. This stylist decided to do just a quick dry cut and then asked me what do I think when I can’t tell nor could anyone. Here’s just a pic of my bangs as an example.

I recommend some supervision on these less tenured stylists to ensure they know what they are doing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPlNysvFuP-p1_bS_TkVfY80bDXsdjdqoOHdc0X&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Molly Bye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVnisr4pxqotavzRn7_75eOU_cVmedCQ8w2Pk_Jxx7GXQNMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Do not go to this salon. I went in to have my greys colored and a few highlights and my hair looks patchy and the color is uneven. Elizabeth has no idea what she’s doing. The salon is a mess and when I tried to call and speak to the manager I was told that she only excepts emails. Not surprisingly she never responded. Their prices are ridiculous and clearly staff need training.
Update- I reported my experience at The Fox Den Salon to the Better Business Bureau and they reached out to the salon. The owner responded to them of course and said if I reach out to them again they would be happy to either redo my hair or refund my money. I reached out 4 times, phone, email ect. They never called me back or responded to my email. I updated the BBB and they reached out and to The Fox Den. This time they replied and basically said they were not going to participate in a resolution. So there you go. Not only did my hair turn out terrible but the owner/manager couldn’t care less.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbhgJiQCgqS6O-AJILrl1C18qUuR0-EFkN2mIf&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-3-20"},{"Name":"Maggie Finley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUo-qaKCtSjJvc-ww6eRWUbsIypU6AM9VWCVOQWHWooZmdGNskx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had been doing my own hair for the past 8-9 years and it got pretty damaged and hard to work with. Kait gave me a great lived in color that will be a lot less maintenance for me and gave me an amazing haircut that makes my hair feel healthy again!! Will definitely be going back to Kait again for my all hair needs!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeCbvNgZeIJ2elSXn-EOGT1vWmLLa7_NdiURw7&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"Kathleen Overbey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5dEOP7WnslUXvNRApm-FqbPHEb3DFg5WFUGOotK2-cKY2cWc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went in on a short notice for a big transformation- my hair is very thick and can be difficult to work with. Esme did such a fantastic job working with me to bring my vision to life! I hadn’t had a professional haircut in years so I was very nervous to come in but she really made me feel at ease. She also took her time giving my hair the proper attention it needed after being neglected for so long, and the results were SO worth it. Not only did she make me feel so comfortable while I was in the chair but I left feeling so beautiful. I will definitely be following her to the new salon space!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORLL4J80oL2oYiVgbFaC32tXfjM-5_TQIRyCNP&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Lele Moon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJsLvnk-R-dCjev7pRlFJWyhjnib7gJU6zz4X8Hf_Na8fWww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"NO REFUNDS guys be aware!! I was not offered to go back and get it fix but there’s complementary but why go back just to get your hair botched again! Make no sense! FOX DEN have NO MANAGER, only sanitation manager named SEEKA which happened to be the ‘owner’ of the business. Unbelievable. Can’t fit my bad experience explanation here. Read screen shots. Save your money and don’t go here take your service else where.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoRZ5Kjx_ymcrMmAxtBHwXGMO2OUXZSDQ3VzzS&fid=0x0:0xaa70a4497d8aa534"],"When":"2024-3-2"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alina Hortillosa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqnoUEVc_hqGN6LfUrmP3iarxMmNbWUi6X47F8lz83rcluw8l4Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After about a year of not having my hair professionally cut, I did a lot of research and found Lexi Frost. Her website and Instagram page gave me a lot of information and inspiration for what kind of cuts she could do. I really enjoyed my appointment with her! She eased all my anxiety around haircuts, and I could tell that she really had a sure vision. She pays attention to SO MANY details. Seriously, she wants you to have your best hair. Based off of a first impression I will definitely be coming back. Needless to say I love my hair and I've gotten so many compliments already.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ellie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_4trAuJe1bcYEcR5VDYEF01zThOFrE0wmnrleoDa0vCT0Xhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Christopher is great! I’ve been seeing him since last summer and he’s nailed the look every. single. time. I’m naturally maybe a medium brunette and he gets my hair to the most perfect ginger/copper color without any bleach. I even asked for a dark cherry cola color in the winter (inspired by dua lipa) and it looked amaaazing. Usually we do one solid color, but during my last visit with him here at cocoon, I wanted to add some dimension without bleach and he lightened several strands all around my head to this really pretty golden/strawberry blonde to look like highlights and I’m thrilled! He charges the most reasonable prices I’ve seen for someone with his skillset. Better yet, he’s personable and eager to help and listen to your ideas. Besides color, he gave me a really nice haircut too, and the layers he added really stand out with the lightened pieces! Overall he’s a wonderful addition to cocoon and would sincerely recommend a service with him :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6-G4G-NzZmc7mRWdDDKKhUaqenYA4Eq2A2hgA&fid=0x0:0xf26493005ab96233"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Lauren Gustner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_AeTsKS47xMzL173nKYc-hMfaReO1jBad7UQg2ke00q7B_v5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lexi is the best. I feel amazing after every cut. You can tell she loves what she does and cares about what you want. I'll never go anywhere else!
She's great at shags and texture (lovely client pics on her social), but also manages my straight, fine hair well. I've sent friends to her, and she never disappoints!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"HeeWon Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLcmoOiFozD0aZtvv6F8bAWZS9m9ezS9MHHuupXzRD4FU4LmI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lexi frost is unreal. She cuts hair magically, skillfully and so artistically. I had moved from another state and was nervous about finding someone cut my hair, but I hope to have Lexi cut my hair forever! She’s also funny and gives the best recommendations for the twin cities area. Thanks!!!!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtLtd14juAj5WuSss09GWR8yBX-5faWUR8J4bUV_0_4RZxKyop=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lexi Frost is incredibly talented and I highly recommend her! She is very intuitive and just knows how to listen to you and provide suggestions if you want them to come up with the best style for your hair type. She’s warm & down to earth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jasmine Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvxyxVmwXqystq05Z7Molfyf6t1f4x8uwICSRUe_qtTm40jLYT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got recommend to Christopher and he was so responsive and fit me into his schedule on short notice! I showed him a few inspo pics and he did an incredible job! I’ll definitely be back :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristin Canham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8snmXZ2BxkeB8GNgzTJdQJlW_V8F3jLzASAycF-9WLX_CR5AS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had my hair cut at cocoon, and I can honestly say it was the best haircut I've ever had. I worked with Emily Angelo, and she was wonderful! I showed her a few pictures of the style I was aiming for and described my usual hair routine. She listened to me and didn't fill my hair up with a ton of products or break out the straightener and curling iron. She styled my hair just as I wanted, it looked amazing, and I have been easily able to recreate it over the last couple weeks since I got my hair cut. I will definitely be back to work with Emily in the future!

The building is beautiful, and parking was easy in the lot adjacent. Take the elevator up and enjoy the wonderful space they have at cocoon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emily Easton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlA0J4TScsWCTyHe10Hx0QFx1hHk1ayj_kReGsISMIRyf-fQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I book with Abbey Arthur at Cocoon. I’ve known Abbey through the years, and have been very pleased with the transition to her new location. Abbey is fantastic. As usual she takes such great care of my hair, and is always helpful, and pleasant. She’s so welcoming, and warm. I appreciate the fact that Abbey continues her education, and feel she brings the very best to not just myself, but all of her clients. As far as Cocoon goes- it is beautiful, well lit, superbly decorated, and really nice to walk into. Welcoming atmosphere, great products, and of course there’s the adorable doggie. LOVE IT!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Ruth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEKPQfGMjFgyXe0UAW83UC_HkLeOMHnvJBb5wBP5EkrI8Udw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at village salon! I came in for a wash and style, and the results exceeded my expectations. From the moment I walked in, the staff was welcoming and professional. The stylist did an excellent job! My hair looked fresh, smooth, and perfectly styled. Highly recommend for anyone looking for top-notch service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jim Hillenbrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQR4ao7a1yEF0L-ufPTYrfSdfBhuFzBc85W-JlxKXPkBx19g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called today and asked for an appointment with Chuck and to my surprise he had a 2:30 open for me. (I'm a bit of a procrastinator, and I wanted to get a fresh cut before Christmas) He had me in and out in a half an hour and did a great cut as usual. I mentioned that our new Pastor at St. Helena asked me after my last cut \"Who cut your hair?\" and so I recommended Chuck at Village Hair to him. The church is just blocks away so it would be very convenient for him. I was even thinking of getting him a gift card for his next cut just to steer him this way. I found Village Hair some years ago when the Cost Cutters in Highland closed and Chuck has treated me right. Thanks, Jim","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jenice redmond","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNWs4C4eAVZFWUyGAGzIYzUZRm3B-6mvROOilJaU0l7N5WX6JO4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have mixed reviews I saw Katie Today . My haircut was very rushed ... but she did great  waxing my eyebrows. She is one fast talker and a sales woman that's for sure. Before I knew it I was getting highlights I asked for subtle highlights.... most of them except for the big one down the middle are subtle. She tried to sell me everything but the kitchen sink. You don't want to go in to get your haircut and feel like you're at a car lot I just stopped for a haircut after work and spent a whole days wages😒","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORp_Xph-w4vAk4rNi4gWEetbTuFosKdtx5aM_L\u0026fid=0x0:0x7463615dd4682ee0"],"When":"2022-9-3"},{"Name":"Tiny Tails","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1eArKiauDYHCQIS11q0Sqxk2EZYIoW2X8LLV7ferJYkm14N4c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I just got the WORST HAIRCUT OF MY LIFE from Chuck/Charles Harness at the 34th Ave location in Minneapolis. I have (had) long hair, and asked for a trim taking off the bare minimum with some added light layers. My layers are now shoulder length and I’m devastated. Each side is uneven, and the face framing is uneven as well. I had to repeat myself several times because Chuck straight up was not listening to what I was saying. Instead he regaled me with stories about how his pet bunny used to “r*pe his dog”. He also asked me if I was single while we were in the store alone together after dark, so it was incredibly uncomfortable and creepy. I tried to stop him when I saw he was going too short, and he assured me it’s just because “it was at an angle”. When he asked me if it was too short, I said yes. To which he replied, “you’re just not used to layers”. My hair is short and uneven and horrible! Don’t let this person destroy your hair like he destroyed mine!! Photo evidence to prove that this isn’t a “Karen” review.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcPj3qJJMlxK9wRoNbPS0xr3sTbDTVm8qN40E0\u0026fid=0x0:0x7463615dd4682ee0"],"When":"2022-3-16"},{"Name":"Faustina Duval","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgVhfw2ZegB3WlOC2l9QONx3npQFplyMdV9ZvoPTPWGLegoNE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lela cut and permed my hair and I’m super happy she made my vision come true :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jean Stilwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9kxk1qZlvUELwkaAr-R9ur_hPMe10_PhUtxvNxxpSCx_65w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck does a great job and at a super wonderful price. I wouldn't go anywhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shor Salkas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4PsItX7Im3_-NLhi1F9M-9gG-ztNRtHWV0Z5BFpsd8w0jImk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ugh I don’t know where to start. I usually get a fade and leave some length on top… when I asked for this Chuck said that sounds too short for a ladies cut. I don’t get my haircut to have my gender critiqued or assessed by hair stylists. My hair was not faded and it is uneven with long stray hairs. There are clumps at different lengths. The lines and sides were not cleaned up at all. My stylist’s hands were shaking holding the clippers.\n\nTruly, I would never recommend a haircut at this establishment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Howie Gerstner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUv2l9A2Kffjj4Hbi4JhibGGeDldb3TliXOySF8qULeSZpj9_IaQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Couldn’t get into my usual barbershop until the next week, but needed a cut before then, so I went looking for a chain haircut shop thinking that they would have openings right away. I got an appointment next day. Service was friendly, but I simply didn’t get the haircut that I asked for. I asked for a fade on the sides, but got a straight cut instead. Furthermore, I have a lineup on the front of my head that has to be cut back very carefully; the lineup was pushed back a full half inch, and now I will have to grow it out, as it’s not really a lineup anymore, I’m just missing a huge chunk of hair on the front of my head. I really thought I could go to any barbershop and that I’d be able to receive a decent lineup and fade, but my faith in chain shops has been even lessened. As I said, friendly service, but the cut was below average. I will not be returning.","Images":null,"When":""}]
