user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Danielle Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvUNNsEtm4ob6uRQOT_4mYXCmtWseaAZvCZpN7PlAYGghbLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is easily one of the best salons I have been to.
The vibes are immaculate, and the staff are incredibly knowledgeable and skilled at what they do. I see Mack for everything I get done and could not recommend her enough, but every interaction I have had with any of the other stylists has always been fun and welcoming as well. Which helps a lot for an anxiety riddled person like myself.
All of the experience I have had here have been nothing but friendly and professional and you can really tell that the stylists love what they do and want to help their clients. Plus my hair always looks amazing when I leave! I have and will continue to highly recommend Wild Hare Salon and Gallery.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Saige Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1UAVy2U6opJxElAYLASONg5tjnEahxEXwmR4wl7BXx_HnRjHu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The salon's decision to hire a stylist with a history of mismanaging client credit card information raises concerns about their commitment to client security. Furthermore, the departure of the salon's only skilled stylist, due to bullying by coworkers, suggests a toxic work environment. MANY clients have expressed disappointment with the services provided, citing significant financial expenditures without achieving desired results. Rachel, Cindy, Amylee, and Mack are among the staff members whose professionalism has been called into question. Jess works some hair magic, and I'm so grateful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rose Heaphy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6H03-sxW3yjsrDM0v209E4iC5Qh548XXddSkkQjfVnLGWMkfLTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I go to Bang Bang for my usual trims and eyebrow waxes and the service is always great. I can't say enough nice things!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eva Hurtado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV9-RsmtpxLn0k7mvSzT1iP8LbqYWCtwMLaQJIDYJwUHJzimCq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw Brianna for the first time looking for a new color and stylist. My other stylist moved so I'm relieved! I would definitely recommend this salon to anyone and everyone!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carly Huber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAViXJuXQtSSkds9fwmHfovHdIryhi8j81tDveh6HX4zwr4H1j=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of my favorite thrift clothing/hair salon stores of St. Paul, the owner is very sweet, the stylists wonderful, and has a wide collection of really cool, authentice or odd men and women pieces (experience: went in looking for something and found an original 1940's St. Paul Girl's Scout dress for $25- no joke, fit like a glove). An awesome place to go on the weekend with a great coffee shop right next door!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lydia Nielsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWv1Onj6aiDpy9oh4TDI69oSB-bKVuAJXX9BUBy6b9n2Fqge2ha=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a really cool spot! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Erika Ent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1Q8Asu89eZF9MD8fvNb6p_GPCU7LciswQCIzwvKF1pONRxvhj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a wonderful experience! Kimber was so caring, kind, and gentle during my facial. She was so knowledgeable and the service was exactly what I needed for my skin care needs. I will be back for facials 3-4 times a year per her recommendation :) 100% recommend to friends and family. 10/10! Nora at the front desk was also so sweet and courteous over the phone and at check out. What a great team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ariel Weygandt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_Dra6vh1sZWA0z3T_Xhy1yCLPWYEoPXkqjoHVyXO0Aj-tMQsZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is a long one but I’d say this is more for management for hiring someone who lacks the professionalism and experience to be a decent esthetician.

The esthetician whom I love moved locations and is now outside a reasonable drive (though after the experience I had at Riverstone, I may revise my definition of “reasonable”) and I needed to find a new waxer. I found Riverstone as it was close and the wax prices were reasonable. I booked a brow and bikini wax with Kimber.

I’ve gotten many waxes in my life, and this is by far the worst I’ve had, from a technique aspect as well as professionalism.

Firstly, Kimber made me extremely uncomfortable. Waxing can be a pretty intimate experience, and you expect your esthetician to be professional and respect your body. When being waxed, I expect the only touches to my body to be when you’re waxing me. On the contrary, Kimber was constantly touching me, squeezing my arm, my shoulder, my leg. I’m not touch averse but when you’re half naked, you’re in a vulnerable position and an esthetician should be hyperaware of that and keep their hands to themselves when not performing the asked for service.

Professionally, she needs a refresher in what is appropriate to say to and do to your client. At one point she joked that when she left the room she took my jeans so I couldn’t leave (I had to check because I honestly wasn’t sure if she had). Who says that? (she also informed me she has said this to massage clients, as well)

She also sprayed my face with a rose water toner without asking (I wasn't getting a facial, so nothing like that was necessary). What if I was allergic to something in it? Or sensitive to wearing scented products?

From a technique perspective, she did a horrible job. Worst wax I’ve had by far. My brows still had short hairs (ones that should have been tweezed out if the wax didn’t get them) that I saw when I get home that I ended up removing.

During my bikini wax, Kimber didn’t ask me to butterfly my legs, which is standard procedure. When I tried to do so, she asked me to place my legs straight and then just waxed the top of my bikini line. After my bikini wax, half the hairs were still left (and obviously further down the thigh didn’t even get waxed). I honestly couldn’t believe she thought she’d done a good job.

I asked for her to wax my bikini line again and even then she didn’t get all of them (I went home and tweezed those out, too). She also didn’t remove the wax residue from my bikini line, which meant my clothing stuck to my skin (sadly not enough to take out the leftover hairs). I thought using oil to remove leftover wax was Waxing 101?

Apparently, she doesn’t do waxes from the waist down, which begs the question of why the salon booked me with her.

Kimber also took a very long time to perform two basic waxes. She spent more time talking, spraying me with toner, and trying to convince me to get a massage (she even commented that I would love “getting squeezed by her”) than doing any actual waxing. I was there for any hour and still got two terrible waxes.

And I still tipped 20%. What is wrong with me? (honestly, it might be because I was unconsciously worried she might follow up if I didn’t)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karri A Dieken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCIAxICZV2ZLloOaP7gR7IRb_KUQkTw_a3dG5lOiuS5VS_0oyC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I went for a hair cut, please note other times going to this salon have been successful. Last Friday I went for a hair cut and the stylist cut off four inches of hair to give me a mid length bob. She then proceeded to curl and style and I thought she was just being nice. Come to find out after I washed and dried my hair that it was choppy and I’m even. Now I have to go to another salon ti fix this mess. Worst experience ever. I will never go back and will not recommend to anyone.

Worst part is I have been growing my hair out for the past year and now I have to go even shorter to fix the mess that Cherie made. Do not trust your hair with her.

Update: 4/11 the manager has reached out to provide solutions to the issue. The manager was prompt and professional and understanding. I appreciate her time and feedback and resolution. I have changed the review from a 1 for the hair cut to a 3 due to the management reply.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0RPwNYfqZdAYVsxPsHOXGLsRI4dCrjBAtAb0c&fid=0x0:0xc700d95559a76dd9"],"When":"2022-4-11"},{"Name":"Elizabeth Kujak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk1sn3WpfGAfCXpa7n1GHwoirVN0rO6jQJj3aB0vYvRIXaVAkM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What an amazing and welcoming atmosphere. It truly helps you relax and be yourself. I received a facial from Ashley whom was so kind and explained everything in great detail. The owner and ladies were full of joy and laughing - great to be in a positive environment. I had some amazing conversations! Service was amazing - I will be back here for years to come.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tamra N-H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVKrva0J2YeDobtL0iP7KSJSKzU4f6cZdVyQrpjAI6-eS5wZk8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Tl;dr the customer service was good but the actual manicure was terrible.

Ok so unfortunately I didn't have the best experience. I went to get my nails done for a little gift to myself for working so hard over the holidays. I went in and the customer service at the front desk was great. The lady who did my nails wanted to chat the whole time. I don't mind a bit of polite small talk but  I mean the entire session she talked. Whatever, some people are just chatty I just sat and listened and tired to be friendly. When I got out of the chair she helped me grab my wallet out of my bag and helped with my coat. When I got out into the bright winter sunlight I could see that my nails didn't actually look good. The polish is thin on some nails, see pinky, and in some place and the top coat doesn't go all the way to the cuticle, see thumb. I just expected better and was sorely disappointed. I don't think I'll be going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqpzT883-HZJp8hNUkiIJWqOkQQUudRelWNe_J&fid=0x0:0xc700d95559a76dd9"],"When":"2020-12-27"},{"Name":"Andra Bauer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0TTiR4ylHf831kEo6_a0pNsfyEqsCtz1VPRkEm53HQhhRkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had cut my own hair and came to this salon to get it even out. The stylist and I misunderstood each other, and she took an additional 3 inches off my hair. She suggested an inverted cut would look nice - which I’ve had before so I agreed. To me it’s more stacked in the back and was so sort back there she had to use clippers on my neck. I was mortified but paid and left the salon to think about next steps. The hair cut was so awful to me that cried every time I looked in the mirror for a week. I wanted to shave my head. I contacted the salon about this. A lady called and spoke to me, asked me to send pictures (I did) and then never heard back from them. I’m living on a budget and paying $80 for just a hair cut that I hate more than any hair cut I’ve ever had in my life, and then never being offered a solution from the salon is really disappointing. Don’t go here, and if you do, make sure you’re really explicit in your request. Asking to have the length “evened out” because you like it does not mean cut off three more inches. You also don’t need to cut it up to the hair line in the back and stack it to make an inverted cut. My hair was shoulder length and barely touched my ear lobes when I left. It was also super unflattering for my face shape. The stylist told me it’d be super easy to care for - it’s more work in the morning than I’ve had in years. She clearly didn’t take time to understand what my hair type was.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beth VanderHeyden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUipsG3TxJaRZNTKNv181WgA57XT8yBHrYmekqnHRpM3jds83jC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to Riverstone first for a massage then came back the next week for my first haircut in six months. Mary gave an amazing massage. She used a few different techniques and paid more attention to my back per my request which made for a really great experience. I left feeling so relaxed and refreshed.
My haircut was done by Ben, who was also wonderful. I told him a loose idea of what I was looking for, and he gave a great consultation based on my hair. I could tell he was really talented and experienced, and I felt pampered the whole time. My hair looked incredible afterward. If I was a celebrity I would hire him as my personal stylist.

Also, I felt very safe the whole time. They're taking great precautions (screening questions, temperature checks, plexiglass at the receptionist desk, didn't sit right next to anyone at any point, etc.) and everyone there seems to take those precautions seriously.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dyani Acosta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVftJDBJ_p9zMEsaKQuirNkwFYkrAY7jrEkmG9oNH709tmdwim_UQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were able to fit me in at the very last minute and did a WONDERFUL job on my hair. Listened to everything I wanted and I was able to see the results in my haircut. The environment is great and very reasonably priced as well:) I totally recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Liz Barton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkB2_r8yLhQuVxG2xFhTcd2Zyc9x8373d-dFUzEATVGwVyDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had my first appointment there the other day. My stylist was Tanya Wyatt, and she was amazing! Very professional, did a great consultation and helped me decide what to do when I wasn’t sure. I got a fantastic cut and color, the best I’ve gotten in years. The salon is clean and beautiful, they were on time, and even were able to fit me in last minute (I made the appointment at like 8pm the night before online). I can’t say enough good things about Tanya and the salon, and would highly recommend them to anyone!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPD-NIaUqwiGWxXSNEue3_ci3eTzQ_vEdwTVs4r&fid=0x0:0x5549898f7b8623ec"],"When":"2022-10-11"},{"Name":"Jennifer Holyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWd_vFNqByUQ-Qtb9Fo_yMsBP9sfrCxgz9vPV563dqH810Td8o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tanya made my whole year! Every detail from online booking to easy payment- and every creative, beautiful, professional moment in between - was an absolute treat!! She is a gifted and careful artist and I could not be happier or feel more gorgeous and taken care of!! Thank you!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joanna Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQPMsaRRzcgVmlIxmYSrlZ6mVf7cKiGI0CM5WFmSI6Ubn7-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing,.simply amazing! I made a 3 am appointment online because I had a wedding that weekend and received the color of my dreams! You know when you walk in with pictures and there is no way you will get that result. We know it ladies, it is a dream, but Trae nailed it! He didn't shame me for my box dye job ( I live in Northern MN, give me a break😂) and managed to provide the exact color in the pictures. You, Trae, are an artist with a gift! Thank you for sharing your gift with the world! ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sherry Battin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUp8iyLvkbwO3jJpQ44zopiV4HhYrK8IA47InbpTxEke9lCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Derek is the best.  He's been cutting my hair for 11-12:years and he's really good at it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olga Gutarts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_CuhkqsYq2rQ2Lr8jN1PillHqWOtsCyItB6tCH_XC4RtVIwg4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Don’t know about other stylists in there, but definitely not going back to Becca. I came for a root retouch and the colour turned out fantastic at first, so i was very happy. But only two weeks later all the grey roots were showing again. She didn’t do a good job covering them at all! Also when blow drying my hair, she was extremely awkward and didn’t look like she knew what she was doing. My hair is only shoulder length, so blow drying it is not a difficult task for a professional. Whether or not it was just a fluke and she was having a bad day or simply lack of skill, I am not leaving my money there again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjYxNdE98SxbChTqOJomYPXHwXuTb5bN0OddtZ&fid=0x0:0x5549898f7b8623ec"],"When":"2021-2-14"},{"Name":"Nicole Gerber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5ZN7zg12tPdvzrlOJAYJ4fNr5BtNjtilXEb_1mDWAiSUrqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wish I would have found this place sooner! I’m never 100% happy with any haircuts I get, and I usually say it’s great and sit in my car and cry. This was definitely not the case today.
I booked with Trae after having this salon recommended to me and read the online reviews. I usually have a photo with me, but I just told them what I wanted and showed them uneven parts of my hair that I wasn’t sure could be fixed, but hoped maybe it could at least look better than it currently did.
They knew exactly what I was saying and did exactly what I had envisioned in my head. They even asked and made sure that I was ok with the amount of length I asked to get cut off, which I was like wow, no one has ever double checked with me to make sure I wouldn’t regret cutting off a few inches before. It’s a simple question, but I have to say I really appreciated them making sure that I was sure. The conversation was great and didn’t seem like a strained or awkward one that usually happens when I’m getting my hair done.
Anyways, to make this very long winded review a little shorter, I walked out with an amazing haircut that I felt confident with and looks incredible and definitely did not sit in my car and cry!
Thank you Trae!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deborah Velasco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLK-9So2uct4km8rrpD1AL_RojCX-pW-48eVgSVAskSef-FBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been looking for a hair stylist for years and today I found her! Jamie thank you so much! Everyone loves the cut and color, specially me! See you soon for the touch up and Brazilian blowout.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8__oLMdXU7dSuqxP46J48x7SAQcHmJcU3sI2s&fid=0x0:0x5549898f7b8623ec"],"When":"2020-6-3"},{"Name":"Neva Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2yiAWojxTkibdPUSkIuj3ahnBYHT89n2lOYkI-ZTx1evp-B_L=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw Katie today- oh my god she did SO amazing!!! I got a full foil, and she got my hair exactly how bright I was picturing. Can’t praise her enough, and 100% recommend her!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Z.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQ4Jb_kzziFRJjXVUypG488hpDw5OwDlBaPkly9Dvb3w3Q9715=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I saw my stylist who has recently moved to DOME, Emily Angelo (@emlyanglo), and it was lovely! Emily is, per usual, an amazing stylist who makes magic with my mixed curly/wavy hair. The space itself is in a wonderful location with plenty of bright light, and the products they use have very subtle smells and are perfect for folks who don't want unnatural stuff in their hair.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOD-hz1gcdKvfN7SlMclYsjJ-yuPtD5841sOgmU&fid=0x0:0x32aceedae3a0da17"],"When":"2021-1-4"},{"Name":"Mac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBMlP68F6ZBjuF9u-WkcwMdz03N7yo-D6AM5HW-dZJ_TghpsU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best salons in the cities! Owned and operated by one of the most talented stylists who always thinks outside of the box and pushed the hair ‘norm’, Tanya.
Along side her are a handful of extremely creative and lovely people who are dedicated to their crafts. The space is so well curated from the waiting area, to the shampoo bowls with hand laid tiles and a custom mobile installation above.
Ample beautiful plants placed throughout the space in hand crafted pots. Well thought out product choices for use and for sale. The crew here are always pushing boundaries when it comes to hair, and you’ll never be disappointed when leaving. Plus, there are several lovely food and shopping choices within a walking distance. 10/10 recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBMfRp4SaSFw8SrdxzHKuQhcTumkBcqFa1Jsf5iHVieoITjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tanya has been my stylist since she was at Rocco which was a long time ago and I've been following her around the cities since then. Dome is a lovely space - small, quiet, so many plants and a calm vibe. Also wonderful that it was started by a group of friends so it's a nice community.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Livingston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_8zXzPSU0fYIe7pHFRijORNOnYiZhcQ89KiLRw-c4wg8yln3r=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always an amazing experience here! Tanya is so talented and intentional in her interactions with her clients. She is great at cutting your hair to flatter your specific features, and all of the artists seem just as skilled. The space is welcoming, clean, and gorgeous!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIulFslK6wjchTDeA3pHdk_FNkc6cqHfjIqqi8X-Y8KWRWvhA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best salon in Minneapolis! I see Heather for full highlights and she does amazing work - close to the root, natural blond coloring and uses great products (color doesn’t fade and blends so well to my natural hair color). I see Madoka for my cuts and she’s the best. Cut always shaped well and on trend. My husband sees Madoka for his cuts too and she does a great job with his curly hair.  Love the space as well, very NE vibe.
Steph Bagley","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tara Miko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhEGGFAqemrxUjgPEWzZw9XGn16B1dm4TkNZtAsJsAQcZaNYBv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got my hair done by Madoka- a lot of friends go to Madoka because of her expertise in different textured hair. I have very coarse rough hair and she cleaned up a lot of the dead ends - I got the perfect haircut that compliments my natural hair texture.
Also the inside of the salon is beautiful and has a wonderful atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-q_5EDod5aduy5feTzqc2xbdRJtAGsuv-bOU&fid=0x0:0x32aceedae3a0da17"],"When":"2022-1-25"},{"Name":"Erin Babineau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUviEgCI1rxchzmGtRenwiYIAlShg9CbV6U6jG41rBxgqRhp3Nh_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Madoka is the best! She is such a great artist and has helped me embrace my waves - she is attentive to detail and makes my hair feel so great. Thank you, Madoka!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Kaja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUywkuNUGE3T8XEmQGYHHH9Rt2UcnK_7FBPjyL1GeFgq_iZtQus=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"In case you were wondering...Emily Angelo is still the best. I lived out of state for a while and was relieved to get in with Emily when I returned. I have coarse-ish, wavy-ish hair that is starting to gray and that I hate to style with heat. I show up not knowing what I want except for my hair to look better.

Emily gives me a gloss and cut that are exactly what I wanted but didn't know how to ask for. It grows out beautifully (at least in my opinion, which I suppose is the one that counts), is easy to air-dry  with just a touch of product, and keeps me smiling. Already looking forward to next time :)","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ellie Martinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocID_1IFukWRO5B6PCO0lurxnPuX_WnzWzVWj7mPMQSsH6eywkX7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience here! Hannah was very professional and went above and beyond to help me understand my hair needs. I walked away with some new product and feeling happier/more confident about my hair than I have been in years. The salon is also close to plenty of food/coffee entertainment, if you want to make a day of your blowout. Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOg5u2AbarQ_ujG-bNJP0GVDLGAJqF1FIB_xqNa&fid=0x0:0xcc747badea8d81bb"],"When":"2025-1-17"},{"Name":"Lily","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRqbiO2TiUwjUbS0ExgDnf0Zc_j_AWvH_81nWZ77SJ_9PlUFI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you are looking for a personalized hair experience this is the spot to be!

To start, I am a very picky individual with a high attention to detail and I can wholeheartedly say Defy Hair MPLS will have you leaving their salon happy as can be! They provide a clean, respectful, fun, and positive environment with an open and accepting mentality. Not once have I ever felt judged but rather treated with care and kindness.

Audra has helped me achieve and work towards all my hair goals! She has a genuine passion for hair paired with a highly experienced ever growing skillset. Seamless she took me from a full head of galaxy colors to the iciest blondes with a full set of custom toned extensions. All the while not leaving a strand of color behind. Just looking for a haircut only? No problem! She will work with you to achieve all the hair goals.
Her skills are unparalleled when put up against any other stylist I have seen in the past.

Defy Hair MPLS is amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOebXTWJOTg6Z_FZcdbrGyNhn76extvb5rYWqDi&fid=0x0:0xcc747badea8d81bb"],"When":"2020-1-9"},{"Name":"G W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3LlbN8AbH9zNly42IQuIKQNpgGU0bkdJt9GK0em-Tei8JKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome, independent, hair salon with the coolest vibes. Bright and welcoming atmosphere with a nice street view. My FAV part of the suite was the art wall.

Booking was fast, had my consultation on a Friday and my hair appointment the next day. Prices are reasonable and they depend on what you are looking to get done.

Claire was my stylist and she was attentive, professional, and very kind. She was also enthusiastic about me becoming a potential client (which was a big plus for me).

Overall very happy with my experience and I recommend Defy Hair 100%","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeoqZbkwqzkpdzdIHNS9PNv6WHeHFjwGzWYpBI&fid=0x0:0xcc747badea8d81bb"],"When":"2020-1-7"},{"Name":"Joslyn Schmitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR9g7GVx2KG38AOhB-Injcpea5G3EcNfw01ieYO1vIusXq-6Mi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I never had a hairstylist till I met Claire 4 years ago. Ever since my first appointment I have been going back to her every time.

Claire is AMAZING at her craft and makes me feel beautiful and cool every time. She is always attentive to my request and references and always does an excellent job meeting my expectations. One of the main qualities I admire about Claire is her drive to always learn and expand her knowledge and skills when it comes to hair.

If you are looking for someone who is super positive, a master at their craft, and will geek out with you on anime/games, I highly recommend booking an appointment with Claire right away! <3","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Carrigan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX07pP36G7momOplUmRDqYNxeBE_w_iKEykDZDZVDt8GBPRfG7c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to numerous salons over the course of a couple of years asking for a particular color/style and was told it wouldn't look good, or couldn't be done, etc. I was fortunate enough to get a recommendation from a friend to see Claire and so glad I did!! They did a fantastic job and expectation was reality! Pretty rare for hair color in my experience!! Will definitely be going back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eva Camille Roethler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRqVtP9D0mFjSuZ5zDD8ZDHFSB8ALTAOXxlEFhBMMQzeYYTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had my first cut with Audra at Defy and I cannot express enough how impressed I was with my experience.

First, I look and feel great. Audra is super professional and made me feel instantly comfortable, then gave me the best haircut I've had in years!

Second, I shared that I have disability that can make styling a struggle. Audra caught this and gave me a very accessible hair tutorial at the end of my appointment. I can tell Audra was paying attention and it made me EMOTIONAL that Audra took the time to make sure I had the tools to style my hair in a way that works for me. A+++++++ for accessibility and inclusivity.

Third, I absolutely LOVE the pricing structure. It is gender neutral and based on length!!!

The only warning I have for future clients is to give yourself a little extra time to find parking, but I TRULY can't recommend this place highly enough! Do not hesitate to book, you will not regret it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Carlson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6GWtvKFS1-hxOa8fvqU_AvjmvOiU8yVaj8RxpoGV9-GSFSio=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Defy Hair MPLS and Audra have been great! They did such a wonderful job on both hair and makeup for me and others in my wedding party. I opted for a trial run of my hair before hand and it really helped relieve some of the stress of making sure everything  was perfect on the big day.

In addition to that I think Audra has been able to color and cut my hair better than anyone else. I receive many compliments about my hair from friends about how much they like what I am doing with it and the credit has to go to Audra. She always goes above and beyond!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lysa Lea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqd9vrd1vihg7xa1P2dOaZDCJIYmF8-sGYDfXa4s9KDWt4Tg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this salon so much! I just moved here from LA and Claire and team take such good care of me every time. I come with ideas and Claire makes magic happen. Life long customer here!
For fellow curly hair havers, Claire knows what they are doing! I’ve been consistently impressed with my cut and style, they understand my curl pattern.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnr8D1h5b6Av65Cz2Pe97RqtVHi-e-KKvQaN-z&fid=0x0:0xcc747badea8d81bb"],"When":"2021-12-19"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Amanda Weber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUt9nd00PUqv9S6alYvcn142nWJ6RcIcGc_uGxatWmCQg_Wm4KY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I want to give a shoutout to Alyssa at Pompadour for the wonderful bridal experience! I didn't have a wedding party, so it was a pretty lowkey appointment, but Alyssa welcomed two of my friends to come along and watch. Both in our trial run and on the wedding day, Alyssa was fun to brainstorm with and receptive to feedback. All of the other hair stylists kept swinging by to sing her praises, especially for updos! She gave me color, braiding, twists, and curls, and then my florist helped to add a comb... I was so happy with the finished product! AND, it held throughout a very windy outdoor wedding! Thanks, Alyssa!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONkre-Olz-uUhYqiTRw0PJ-qyFWqXbA7LEyycU&fid=0x0:0x418d037d59a77ac2"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Marley Prichard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLacx8JrSkVPLQeHTHKCfi8mu22lVnFso6_zVWzniG69-OkGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cute salon, reasonable prices and great service. Helped fix my messed up at home coloring and got my favorite haircut and styling here! Never gotten so many compliments after getting my hair done. Shout out to Tatum specifically.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLah26u3Q-KFp7OVhKGi37R8mhlAKneOaBOyNLWaTnN5C6vxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lindsay at the Nicollet Ave location is awesome!!   She is skilled and listened to my preferences.  I'm super happy with my haircut.

I want to leave another glowing review each time Lindsay cuts my hair. She understands my hair type and has the skills. 10 million stars. Her haircuts have me feeling good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyTUOR6Jwn_clvvWWX3NjHYUbnaMDcYSyD8Gzuqd6UrGgmYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am not a regular salon goer-but decided to treat myself at Pompadour for my son’s upcoming wedding. I was much in need of freshening up my drab locks that weren’t greying in a desirable way. Stylist Amy took very good care of me. She knows her color craft and is sweet to the core. I am so happy with the practice wedding do, a vintage wave that pops my new balayage. Really feeling fabulous about Amy fixing me up for the actual wedding day. I cannot stop admiring my reflection!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Berth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHN9J6xkThmm3ue5aLHofEw_5zorceo4T0_8GYeBdyxxNANg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an awesome first experience! The team is collaborative, creative, and talented! Lindsey and Sadie both helped me go from a blah color to a bombshell redhead!

UPDATE: look how beautiful this color turned out in my fall engagement photos! I could not be happier!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaqFPjtvy59jPjl7s6y6ff3YCMN3CQNQXzDvn8&fid=0x0:0x418d037d59a77ac2"],"When":"2022-10-23"},{"Name":"Anna Benson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3WV1WJYA7ZYf4YjXqE10mlTfdgsQGfMasgJFDpu3bo5Qwexo9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service! The place was very clean and orderly, and the staff were all super friendly. Huge thank you to Sadie for the best haircut i've had in years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Babkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLJ1DPm9lJATrrqGZNBpYv6l1yeEdKxsV-bKdr_N9NqsX3Nb9i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pompadour is literally amazing. From the minute you walk in, you're greeted by a bunch of wonderful women who are not only incredibly skilled at what they do but some of the friendliest people you'll ever met. I have stylists that have never even had me as a client remember my name and say hello to me when I come in and they're all genuinely lovely people.  I've been having my hair done by Steph Perry for over two years (she is a miracle worker when it comes to hair color, wow-ee) and have yet to have a single even mediocre experience with her. You have a very specific hair dream you want? She's got you covered. Walk in indecisive as all heck and don't know what to do? She's got ideas. I get compliments on my hair just about every day.  On top of that she's an genuinely charming, funny, and darling human! If you're looking for great service and a super comfortable/warming environment, you've totally got the right place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs3HDZVkgcmQdSdQ3WeL5VbawYVtBMq6ub9CYR&fid=0x0:0x418d037d59a77ac2"],"When":"2017-12-6"},{"Name":"NBK","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMUpZtAQ2BQNtObZweVOvFrJ9Zf_nk43plQZzHXJNOgRXURGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lindsay is fantastic. I have a bit of grey coming in & she lightens & blends a good mix so your hair is not fully dyed ( a partial) It grows out softly, is bright & looks natural. She’s excellent at both cutting hair & coloring. Book her ! You’ll walk out happy.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Carrie Tetting","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqLGck4SuA0DG-35d_4t9Kumhy85tRHrGhDdz3NWjmbNITQnH5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been visiting D'Anna for awhile now. She's wonderful and fun to catch up with.
I'm pleased to have found this charming salon in my neighborhood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjyRlheASQJvu2vV8tTYiv0yx0oLg84hhUZBivRar5YyQQxwuiJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was fortunate to get in with Eric after he had a cancellation and I couldn't be happier! I have wavy/curly hair & he took the time to ask about my current hair routine, what my goals were, etc. Based on our chat, he recommended a game plan & got to cutting. He really understands curls and how they behave, so he dry cut of each individual curl and all I can say is WOW! I look & feel fabulous & already made my next appointment. Thank you, Eric!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsOVjoBpy5E2RETotMh5iPZnZj35VYh1cza_4urwIRUHkYHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great first experience with Eric. My hair is long, thick, and wavy/ curly.  Eric really took his time analyzing my hair texture and condition, and gave good recommendations. He respected my wishes to only trim a little off to freshen up the ends so that I could keep the length. The salon was also very clean. Will definitely use Eric as my stylist going forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebekah M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZhkyN4IUbWihlYEj186lvbjI0roBWRvCQLiL1l33PITYU9WnXfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice, chill atmosphere. I absolutely love Eric as a stylist, great guy and awesome haircuts. I followed him here from another salon and couldn't be happier!! And he really knows curly hair--I usually just let him do whatever he thinks will look good and I've NEVER been disappointed. He'll mention products that he's using or give recommendations if you ask but never tries to push or up-sell. Great stylist and great salon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayli Kerchner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5WekdgXFsyPX6ZQhwe0LhCk6tPm9xUApMaSzjXRpelYUYH2LZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Apostrophe salon is the best salon, no doubt about it. To start off, the salon itself is so adorable and designed beautifully. Super clean too. There is a good selection of quality hair products and makeup as well. D’Anna is the best stylist (and person) ever. She truly listens to what you want and gives her own thoughts and opinions as well. She makes everything look wonderful. She is also a super great listener and super friendly and kind <3 Highly recommend, you will not regret it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Conti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFfd6f3vtiH8eIBjK85GvdFhDumwTG-x3NGLAS8kG6WrV_T0qClA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I followed Eric from the Hive to Apostrophe 5 years ago. He gives great haircuts. It always grows out well. I have fine, curly hair - which is usually really hard to predict - and it always looks good (when I actually style it - hah). After years of more conservative haircuts, I entrusted him with a hipster sideshave breakup haircut...and it always looks awesome and grows out well. I get compliments on my haircut all of the time. All of the time. Eric will also buzz the side of my head and do a neck trim for free. My girlfriend's stylist charges her $20 (apparently this is a thing), so I'm thankful for the quick maintenance.

I was also super pleased with Covid safety measures. I got my first haircut since January last week. I am probably not getting another one until the summer, but the situation felt very low risk compared to a lot of other experiences I've had.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Composey Music","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmDELIdRhp9nugzLWTHyGy7KAihSGWrktAw-z68AK96T-foA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love my haircuts and styles at apostrophe! It’s a calm space and I feel like D’Anna really understands style and the needs of her clients. I’d highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sophie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR9H11K0ejP27Z2u4q3P0_dCGw7gsANOju4ctOKuYXbY0jEjTp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a refreshing salon experience! Sweet and clean and bright space with a relaxed vibe and personalized attention by D'Anna who really listens. My hair had some 'color challenges', and thanks to D'Anna's expert skills in coloring, my hair turned out far better than I could have imagined.
If you're looking for an 'unhoity' salon where the vibe is relaxing, where there's no annoying loud music and where you get personalized service by a real pro, you'll find it at Apostrophe Salon. I couldn't recommend it more.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jennifer Haffeman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0QLEATafHwbNxEsIwQbamZyahfK5uobQod8WRwtV2TeCOLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just came back from a 1 1/2 hr massage by Caroline who owns Alpha Sports Massage and it was the most incredible experience.

I have in my life over 100 massages and this one stood out as one of the top!

Not only does she offer 3 different levels of intensity for pressure but she asked during it so you can change the pressure if desired

What I loved and have never ever had was after each section of the body she grabs a steam towel and wipes you down so you don’t walk out greasy! That was incredible!!

Lastly what stood above any other was Caroline asked as I checked out if they was anything she could have done differently to make the experience better! What a professional question.

I will absolutely be seeing here in the next couple months. She is truly one of the BEST!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPieAZjpv6VXaRFXjP-uIQfR-_dtsOPpE2EW5Wu&fid=0x0:0x24676f0a8f45fc20"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Kate Sobraske","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcbECKNly_sGwE0xGGuiz_pzLi3R5KMVGQnzO2pcerMj6itA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ella is the only person I let color my hair. I always leave with dimensional color and soft, shiny hair. Coloring can be harsh if done improperly but she makes sure to keep it healthy and strong.

She also takes time to know you as a client. At my last appointment she said, “This new product just came out and I thought of you immediately. Do you want to try it?” It was perfect for me and so nice to have a colorist who knows me and my hair so well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZx942t-LrZ1oeGtK7E7woCKThBiBK4Yc-WTp6&fid=0x0:0x24676f0a8f45fc20"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Jennifer Cao (Jenny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcWD-DlSFlP6hy-ZxY06uCyOsH6iA_y-buucBO5klb5UN7vJ6MVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love love Lisa-Marie! She's been cutting my hair for almost two years now. 😊
I've got thick, straight Asian hair that's lacking any sense of movement+volume, so a good, layered haircut is crucial to prevent me from looking like the head of a wet mop.
Lisa-Marie is experienced with my hair type, fast to respond, detail-oriented, and honest while still taking my thoughts into account. My hair has never been softer, shinier, or bouncier .✨ Honestly I just let her do whatever she wants since I know the end result will be great LOL. She also did an excellent job refreshing the vivid green color I already had in my hair so it really popped in my wedding photos. 💚
Definitely give her a try if you're looking for a good hairstylist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristina Rootes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIx8CoamcerNlDFxRWCIujx1MmdsixxB34KjrmuaEp-9VGutA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience with Jen H. Not only is the salon is a great area and super cute, but I felt so welcome the whole time. Jen H did an amazing job on my hair, making sure to take the time to ensure she understood what I was looking for. I absolutely love my hair and would highly recommend!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Isabelle Bailey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVRMOGYEEkuHbyXD461D8BY9pwRy0zrUDlLoNfj91l9YB4s7U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Jen H. by a friend who had such wonderful things to say about her, and I'm so glad that I decided to book an appointment myself. Arch Salon provides a warm and inviting atmosphere. During my appointments, Jen pays attention to detail and takes the time to understand exactly what I want done. She makes sure to ask questions throughout the appointment to make sure I am happy with how it is turning out. Hair days are the best days with Jen. I can't wait for my next appointment!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracy Olsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSR2Yyaj5X3LtjfD5Y-Qh5vZ5pW6Jxgp_QJTiaQvetBGOw8wqB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lisa-Marie is amazing!! I needed someone who could cut thick Asian hair, and I'm so happy I found her. I used to drive 1.5 hours to get my hair cut by her before moving to the cities. She's 100% worth the drive!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vivian Perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQdmN_n3YuY3mF7wNH8sQKsjU9w0IfHBOSNEdhpA4SEo0W6etS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"i just moved to the twin cities area from chicago and had initially gotten my hair done from a salon down the street from me when i first moved here. i showed an inspo pic and got nothing close to what i had asked for. i was extremely sad, disappointed, and overall lacked confident in my self because of my hair. fortunately though, i found ella (@thatvividsmagic) on ig and reached out to her to see if she could possibly fix my hair and she sure as heck did. she was able to turn my inspo pic into real life and has helped me heal my inner child as im rockin pink hair right now. so if you are looking for fun, vivid colors, or any type of correction for that matter- ella is your gal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMofK4KCoJh84_qkBcF-d0KhouW5l7CN6s8DIU0&fid=0x0:0x24676f0a8f45fc20"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Drew Dravis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUK-pOE88YBiHPbBLbNXuJ3Z8vgBETS3y1_3ukPBCQ49HdmBGk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had just recently moved to the cities looking for a trustworthy place to get my hair essentials done. I found this place through Instagram while searching up people to do fun colors and I haven’t looked back! Ella who does all my vivid hair coloring is PHENOMENAL. Genuinely so good at what she does. Trust the process with her because her end product is always a breath of fresh air. Seriously she works magic. I’ve also gotten my hair cut here by Leila and she was great, especially with the layers! Overall this place is clean, aesthetically pleasing and from what I have experienced the staff is kind and great at what they do. I plan to come here for all my hair care and salon needs! <3","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Abby Christopher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2-8dsUFEaSGGoRA6u8Aj3SKhv_4OeQ3iXCYdHMAWgGydZTwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A special shoutout to Kelli, my stylist of over 3 years! She always makes me feel confident and brings my vision to life, allowing me to be creative with my hair. Kelli also works around my shunt, making it more comfortable for me to wear my extensions with her magical expertise.

I also want to give a shoutout to all the stylists at Hair Police. They’re everyone’s biggest hype squad, and I’ve never experienced an atmosphere like theirs in any other salon. Patricia was super nice and did a great job on my hair and eyebrows. I got a simple cut, but she took the time to style my hair curly and twist individual sections (which I don’t take the time to do myself). It looked so nice! She was great and listened to what I wanted and asked what my goals were. She didn’t pressure me into anything (an issue I had with a stylist at a different salon). [{"Name":"Diana Magnuson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXib1X9lK7IH6FXztPycVDWZgtlC7puVCxQZk9p111hfm7pBvU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bringing my hair to life! Part 1.

Super excited to finally go back to blonde after letting my hair grow out for two years (new mom and former blondie 👱‍♀️).

I’m very happy with my results so far and excited for my next visit soon!

Anna has been very informative and able to deliver the style and color I’ve been looking for!
She understands what I’m aiming for and gives great suggestions, I trust her with my hair!

I went into Blondeluxe in effort to go from brown to platinum for the sake of humor + a photoshoot. Changing my hair color for the very first time, and hoping not to just have to buzz it all off made me apprehensive to say the least. A las, I went in after many recommendations along with the salon director's [Martha] and saw Steph. From the opening of the door, my nerves were quelled and I felt confident it was going to be a great experience. This was in January of 2024.

Today (literally), I am leaving the salon having done the exact same thing but with the very talented Anna - Steph is on holiday for a very well-deserved break to all our losses ;) - but no matter, Anna proved to show that the whole team is not only well-rounded but wildly talented each in their own right. Thank you, ladies, for another terrific trip into the salon. I appreciate your professionalism & hospitality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXCEUfcS_5zAxHeWincncR4ETk-VdtMmg7ouuk&fid=0x0:0xe3ee7c0204ea8506"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Julia Poor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_yNCpJO2pCFwo_9oL5Upyui7ayRxqF1vZ_T0kpmcEtVA0lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to see Megan to get my hair done for a while now. I always leave feeling so much better than when I come in :) can't wait to go back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1hQJPns6aAcYoKijoyQsNohjHHGYnfT13FJv0&fid=0x0:0xe3ee7c0204ea8506"],"When":"2025-2-21"},{"Name":"Hannah Zaborowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZWYhOM77oZHUoNcsqc-ZofCjagSjkkQtXAJg1z0MHLovSUnhV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Anna is the best! Always so welcoming and my hair always turns out amazing.. so many compliments! Always recommend her to anyone who wants the best hair ever 💗","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rae Ganci Hammers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWoQHSABe_FJKAV7NJwXlqKXfkhHbamaf4NlOjYwvZyB6McfTk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every person I've interacted with at Blondeluxe has been terrific. Knowledgeable, professional, friendly, and crazy talented. Stephanie (color) and Kiana (cut) - in particular - are stellar. Stephanie took me from a bleach and tone routine (from another salon) to a softer, more natural look that works beautifully with my dark natural color. I've gotten so many compliments. I appreciated the pre-appointment consult with Stephanie so that we both knew what we were getting into. And after seeing my hair, Stephanie recommended Kiana for a cut. Also a great fit. Both artists listened carefully and asked the right questions. They built trust by making suggestions after hearing my thoughts, ideas, and concerns. I feel like I won the salon lottery. Wholeheartedly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cassandra Caola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVuZo8jBltrKa_uKXIJwlAXZEMWkChPSAxIB8w0dmnbwhQ2R0-sA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I WISH I had started going here sooner!

I was your typical "toe head" with white blonde locks growing up, and to maintain my blonde over the years, I started getting highlights! I've been twice now for dimensional lightning with Maddy, and she's nailed it each time!

Maddy highlights with small pieces of my thick, fine hair, leaving my natural intertwined. It gives it a nice look when it grows out!

Happy I found a new go-to salon in Minneapolis. The products they use here (I think Keratesse) are really good, too. I will be back for more. Thanks, Maddy!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNv3UbcfT80HhgWfM0BmAzFQU55voi2exMYNt7G&fid=0x0:0xe3ee7c0204ea8506"],"When":"2024-12-31"},{"Name":"Anthony Abousweid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8bEdRoEhPsT3zQShB-rHew5WE23OonxndxeAnBUrkK3jy5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Walking into Blondeluxe was one of the most uncomfortable experiences I’ve had in a long time. It was freezing outside, so instead of sitting in my car burning gas, I decided to step into their lobby—a lobby that clearly exists for people to wait in. From the moment I walked in, the blonde woman at the desk locked eyes on me like I was some kind of zoo exhibit, just staring, saying nothing, making it abundantly clear that I wasn’t welcome. Then, as soon as someone else approached the counter, she suddenly made a point to mention locking the door—as if my mere presence was a security risk.

I was obviously just waiting for someone, but that didn’t stop her from addressing me with a condescending, almost irritated “Can I help you?”—as if I had wandered in off the street looking for a handout. And the audacity didn’t stop there. Apparently, this place charges over $100 just to take out eight tape-in extensions. Insane.

If you’re looking for an overpriced salon with a side of passive-aggressive hostility, this is the place for you. Otherwise, I’d strongly advise against walking in—especially if you’re Black—unless you enjoy the feeling of being treated like an intruder for daring to exist in their space.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"My_Superpower Is_Awkward","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIloip5OyxplyoK25V4uMnAmd71b_iqmfrqNe1tIsj4grQXDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve gotten haircut from both Damian and Stephanie and I can’t recommend either of them enough. They’re both very chill and easy to talk to. On top of that they do great work! All of the other staff there are incredibly nice and welcoming, which lends to the good vibes that you get while you’re there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christian Calabrese","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqQIyRufJkz1d7afX3Nd702-HzLA5zo4ODjTv3qRjXNILGtyx2sw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere; I was seated immediately upon getting there. My stylist, Kris, absolutely knocked it out of the park: extremely personable, and meticulous. There were several moments I thought the cut looked great, and she would say "on no, we're still in the rough draft phase!" The feather & layering was flawless, and the short cut was made "to perfectly compliment my head structure and cowlick." This is the best short cut I've ever had in my life, it feels like not a single hair is out of place, and I'm incredibly impressed. 10/10 will go again; the price is well-worth the premium experience and attention to detail.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peter Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1IOFhpO3KFKBa6QvRKULbecmW2pgVq39klR5kbh7q90_80Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kris was freakin awesome! I’m so happy with the cut, and had a blast chatting with her. I will definitely reschedule with her.
The men’s spa is a nice place and very comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJuwtf6LuMaBaR4npbvV401leEn2JeZ_UdC5EsDlc69DGakA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"In a matter of 8 months, the salon last minute canceled three of my appointments. I've been with salons for multiple years and never canceled on once. To be canceled on 3 times in less than a year is unheard of. The options to reschedule were in one case weeks out. I am understanding to a point, however, you have to question the stylists you employ and realize that customers book appointments well in advance and plan around those appointments. Based on other reviews, it is apparent this is standard practice at this salon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nick Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyoFPzZyUUmkdYvzo67luC9xXHkrETCL04ymckAELWzkkP30wy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jaeger was the best, used to come in and see his brother but after today I'm so happy with the fresh new style that Jaeger gave me. It's fun to reinvent your style so if that's what you're looking for, definitely stop in and make an appointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Max Utterberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqpBu0h4V8rykku7yUC5uDvcQLkrtj5nmX2NMGm6_jNClhB63yJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Darry is an excellent barber! My haircut is always on point with him and we have a fun conversation. Strongly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anthony Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu2XRX9hantMyYKWZKUd2AbO8AutKGZ_SBmEZsFKH2Gno8l7pEbw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've found this to be a very comfortable place for my spa needs. Always clean and I like the modern salon styling too. Damian is my go to for pedicures, he does all the steps you would find at a resort. The massage chairs are great. Highly recommended

Cailee did a fantastic massage and facial. I highly recommend her. Very friendly. I drifted off so many times. It felt like I was on a tropical island escape. 🤗","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZjLp_8N_tFoyUp-XoKkXsPwOSKdDvzQT6N0S7&fid=0x0:0x9b7d0306f5477709"],"When":"2018-11-8"},{"Name":"Leslie Cain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYPaaKL8u_37nrqWRj4pp2ROc0roEIXW6CC477u69ZM9oiKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kat is my go to girl now. Great conversation and always a good haircut. Makes me wanna come more than I need to just for a relaxing afternoon. Find your person here and stick with them because it’s a great salon.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shawna L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEU3mtCfkGI1xVcj0nHCB3vtoHNpOZc54JNZnCnAyDW5Yer3DA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Margot has been cutting, coloring, and styling my hair for many years. She's extremely knowledgeable and skilled at her work. She has a great eye for creativity and is so gentle and caring with me when she's doing her work. She listens really well when I have an idea of what I want and works with me on anything new I may want to try. The salon is always a welcoming environment, everyone who works there is super sweet, there's lots art on the walls, and it always smells really nice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michele Lindberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVe_QY_ugUPXYofXafQy4G1Db2eMOAWKjqQyGxWs27_pfuKXGCG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found this place through a coworker. From the street it looks really nice, it could use a little touch up on the interior but I'm still going back. Margot gave one of the best cuts I've ever had.
I have fine long hair but I like movement and pieces around my face. She did an incredible job. Both her razor work and scissor work look fantastic.  I'm going back for color soon- I'll keep you posted!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terra Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVj0i7LBwLFHMPRvEJrT2QzbJilw3d6RZxpFyunoWD8R0A-sBlFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tenille is honestly the nicest person and always cuts my hair exactly like I want. Even if I'm doing a poor job of explaining myself, she takes the time to understand my wants and turn them into a reality. Super recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gina Zech","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRlL5jh6lJ1882FPiOB6UcgaVNkmahiYU5GZaS4Jfj4ZML9g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is amazing! I’ve been going here for years. Tennille is great and always gives me a fresh fade. They don’t offer a senior discount but the cut is worth every penny! Would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Wimber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCEo12zuZZ0EJ1AGdK7WYdL9tObBetqCxXj5SYyZArHZnmG6BD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Margot is a color genius. She thinks not only about the finished product, but about longevity as well. My color always fades out perfectly between appointments. She can do fun, punky hair, as well as trendy styles. Book and appointment today!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-BP94dtmTsTyehXRG9E9OcGVFpSNWhHkWjKYfUSO_kaEOKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a phenomenal hair cutting experience. Abbey was recommended to me as someone who would help me with a major transformation from long -> short hair. Abbey has an incredible fund of knowledge and ability to apply what I said I was looking for to an amazing haircut and style. Abbey advised me against a hairstyle I thought that would be flattering and recommended other options. She did this tactfully, kindly, and built trust. It was a big transformation for me, and I could not be happier with my results. I left the salon literally glowing (per my sister who I immediately FaceTimed upon leaving). A few days later...I still look good - even my bedhead is stylish!

I am so happy that I found Abbey, and I think you will be happy too. It's not just me, she has other glowing reviews here as well. She truly made my day and I cannot recommend anyone more. She has definitely earned me as a return customer in the future. I am so grateful that I chose Abbey to transform my hair - I have the utmost respect for her and her work. You will be in good hands.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"lizzy hinman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnjmrS8HvFMKeA2WqZpzNY3X0P3AU_mn0VSgyJmaFT5M1-AsbQ1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tennille did an absolutely AMAZING job with my hair. I came in with some work *needing* to be done and she was fabulous about taking my hopes for my hair and making it a reality (and explaining her process the whole way). Great experience all around - highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kami Marie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqJlmpq9bqJMq9sMSBxGWyK5VAhpPGM0HOLAw4F1aGNCVliDfpTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Abbey!  I had a bad cut from a prior stylist & she knew exactly what to do with my moppy hair, and my new style looked great.   Wonderful personality and expert skill.  The salon itself is very clean, and you’re always greeted with a smile.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jane Kuusisto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEqEuVK6pAFIlHU5TuJExghnX3ishU2PGRXu_XoBeEA4SXF3de=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a girlie who has had her hair done so many times she can’t keep count and had every hair color in the rainbow, I cannot recommend salon abe enough. Woman owned. Super cute. Best stylists in the twin cities, what more could I dream of?! Reese is amazingly talented. The care she put into my hair, is unmatched. Kenny sure knows her way around a money piece. I went from a dark reddish color, to the most amazing blonde of my life, all thanks to the outstanding talent of Reese and Kenny. Awesome staff, don’t hesitate to book an appointment if you are ready to SLAY.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayla M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEAiAwqSyad8ljZRIHbgKLZ6W3REqxn8AfLfdDM8odgalvWXdI4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Megan R (the owner) is a fantastic gal. She was my stylist in Dallas, Texas and was loved by all! She has built a beautiful salon here in Minneapolis that is cozy and inviting. She hand picks her wonderful stylists who are kind talented humans.  If you want a wonderful stylist l  recommend everyone here💕 McKenna and Reese have both done wonderful work on my hair and I recommend them to everyone.
They do excellent work.  I have found my forever salon here! If you're looking for a fantastic stylist you can't go wrong with any of the stylists at Salon Abe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbjaxFkKV2vShY9VIUSkuKgEq3wTmO8C8xm2zc&fid=0x0:0xef3be90e369adb55"],"When":"2024-2-28"},{"Name":"rosalie harrison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUFgzuCE4lsyGl3aOBpZC5rb7kUGHywAMwsXafPHld-3g6fE73=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"McKenna did an amazing job on my hair and makeup for my wedding. She listened to what I wanted, stayed true to my inspiration photos, and made adjustments based on my feedback/comfort and using her expertise of what would work well on me. Both my hair and makeup held up all day through a sunny, warm, outdoor wedding. I felt so comfortable through the process and the outcome was beautiful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jackie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOJLNxIWCZiTQDP3xYwI31tJ1Zmeuy-Jyv-eXw9SMNrBRPUMmb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reese always does a fantastic job with my hair! The salon vibe is calm, clean, and modern and they are so skillful with bringing visions and requests to life. I have loved my experiences here and appreciate all the care that goes into their services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonas Ness","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGpzqYB7WXrq811siexVoPwNLh0ALgXM7bbXeZvOj9x7Q9ihSE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hair is in this awkward stage while I am growing it out. In addition, since I work outside, the sun has bleached it out into several shades and made it brassy. I was looking like a total goofball. But I visited this salon and had maintenance cut and color session with the stylist Ashleigh Leick. She cleaned me up and brought back my color to its natural look. She also gave me some tips on how to keep my hair healthy and manageable and how to style it until I reach my desired length. The studio provides a comfortable atmosphere and is very clean and cozy. I highly recommend Salon Abe and I will be booking another session with Ashleigh soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Seaberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRijl5Fon828z1ueJ0w2vSEIFIzPF_QcFURIdBi_h1bahGzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have had lots of negative experiences with businesses, but this is the first one that was so bad I felt obligated to warn other people.

I was recommended to Reese by 3 different people I know.

The first several times I went to Reese was fine. Then I decided to go to a darker blonde. I always make sure to express that my biggest fear with going blonde is having my hair turn orange.

The second time we went darker, my roots were orange. When I was in California, I had it corrected by a top level stylist out there. He referred to the color as “Chucky orange.” His take was that she was using a product that works well on light hair, but that should not even be considered on dark hair like mine. When he finished my color, it looked normal and great.

I had Reese only use toner this time, thinking that would avoid any potential issues from using the wrong product. It turned out orange. When I politely asked her if it was supposed to be orange, she looked offended and immediately went on the defensive.

She told me that toner was supposed to make it look orange when applied to the the level of blonde it was. Maybe she didn’t listen when I said I don’t want my hair orange - I don’t know. I can’t understand why, if it was SUPPOSED to turn out orange, she wouldn’t mention that to me beforehand when we had agreed on a sandy blonde.

Ego is okay if you are really good at something, but if you are not good at it, having an ego and refusing to apologize for your mistakes is not okay.

Apologizing for making a mistake goes a long way. Reese didn’t once say she was sorry. She didn’t charge me for the toner, but it am now forced to walk around looking like this until I can pay someone else to fix it. She didn’t once offer to correct it or do anything to compensate me for the fact that I am forced to walk around with orange streaks in my hair for at least a week.

Aside from not being a good colorist, my opinion is that her behavior and customer service skills are highly unprofessional. I would absolutely warn anybody against going here for any reason unless this is a risk they are willing to take.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjM4KRzFQLemgjgaAZNWPgrFEmBjZFplhrMfub&fid=0x0:0xef3be90e369adb55"],"When":"2023-3-14"},{"Name":"Natalie Bigley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPN6dWbIMknURu_Te3DI12xhaeOxIg0Xa_RZ_YKsMqvZFWTVgN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Megan/Reese (she goes by both!) at SALON abe is a 12 out of 10! Not only do I always get compliments on my hair after I go to her, but I just generally enjoy being in her salon. I love the decor, the conversation and the relaxation of it all. And of course my color and cut are always amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_4bIN_nTdl6nnBvZ016w51_GSBQRQvmvHe_d_&fid=0x0:0xef3be90e369adb55"],"When":"2020-10-28"},{"Name":"Mary Beth Gallagher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVKVc3GH2_bv_jQbsYiAvmG2nMZFWls2ddL-ijM94TfgVDDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the first time I’ve ever had the same (wonderful) hairdresser for a number of consecutive years! Reese is it!! Amazing at consulting, magic colorist, great stylist. I almost hate to review for fear it’ll be harder to get an appointment. ;-) AND…her salon is beautiful! I’m beyond grateful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbwCo6HqfGRB_IgMnSVzEoeBTEbpb-shEzegiH&fid=0x0:0xef3be90e369adb55"],"When":"2022-7-25"}]

[{"Name":"minjun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1yIMBtv_Yv237P9YgO11p23LtJ6_IBGjjH0ffrimWhBYVUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"don't ever get a hair cut at this place. I was there and told them to give me a wolf cut.
