user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Hanna Gebremedhin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYOw-9C80MheOVpI0T-689Gw87jvq8MQD-e3EHwUREAWK2YWM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I felt it would be helpful to write an objective, unbiased review of my experience at Get Gorgeous Salon. I saw Ilka and had a wash and blow dry with a trim. I also have natural 4b hair. Let me start off by saying that I appreciated how quickly they were able to see me considering I didn't have an appointment. Also, the ladies there were friendly enough.

The wash: I expected this to be the most relaxing part of the experience, but it unfortunately wasn't. The stylist was trying to forcibly comb her fingers through my hair during the shampoo process which was unnecessarily painful. The wash itself was ok (a little on the harsh side), but I think it would have gone a long way if the conditioner had stayed in my hair for longer than 2 minutes. 4/10

The blow dry: I did not enjoy this at all. For those of us with curly/coily textured hair, gentleness is the name of the game, especially since our hair is prone to become more tangled after a wash. I wish the stylist was more patient during the untangling process instead of forcibly running a brush through wet hair. After a few winces, the stylist attempted to change her approach but not by much. 2/10

The cut: This is where the trauma happened. I mentioned that I mostly wear my hair curly - I wish the stylist would have taken that into consideration, cutting only the ends that had damage. Instead, she cut my hair so that it would be "even" while it was straight, which meant much of my hair was unnecessarily cut to satisfy the stylist's goal versus accommodating the way I normally wear my hair. When I came home to "re-curl" it, the amount of length that I had lost was beyond what I was expecting, even accounting for the normal shrinkage when going from straight to curly. 0/10

Final thoughts: The stylist is charismatic and may be great at other services (i.e. silk presses), but I would not trust my crown to her for regular maintenance. I hope this review proves to be helpful to the stylist and honest feedback to prospects, coming from a woman who made the appointment with an open mind and left with a discouraged heart.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5NZmzTVGsRoYzYp7Mq5pc4Ytn2bFXkMsZOTw5zsmTuoz26VZM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a consultation in which I had call ahead to inform them of my potential delay which they noted was fine. I ended up being on time for my consultation yet I sat and waited 5-10 minutes while the person I was meant to consult with had a conversation right in front of me. Once she acknowledged my presence and we began the consultation in which I asked for a straight sew in I was asked why I didn't want my own hair texture. The consultation was very rushed, she was very short with me and had poor attitude and customer service. Still I booked my appointment despite my gut feeling telling me this wasn't the place for me. At this time I paid a 100$ deposit without an appointment date and I was told the service would be around 200$ and that she would have to order the hair for my sew in. A month and 10 days go by. I called to check on the status of my hair in which I was again met with attitude. I was finally able to set an appointment which was 2 weeks out. They call me 2 days before the appointment is set to take place and inform me that the service would now cost 900$ in total. Very unprofessional, poor communication, poor customer service. At that point I did not trust them anywhere near my hair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia McKenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILiUFHSwHRAlzwysiOuy0EFh74ZiMCmR_cMSKO8YOun3AFXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently got crochet braids at Get Gorgeous for only the 2nd time in my life and I was really nervous about it.

Tasha answered all my (MANY) questions about what style I wanted and what the difference was between the styles I could get. She was so quick during the appointment and I barely felt any discomfort once the braids settled the next day.

And then when I started having a bad reaction to the synthetic braids, she recommended a product that I could use on my scalp to help the itching and it worked like a charm.

Thank you so much to Tasha for being so kind and patient and informative to a very needy client (me). I will definitely be coming back to GG.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristy Pearson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeQ8AdI06bVV0NkITW2sP5HDl7T-HzUzOwSqlKVUAE2Bx7zqzT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is absolutely amazing! No matter what style I had from Ebony or Ilka, I always received so many compliments. From braids, sew-ins, to wigs, they always made sure I looked my best. -Kristy P.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpSN0si8OYBD-YrrKB7a-RpbG_03KfDHBAbeTf&fid=0x0:0x5c6823f96606c25f"],"When":"2021-8-3"},{"Name":"Jacquelyn Burt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvfs88Tio2lBWSj5ZOD5kNWLSK4W9R-J7kEF9oAgBrHB9TZdIF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I scheduled a haircut with Get Gorgeous as a brand-new client. As a beauty professional (makeup artist), I have worked with several stylists in the Twin Cities community and have had my hair serviced by some great ones... and I can honestly say that the haircut and client experience Ilka at Get Gorgeous provided was the best cut and experience I have EVER had!
I often have a hard time explaining what I want, and even when I show photos, I usually walk a way with cuts that are good but not great. I told Ilka in what I hoped was a clear way the kind of look I was going for, but also told her that she could do what she thought worked best for my hair and face. She gave me a conditioning treatment and then began to cut and style, and used techniques I hadn't seen before but that left my hair with more movement, softness, and shape than it has literally ever had.
On top of the best haircut of my life, Ilka was warm, funny, friendly, and professional. The whole salon and the entire staff was incredibly welcoming, and even though it was my very first time, I felt completely comfortable and as though I belonged.
I will be recommending Get Gorgeous to everyone, and will be coming back at the first opportunity!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AJ Butler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqeoufSm4zPPG-GpJB_26m02BnzA7nw2hYB8H4lFLrOXqxpdU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went in for a wash, deep condition, and a trim. Ilka, the owner was my stylist. She was very kind, professional, and very informative.  I will definitely be back in the future...","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sweet Capricorn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxEnd_OXMDEdKvZHFtnhLUGxYjngj1tE9GzSGD03rURww4qpM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got my hair cut by a different salon. I didn’t like it so I booked an appointment here. Angela did a good job she over shared her personal life. No big deal most people do that I meet! She found out who I’m related to at the end of our session and ever since then I can’t get an appointment like she black listed me cause she’s embarrassed or think I’m gonna tell my family what she told me but I don’t even do stuff like that. I’m so annoyed her toxic ways keep me from getting my hair cut. Most places only do weaves. I was born and raised in this neighborhood and can’t get my hair done. I’m so annoyed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"erica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdGIR54j1hPg4mPVbuV2E_sKGRmqPSZN9-Jy-n7PxtQN8zeOImCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely loved my experience at Get Gorgeous! The atmosphere is awesome and so are the stylists. There was laughter and music going. Just real laid back. Ebony is awesome! The ladies are so professional, but it's not an uptight feel(very hard to do!) I got my hair and makeup done. Not for any special occasion, just a late birthday treat, but the compliments I got, trust I will be back! And I'm bringing all the heads that need doing around me. I think my favorite thing I loved about being there is the diversity in clientele. What a great way to unite the community! Black, White, young, old everyone is welcome! Try them out! You'll love them!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Kayleen Alexson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0b5OWieq1pvjr_mpbGoREopsBlI6mF49QT1UOv6U_VDlS3--u=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great cut this week at the HAUS Salon in North Loop. It was my first time seeing Katie - and not only did I leave with a great haircut, but I left with my cheeks sore from laughing and smiling. She's the best - and created such a great experience. And I left with the exact cut I was envisioning - she's a pro.

I have been to HAUS salons countless times over the years for cuts and colors - and the team never disappoints. The vibe, the team, the expertise...all unmatched.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bindu gopinath","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXO2ssxGnU0HhJLhbrrO2MvnEO6Algk68aMI6jE56n8xeh7cNnIkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved my experience with Meg at HAUS. I am traveling and picked the closest salon after checking the reviews and didn’t have high expectations really . However I am so blown away by the salon ambience and service. Meg understood my need and took great care of me . I left the salon feeling beautiful and also feeling I wish HAUS was at Seattle!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taylor McMillan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW65diJ0_Mi3SbsTkVoFn7n_XnCm9c67aSw_y5GbdkCEsCqnuEj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a customer of Haus Salon for close to a decade.  I have been getting my eyebrows and hair cut consistently at one of their locations over the decade.  I am impressed by the talent of the professionals and their care and professionalism.  Everyone whom I have seen has been an expert in their craft, kind and considerate.  I have settled in with my two professionals for hair and eyebrows because we click and they are at the North Loop, which is closest to my home.  Having been a customer at all 3 locations, I can say, I have enjoyed my experience at all locations equally.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaarina Tungseth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDwFYC1wS7IZuE5ZjaTz9Uz-70lZbvzJ81CiCsyvvieazUzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Emily is an absolute gem of a stylist! She consistently works magic on both my hair and my son’s, leaving us looking and feeling amazing every time. I’ll come in with a vague idea, and somehow she creates a style that’s even better than what I imagined. Her talent, attention to detail, and warm personality make every visit a joy. I can’t recommend her enough—she’s truly the best in the business!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna Inthakhot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiN_kvoruwNxId5XICVYyp0r9glaNHaZSsxaMJGZd2CTSkxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Helenka is amazing. I’ve been going to her for the last 3years. First, she’ll start you off with a consult and takes the time to listen to what you want… she asks for inspo pics (etc).. and then delivers a satisfying job. The space is pretty and clean— and the staff are kind and considerate.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaTrnmVxDdAZx6AID2-z0xFzw05Yp6B4xEOjSt&fid=0x0:0x182b055024c574b5"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Kristin Dawn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOHBALgACjbyPRopfgNw7rzX5HyH7fAM5b8Zvp2GNqRFexd8ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved my experience at Haus salon as I wanted a razor cut, pixie with lots of texture. Amber did an amazing job in listening to what I wanted, offering her opinion, and creating a beautiful cut!! Love the energetic vibe of the salon, and the drinks and hospitality was a lovely touch!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRyO6EasxzPSl9Xea7SSNipkMepLp4n6J8ONTY&fid=0x0:0x182b055024c574b5"],"When":"2025-1-28"},{"Name":"Mary Heggestad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYjekx46buaS-f3yW8WlnDj4zyVVdH30fycyD9eMIYJ_TTAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Alie has been coloring my hair for years and  nails it every time! I’ve gone from blonde to red then back to blonde. Each time, Alie beautifully crafts my desired color like a true pro. I trust her sense- she listens to what I want, knows what I like, and what will work best for my hair.
On top of that, she is kind, easy to talk to and accommodating. She never hesitates to sit me back in the chair if I’m being picky about my color. Highly recommend this wonderful human!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Davies","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMHE8r3exU6iKBql4RS3-v5S0iK6jc0dJBl6vGttqrOuMYWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both Kaitlyn and Carley always treat me like I am their only client! They are both amazingly talented and make my experience in the salon a 10. They always send me home with fabulous hair!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Ishida Hill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0_E7gq2cOfEvN-x1ugwLGWD3NlTz_un5mzL8pe7LjpiqimQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are Truly a BLESSING!!!! I got scam from a girl claiming to work there. When I got there they said that did not have my appointment and the girl never worked there. I didn't know what to do. One of the stylist stop what she was doing and went above and beyond to get someone to do my hair. By the time I left their shop words can't explain the joy I felt in my heart!!!!!! HUGE SHOUT OUT 2 BLESSINGS HAIR SALON!!! #Stylist BLESSINGS 4 MY HAIR!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOioCnHvXOrr8q-yC3Q5JKRJAGMV9EDPIKlPOnd&fid=0x0:0xfc22f3504a8a9b68"],"When":"2021-7-25"},{"Name":"Erika Harps","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxgtPxm9H6Zk92d9HZdfpvhBTuyygBl-EWp2TZg17TKbuLEUbj4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This review is NOT against the salon, but against the a stylist name Jackie who works at this salon. I booked a silk n press for my 17yo daughter last week through a 3rd party app called Booksy. The app doesn't allow you to leave a review if the appointment was canceled. This stylist hurried and canceled my daughter's appointment while she was still at the salon trying to figure out why Jackie doesn't detangle natural hair. So since I can't leave a review on the third party app I'll leave it here for Google for everyone to see it!! My daughter hair is naturally soft, long, but not thick. Jackie told my daughter while shampooing her hair, that she complained about she didn't do detanglement, and that it would be extra $$ to detangle her hair, extra money because it was thick, but her profile on the 3rd party app didn't say extra for thickness, only extra for length. On her profile the cost for a silk n press is $85 plus extra for length.  She basically was trying to get 145$ extra out of my 17yo daughter.  So my daughter texted me from the salon bathroom about what was going on. I told my daughter to leave, we'll figure something else out. I went back on the app booksy and booked my daughter a new appt with a different stylist who only charged 80$ for s/p and 20$ to trim her ends. We are sooooo glad we didn't do business with Jackie unprofessional service, but claims she specializes in natural hair, but didn't have the tools to detangle non thick hair lol! My daughter said she was doing a sew in when she walked out! So apparently this the real reason Jackie didn't want to do my daughter's hair. See pics from new stylist below the very next day! The new stylist Detangle her hair with no complaints and didn't charge xtra for detangle, length or said her hair was thick! My daughter has never had thick hair she's 2B hair type, more like full and soft but easy to comb but never thick we've seen way thicker.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWT9eqLGvicIu1e5hB-GY_Pmx3cmspw0trmPsO&fid=0x0:0xfc22f3504a8a9b68"],"When":"2024-2-27"},{"Name":"E J P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNkpONytQXGGyECeUPirRtQCx62dMN_jc7vozozYMtQdgBjSDq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a Blessing to find ✨Ashley✨ here at Blessings! She is one of THE BEST braiders for children's styles! Her stitch braids?! 🤩 Not only is she skilled, she's efficient and patient with the tenderest of heads. My daughter and sons stay looking fly thanks to her styling! 🔥 She's a gem in the industry!

✨Ms. Jackie hooked me up with my 1st quick weave and it was 🔥!!

✨Lakeira styled me with a hard set (pin curls) and they turned out beautifully!! 😍

✨Aris installed micro-links for me and I am IN LOVE!! He is multi-talented for men and women's styles and cuts! 💈 🤩👏🏽🔥

The salon itself is clean and comfortable. It's a one stop shop with braiders, natural stylists, weave installers and barbers. I highly recommend booking an appointment and checking them out! 💎","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyinlUie8xFVyrORvO8fSnXd9ctwW-XZ2fLgCj&fid=0x0:0xfc22f3504a8a9b68"],"When":"2023-2-22"},{"Name":"Danielle Huff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRnNtSB6mNsuVnnRKgXs8YZ4mfEaByvv8zSSQgx3YQaRR_AA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just horrible, I was told to come to my appointment at 7am , she showed up at 9am with a weak excuse, kept telling me she is only running 20 minutes late. When it was time to do my daughter hair completely ignored her, my daughter texted me please pick me up… never again, and they they support black business. What a joke","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theola Ofei Budu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfL4fmIN_4xdjI_OmuA16y_LW_mKQQniILRjCE_W2tuvuD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lost a chunk of hair from getting a sew in , lost all my edges . During the hair appointment she wasn’t focused doing other people’s hair. Lost soo much hair. Now I have a bald spot","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sejun 22","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLv5Dr_wC0bnI28Tn-N7oRH-wdKxBj-dML7n3cD-DNm2mO4xA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Yesterday was my first experience with this hair salon. My 9 year old daughter was booked to get her hair braided by a woman name Blessing. She was not prepared at the scheduled time and moved our appointment to 2:30pm. Then into 2 and half hours later of braiding my daughter hair stating “ I can’t do your daughter I don’t like the way the braids is coming out , she has a perm, I don’t do hair with perms.”  She was lying because she was not skilled to braid well nor did she have good time management. She also mentioned she had another appointment waiting. As my daughter was presenting to be sad I started comforting my daughter and talking to her as the lady begin taking her hair down. She told me to “ Go sit down over there”with attitude and unprofessionalism. Of course I refused and requested her to speak to me with respect. This was such a bad experience for my daughter but I’m glad I handled it well and told her it’s nothing wrong with her the lady just didn’t have good braiding skills or good manners. Look at the attached picture. I would say the manager Adele was very nice and kind. She called to apologize and offered another hairstylist I couldn’t accept that was such a bad memory for my daughter birthday. Go to another stylist that had skills and respect for their customer not Blessing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIDqsPtbDoaVuyHww4QrUY2dgtDAoch5GZrBa7&fid=0x0:0xfc22f3504a8a9b68"],"When":"2022-1-22"},{"Name":"Cathey Mayes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0KfhwrU-D2yq32pJUnE4cy-NkSsHA-CfX6S-yX_UGyGjylA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My daughter's stylist was unavailable and she was referred to another stylist named Jackie.  Jackie embarrassed my daughter in front of the entire salon by making rude comments about her hair.  I would not spend a dime in this salon if this is how patrons are treated.  Her comments were not funny and my daughters feelings were very hurt.  She also gossips about other clients and is very unprofessional. These services cost a lot of money, and to be mistreated as a customer is unacceptable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonique Suggs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWHgpsr5mcpZWaljB_65twM-AUSfnUwlUpDONPUJWRqb4H2ZXr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I don’t usually leave reviews but…. This place needs to be shut down. The rudest place I have ever seen. They don’t smile, they have attitudes, they don’t communicate or handle situations with clients good at all. They don’t even look or talk to each other… just an uncomfortable rude tense vibe the whole 5 hours I was there. And why did it take 5 hours for a wash, trim, braided straight back without extensions for my daughters hair. Jackie is the rudest, unkind, laziest, person ever…. And it’s sad how all these reviews says the same thing “their rude and unpleasant,” and yet they continue to be so unpleasant and rude to everyone the comes there. They’re to comfortable. But they’ll have to face the music one day.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Grace Bettenburg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2hCJdqo32IB0BFzgoKaKW68HhmX_FCvlX4a2NX4xp5_5hvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing women’s haircuts and color! Not only do they look fantastic right after the cut, it grows out beautifully with the highlights seamlessly blending with your roots. When I tell people I am not naturally a bright blonde, they are shocked because it looks so natural 6 months later!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abdul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOv0avmYXJ-yX5k5pDC5ivJJ_Q_PUJ4TLedKOVqUVjBTKIg7w5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had my first haircut with Allen at his salon, I was very satisfied with the cut! I showed him a picture before of what style I wanted, and he gave me the exact cut I was hoping for. Would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ann Scott Dumas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX52VHLkWFRveeaaj7yiyqcvZTwFuQG0h7cbLwkZJ1-xtZnFiyN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"No hype... just a great haircut!

I called Allen mid-day today, and he fit me in and gave me a perfect cut. We agreed right away on what I needed, and he delivered exactly that. Relaxed, confident, and thorough, friendly yet focused, he was easy to be with, and committed to doing an excellent job. I left smiling.The first friend I ran into, (a stylist herself, with decades of experience), immediately asked, "Who gave you that great cut?!" I'll be back for more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AC Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZtwWFAfxnPUN5LDExUeAtNMj5uPPKFk3jXn-33IPnlrc5uESR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have curly hair. It’s difficult to find a good stylist. Allen is amazing. Precise. Professional. Helpful. I’ve tried other salons (I think a person should have a couple of stylists they trust). But, no one else compares. As a matter of fact, I’ve needed Allen to fix other people’s cuts. Thanks goodness for Allen!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Johnston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1_3W3N6VevBGH7DWzeJ4CLV4aXroDokqIIYYOJhNY_JPVFShD0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been to Allen several times over the past few years since living in St. Paul.

His cuts have always been on point and quick and even at a great price for the quality of cut you're getting. He even for me in during my lunch break same day.

He's cut mine while is was both long and short and it always turns out great. Plus he's just a nice guy. Cash only, but there's a wells Fargo across the street.

Will definitely continue going to Allen for as long as I'm in the area and he's cutting hair!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christian Engelbrecht","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKo9AxVnOkKXSDcT5PMrBpdTvMK0lOdhymOHH-kCArq-VHK3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found Allen via a google search when I moved into the St Paul area a couple years ago. Even when I moved away to another city in MN I made I kept on going to Allen. Now I live in South Florida and I still try to schedule my haircuts so that when I come back to Minnesota I can pay a visit to his salon. I don't know else to put it: he simply does a very good haircut at a reasonable price. I would recommend him to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"French River","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItbl7c-aQY-Ypw69x3mGV1sLY-vxc94CWt_W68cMVt1vnGHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Allen has been cutting my hair for more than 20 years, and I have followed him each time his shop has moved, now to its third location. I got tired of going to large chain haircut places, where I never knew whether I'd get a good, basic men's cut or not. I pay more at Allen L., but he knows what he's doing and his cuts are always detailed and thorough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Schons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXy62du-gvjBuRP58trWXx1ow6k7SqpXS3uM48N9fJNS6KIoW5O=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by Allen's randomly before a move to NY. Showed him two professional hairstyle sample photos my girlfriend texted me and he delivered.  He is talented and honest and I wish I had found him sooner. Great style at a good price. I recommend giving him a try.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Panie Vang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk5GiSNy2a3X08Pq3YvBb_6i_Xc-U76IzxmCk4ytpTVqQSZXfLAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was able to get a schedule in with an assistant to get my hair cut. I wanted long layers with face frame and thin out my hair what I usually get.  I cut 6 inches feeling happy for lighter hair. I didn't ask to see the results after my cut trusting her cause she kept telling me my hair is jut like hers, the thickness and texture. I had it curled to finish off. But after I washed out my hair and feeling it I realized it's not even layered. Feeling disappointed after i arrived early and waiting passed 30 after my apt due to either they were over booked or being behind plus being patient with her jumping from person to person. I even gave her a tip of $10 because she was very nice and talkative making me feel welcome. I would not recommend coming here if you want to get your hair cut.  I feel they special in hair color.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0yvwu0BgxIl3-xNTeTps3I38ZNOjsXXfvaFQq&fid=0x0:0x95b4cc13912ba5b3"],"When":"2022-2-22"},{"Name":"Vonta Proeun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ9JwzrG1X40QMvquEW0EOxGykEVEwB9eHhgfUZsuO5XRsY7I3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Quynh's Beauty Salon. Quynh is very professional and maintains an open mind with the client's needs. I had a great experience with getting my hair color as desired (she ensured that I was satisfied). If you're looking for a change and are contemplating what to do. No need to worry, she can help alleviate some of that stress. With a hair transformation that you'll love #STYLING","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPChQ4mSp1oiQ9fkhO2iBW_-MgqQXa9C50hhK72&fid=0x0:0x95b4cc13912ba5b3"],"When":"2020-1-9"},{"Name":"Tuyet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvsEYkOH8QBqAXOiakNqJ147Oc1XwrSXQLfn0ohDUsIOWCRpVtnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Quynh really took care of my hair. I really love it! Definitely recommend!

I came back the second time to update my color, it wasn't what I wanted and my hair got really fried and ugly. My shirt was bleached on the back. I did get a small comp for it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLSijGIc3LqC_n4rFuVKf8gvwTTWA9HS2J0k2B&fid=0x0:0x95b4cc13912ba5b3"],"When":"2021-2-25"},{"Name":"Enma Yama","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtOXhtvmJfbF5KfL3QQhLZvYRGUQkCa2eclkAx12RUs8qF_E08=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I LOVE Quynh! She knows how to work with Asian hair. I’ve been to many stylists and she’s the only one who knew how to properly bleach Asian hair (so it would actually lighten). She’s great at doing bright and vivid colors too. I completely trust her with my hair. The last bright color combo I did with her lasted four months and lightened to a soft pastel color, not some gross washed out look, which amazed me. I’m thrilled with my new color combo and am looking forward to the next time I visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucy lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEU5lxCkLiMt6eAW4tdLsrWnT2I5B7xVfWrFB1grVhz6dnsgGJdA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Quynh, it was my first time there and I was a bit nervous about dying my hair for the first time! She made me feel welcomed from the second I walked in. She's very professional and honest with hair coloring options. Her price for hair service is not too expensive compared to other places I've seen. She's very easy to connect with and so full of energy. I love, love, love the outcome of my hair. I will be booking another session sometimes soon. I would highly recommend her to friends and families!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MAI HER","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQvilAkl212cQUOTZrUPQyJ1wGJSAn4Vv7e9gXaRIJ3f8qxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quynh is definitely a naturalist and does hair with compassion 💞 What I love most is that she can spontaneously surprise me every time I’m undecided on what I want to do with my hair. She’s such an enjoyable, fun person to be around with and I always leave so full of confidence and life. Not only that, my two daughters also loves coming to the salon with me and getting their hair done as well. Thank you so much for your outstanding service!
Thanks again Quynh for making me so much prettier and feeling so much more confident! You are the best!!! Love you 😘!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkhaj2vuCElES95HccHw5ZRcygkOM74p_Ka5yIn877tzJsxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I first came to Quynh earlier this summer. I had just gotten my hair done at a major chain salon in the area and was left with an awful shade of brass. I searched desperately for a salon who knew how to treat and color dark Asian hair. I was due to leave for a trip within that same week and couldn’t go with my hair looking orange! She explained the color corrections that would be needed and was very thorough with her explanation. She was able to take that brass/orange tone from my hair and made everything cooler, natural, and with a ton more dimension. I went back to Quynh for the second time yesterday. Since I had spent all summer outdoors and in the sun, my hair naturally lightened and started to pull very warm again. I swear my hair looks even better this time around because she was no longer working off of a terrible color job. Quynh takes the time to get to know her clients which then translates into knowing their style. She knows that I’m low maintenance and although I do highlight, I don’t like it to be too bright or unnatural. Do not hesitate to book with her.  She is super down to earth, welcoming, and of course an amazing artist who knows exactly how to color/lighten dark Asian hair (and obviously all other hair types). Thank you, Quynh!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xia Khang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0WMCiBwvuFC9I3eRaV2USYuAmdR-H6UxjwcwLjdLMUiN8sw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got a haircut from Quynh and she was so great with the way I wanted my haircut. It turned out exactly how I wanted it to be. She was so awesome, great service and super friendly. I literally felt like she was one of my girlfriends cutting my hair. She also colored my hair black blue and it turned out great.  She is so awesome and literally had a great first impression. She works magic and is so fun. Give her a try and you won't regret.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Virginia Sanchez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIUntBZNrjlh60m_0eqjPn-eOVfmvGFUIE3ihLNoOaIpNkBRP_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a great experience at Mai Hoa salon! I walked in and was greeted and attended right away. I wasn’t able to catch my stylist’s name 🥹 but the gentleman is a master in his art of hair styling!! He has cut my hair 3 times now and always does such an amazing job!!
Three months ago I asked for a bob and it was fabulous. He mentioned that he’d like to try the wolf cut or a shag bob for next time. Suggesting that it might suit me better.
I include this to say that he did a fabulous job at the bob (what I wanted) he delivered.
So today I went in for him to work his magic and take his previous suggestion.
We went with a wolf cut for this cut and he did such a great job!!

Seeing him at work inspired my mom who has curly hair and is usually hesitant to get her hair cut too. She absolutely loved it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZtpQNueyL_QOlWOFBMztO-VQyWTwXR92xNvdD&fid=0x0:0x3f2ebaf933e96013"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Youngmin Joo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZdVCaLs9FF-NpDBzbQ9bczaXfVPiwdf7ED0YbSVEo86OkqVx2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Avoid Mai Hoa Salon AT ALL COSTS. Their cheap prices for Asian hair color are 1000% NOT worth the damage to your hair or the terrible experience.

I used to go here for root touch-ups and highlights, but every session involved unnecessary multiple bleach and tone jobs because they couldn’t achieve the desired color on the first try. My last visit was a nightmare — OVER 5 HOURS of botched highlights, repeated mistakes, and my hair being completely fried by the end. All while they kept bouncing around between multiple clients and losing track of bleach/hair color time, instead of focusing on one client at a time.

The salon is also dirty, with unsanitary seating and unprofessional staff who openly gossip about clients in Vietnamese.

They prioritize overbooking and quick profits over quality or care. If you want to maintain the integrity of your hair and mental sanity, I’d highly recommend spending more and going elsewhere for better results. Don’t let their cheap prices fool you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zaida Garner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBynK9VWltkP7d6gJDGnbN176jBgVNMXzYk8vDPVkr2xMbMiO6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a very bad experience here. For one, the hairstylist had long nails, and scratched the shit out of my forehead and scalp, and I asked for a trim, and make my hair look nice, but it barely looks any different. I also asked for Crimson hair dye.. it looks terrible.. they didn't leave the bleach in long enough, OR the hair dye either, so it looks very washed out. We were overcharged for 120 dollars.. I'm never going back to this Salon again, very bad experience.. the hair dye also had chemicals that burned my scalp, and I have never had this issue with hair dye before. Hopefully they take this as criticism, and not negativity, but I do not like this Salon at all.

I believe it was Mr. Nam I got put with. He did a bad job, train him better with hair dye, Kim, please. And thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jules Parnell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSvHvaRmBGXuVQqOasVRwzSQIFeQVWQkfh605KsTcLLycYLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service at Mai Hoa Beauty Salon. Thankfully the had an opening and I was assigned Tianna. This was the first time I got to see her work and I absolutely loved my highlights and experience with her. Don’t hesitate to give her a chance :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOq8yIHaM7BWbvvEnvlL257XvrPmGO8SPKAUBt3&fid=0x0:0x3f2ebaf933e96013"],"When":"2022-9-4"},{"Name":"Uyen Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwk-IPT8fy_py5wj0DgeTJZqcqG4bCjrXxLltpkwqtY2QGlw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was disappointed with my experience here. this was my first time here and i think it will be my last. i wanted a haircut and a hair color. and i told him i only wanted to cut about 3 inches. he ignored my request and he cut more than 7 inches of my hair(maybe even more) and I was shocked after he finished dying  my hair. he cut my hair and made many adjustments, and my hair was much shorter then i wanted.  i felt he didn't know how to cut hair even though he said he had 20 years of experience. he cut about 11 inches of my hair, i was really sad and wanted to cry on the way home. he should have cut a little bit at a time and asked me if i wanted more or if there was good instead of chopping off way too much at the start and it was too late by then. also the dye that he used really burned my scalp. he said thats normal but i never felt that before.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angelrose white","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhxixyId3dKqO8uks13W1ggMQdG-NOmFOMhezutPyH6i3tlw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing place! I've gone to the Beauty Room for 12 years now to have my hair colored by Mi Shaun.  She fixed my orange hair from years of bad coloring and has always been realistic with my hair goals.  She is the best of the best when it comes to blonde hair.  Another shout-out goes to Vanessa who has cut my hair for years.  She is fantastic at communicating what she thinks would be best based on my requests.  The Beauty Room is a beautiful space with great product lines too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria Brennan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJImzN6BJmkJ_GYGjBHZFNgy9JSQ6kYAVTI_kn8H-JpFQrC-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If you have thick, curly hair, I would not recommend. The individual who I saw seemed very overwhelmed by my hair type and texture. After a cut and color which I was charged nearly $250 for, my hair looked nothing like what I had asked for. I completely understand that working with certain hair types can pose a challenge and that you may not always be able to achieve the look that you desire. Had my stylist been honest with me that she could not get my hair to look that way, I would have understood. Afterwards, I was not satisfied so I decided to reach out to the salon/stylist. I emailed and called for over a month without receiving any response. The customer service at The Beauty Room was incredibly disappointing. The stylist was also a bit condescending, as she stated that she never received any of my attempts to contact her. Thankfully, with both emails and phone calls, you can provide proof. I was able to get a refund through my card company, thankfully. The Beauty Room and my stylist were less than helpful in resolving this issue. I will not be returning to The Beauty Room as I was very disappointed by my experience with them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dana Grethen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWB6jhaEKwrCG9MtyuBZKsE2NsKBfyANpvHuVcHUFg0ADDXrns=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had my haircut by Stephanie and my color by Bailey. Both did an excellent job! I appreciate stylists who listen closely and take time to consult with the customer. I also appreciate when stylists are honest with their feedback about what will look best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jo Turpin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBy9bG7dgg9VpxZ2KCI0rKNZudoV4s_grkbeQqtXplcY5qzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got a lip flip done by Amanda and it was amazing. Super fast and easy, minimal pain and I had no swelling/bruising. She was super thorough and walked me through the whole process and answered all my questions. The procedure itself is subtle but helped boost my confidence a ton! I will definitely be back soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvRtQ2t9KYy2LL5VjzwgljUUbH85KR1GUfByj2\u0026fid=0x0:0x5eca782385ffd5d5"],"When":"2020-11-30"},{"Name":"Caitlyn Meyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-MJrOPcppMPaK24Ils-f6mUK3WRJqMIf2Cn7UWRkUlgh_WeY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Amanda Wippler with above shoulder curly hair dying for some better shape. Went 5 times to a curly hair salon not completely happy each time the last straw being not shaping my short hair anything like I wanted. Found Amanda and one other stylists profile on The Beauty Room website that I liked because they both stated curls and short hair as an interest to them. Booked with Amanda and my experience was 5 star. The Salon is beautiful, just my style. Amanda was very personable and really listened to my needs. Shaped my hair into my vision, added some defining balayage..had me in a week later to make some adjustments to my curls as they were naturally. Didn't push products but the salon has a nice wall of products in the lobby with descriptions on display very nice. I hope to make this my hair home. Loved it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Archibald Chuzzlewit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKl4gmV8uoQ7zFSFsvpm8ENFZinEr7b5VZqvKZnBXyi6T1n1U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Holly at the Beauty Room is the only person I trust with the highly esteemed honor of cutting my hair. She's amazing at her job and a great person. Also appreciate Beauty Room's high cleaning and sanitation standards especially in the middle of Covid.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christiane Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrPAnvyQ4Ggv5myB9_a5xzwG3DIvH5DhlqK2PZfH1_K5OBA37s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Abby is the most qualified Hair Colorist of all times. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Selena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL7duZpbmmW4Zt_40YoxxrcSHc_4vYwBUd_lKxqUOH4oQicZ34=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first experience here with Tamiya, she is so authentic, honest and cared about the health of my hair above all else, she gave me her honest opinion on how we should go about coloring my hair. She gave me a hair treatment under the steamer which felt so amazing, applied a beautiful color, did a trim and gave me a beautiful silk press and also laid my edges. I felt like Tamiya truly took her time and made the best plan for my hair. I will be back here specifically for her! The rest of the staff is also super cool, funny and inviting. The salon itself is spacious and beautifully designed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfSSlg92dulRrNYPSzWx3Z6zoEPYS3AJIaA5mB&fid=0x0:0xc49dd386e2b57f60"],"When":"2025-1-29"},{"Name":"Danielle Hall-Giles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIya5iedwAQewkOHM-6BpAEkGvH2Jae8N074QxHjUUPtGMyfg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Melissa is awesome! The other stylists are friendly.  I have hair trauma, and she made me feel comfortable. I love my cut.The shampoo was the best I've had. Thank you for creating an environment where I can feel comfortable and welcome. I will be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Jordan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcW5CVJsRbc8HID_wtGKpqOKNY9mzLF7sQbRSgCMw3LVxPyC21=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I worked with the Beauty lounge for my wedding earlier this month. Melissa was not only kind and professional but also very knowledgeable and experienced with working with type 4a-4b curly hair! I was able to do a trial hairstyle in September and not only was the style recreated perfectly on the day of the wedding, it lasted the entire event!(something I have trouble achieving when I do my own hair!) Additionally, I was able to schedule an appointment to get my hair braided for my honeymoon at the beauty lounge with Aquila who did a magnificent job. 10/10 I will be back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1GcbhfXWp-2j3ovNLOna6a_DNyersr3b6EyWO&fid=0x0:0xc49dd386e2b57f60"],"When":"2024-11-23"},{"Name":"Delanie Kordah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmsH9mfbGai06MeP2SW6Ci3W9p8RVnvdX9tRvSnU-NX9jw00-c0g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 recommend this salon. I have mixed daughters and I’ve tried other salons that have just botched their hair and claimed to know what they are doing with mixed hair but have no clue. These ladies kill it every time! I’ve had Nicole and Tiffany with my daughters and have both done absolutely amazing jobs. I will not bring my kids anywhere else for their hair. ♥️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lane Ilstrup","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLCyG_7FyXkYN03GNzXkd4oopPis5SXNiwLGFIKE5htarp5_E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hair has never felt or looked this healthy before! My stylist was Cey who was amazing. I had not had my hair cut professionally for years due to poor experiences and was nervous - she took it in stride and patiently explained every recommendation to get my hair in the style and healthy maintenance I was looking for, with basically no prior knowledge on my part. More expensive than I expected, but that's what you get when you go to someone with expertise and it was worth it. I also had a positive experience here as a transmasculine person, there were no cut or style surprises that can be really common for us when getting a haircut. Altogether could tell that Cey is an experienced stylist who cares a lot about clients' experience in the chair and the education taken away from the appointment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine Jennifer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0iUH6-1E7O36lPrRNPxk8QwLucXxFl8CCdKP1zy_PV2CHKgoR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We used Beauty Lounge for my wedding at the beginning of May and they are PHENOMENAL! We had 9 women total that got both hair and make up services for the wedding and the team absolutely killed it!

For starters - my Bridal hair was styled by Bryanna and it was perfect! She perfectly captured what I wanted and it lasted all night long! I could not have asked for better!

My makeup was done by Melissa! We did both airbrush as well adding lashes and the way she did my makeup made me feel so beautiful! She achieved a flawless look but more importantly, I still looked like myself (just slightly elevated) which was exactly what I was looking for! As I still looked perfect at 2am!

As for my bridesmaids and my mother, Bryanna and Melissa, as well as Stephanie and Natalie coordinated everything perfectly to get everyone ready on time and more importantly every single person so was happy with how it all turned out! We had a number of different hair textures as skin tones, and that team flawlessly executed the hair and make up for us all!

I can not speak highly enough of Melissa and her team! They are incredible people along with running an incredible business and I will 100/100 times tell people that they need to work with Beauty Lounge!

I can't wait to work with them again! Thank you all for your incredible work and making our morning so fun!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOhlRFlRPLj0WrJd1OGmBnfeQaVItnRIra985j&fid=0x0:0xc49dd386e2b57f60"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Laurisa Donte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4k11l76jp331P1E5-c_wA2zRccC0qLMy1zA5DGPqeiw3sPa6gZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very clean, very friendly, very reasonable. I have natural hair, and they did an amazing job.

You feel like you are about to be transformed as soon as you walk in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuC3fw9aO9qB-Qp7MIV2di-PktF_nGX8YYGW-x&fid=0x0:0xc49dd386e2b57f60"],"When":"2024-4-22"},{"Name":"Jill Grunewald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKopCDMBrPqqD0ZXBzkD7Vvd7nNQE-wAuII-Py-dK505k0grw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I simply cannot say enough good things about this place. They're best in class and they're our forever stylists now. Just amazing.","Images":null,"When":""}]
